Omuwendo gw’abantu abafuna obulwadde obuleetebwa akawuka ka corona (COVID-19) ogweyongera ennyo mu Mukago gwa Bulaaya (Eropean Union)/Bulaaya n’Abasuubulagana nayo (European Economic Area) ne Bungereza (United Kingdom), 1 Janwali okutuuka nga 15 Ogwokusatu 2020
Omuwendo gw’abantu abafuna obulwadde obuleetebwa akawuka ka corona (COVID-19) gulaga enneeyisa efaanana wakati w’amawanga g’Omukago gwa Bulaaya /Bulaaya n’Abasuubulagana nayo ne Bungereza nga kino kikakasa nti, newankubadde ekizibu kya COVID-19 kiri ku mitendera gya njawulo mu mawanga ag’enjawulo, kyeyongerera ku misinde gya maanyi mu nsi zonna.
Okusinziira ku kibadde mu Italy, amawanga, amalwaliro n’obusenge obujjanjaba abali obubi ennyo birina okwongera ku ngeri gye beeteeseteeseemu olw’okweyongera kw’omuwendo gw’abalwadde ba COVID-19 abaneetaaga obujjanjabi, naddala obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi.
Nga 31 Deesemba 2019, abalwadde ba lubyamira (pneumonia) atamanyiddwa kimuleeta baazuulwa mu Wuhan, mu Hubei Province, China.
Nga 9 Janwali 2020, China Center for Disease Control and Prevention yategeeza nti obulwadde buno bwali buleetebwa akawuka ka coronavirus akatamanyiddwa nsibuko nga kati akamanyiddwa nga severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Okuva olwo, obulwadde obuva ku kawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 bwatuumibwa coronavirus disease (COVID-19).
Ebizuuliddwa biraga nti ebitundu nga 80% eby’abantu abalina COVID-19 babeera n’obulwadde obutonotono, kwe kugamba, okukosebwa mu mussizo (respiratory tract infection) nga mulimu oba obutabaamu lubyamira, era ng’obisinga ku bwo buwona.
Mu bitundu nga 14%, COVID-19 afuuka obulwadde obw’amaanyi obwetaagisa omuntu okuweebwa ekitanda so ng’abantu ebitundu 6% bafuna obulwadde obw’amaanyi ddala nga beetaaga okuweebwa obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi.
Abalwadde abaweereddwa ebitanda olwa COVID-19 ne bafa bali ebitundu nga 4%.
Mu kunoonyereza kuno, twekenneenya okweyongera mu balwadde ba COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga ly’omu European Union/European Economic Area (EU/EEA) ne Bulaaya (UK) ne tukugeraageranya n’okwa Hubei Province, China.
Era tugeraageranya omuwendo gw’abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu kiseera kino mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK n’ogwa Italy mu kiseera 31 Janwali–15 Ogwokusatu 2020.
Abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK
Oluvannyuma lwa China, COVID-19 yasaasaana mu bitundu ebirala era enneeyisa ya nawookeera wa COVID-19 mu bitundu by’ensi ebirala egoberera ey’eggwanga lino.
Nga 11 Ogwokusatu 2020, Ssenkulu wa World Health Organization (WHO) yalangirira COVID-19 ng’ekizibu eky’awamu mu nsi (pandemic).
Mu lufulumya lwa Eurosurveillance 2020 olwa nga 5 Ogwokusatu, Spiteri ne banne baayogera ku balwadde ba COVID-19 abaasooka mu Bulaaya okusinziira ku nnyinyonnyola ya WHO.
Mu EU/EEA, abalwadde abaasooka baazuulwa mu France nga 24 Janwali 2020 ng’abantu bano baali bavudde mu Wuhan, Hubei Province, China.
Nga 15 Ogwokusatu 2020, obulwadde bwa COVID-19 bwali bumaze okuzuulibwa mu mawanga gonna 30 aga EU/EEA ne UK, nga mu kino wakati wa 31 Deesemba 2019 n’olunaku olwo nga luzingiddwamu, abalwadde baali 39,768 n’abafudde 1,727, ng’abalwadde 17,750 n’abafu 1,441 bava mu Italy mwokka.
Okufuna omuwendo gw’abalwadde ba COVID-19 n’abantu abafuna COVID-19 nga bwe gugenda gweyongera
Ku European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC), emiwendo gy’abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga mu nsi yonna, okuva mu mikutu emitongole nga Minisitule y’Ebyobulamu mu mawanga, ebitebe bya WHO ebyobulamu mu mawanga n’amabendobendo, gizzibwa buggya buli lunaku ku ssaawa 2:00 ez’okumakya.
Obubaka buno bwakozesebwa okwekenneenya ebikwata ku COVID-19 mu EU/EEA ne UK, n’okubigeraageranya n’ebyo eby’omu Italy.
Ng’enkola y’okubala omuwendo gw’abalwadde ba COVID-19 abakyajjanjabwa, twabala omuwendo gw’abantu abafuna COVID-19 ogukutuddwakutuddwamu mu nnaku 14, mu buli ggwanga lya EU/EEA ne UK, mu kiseera kya 1 Janwali–15 Ogwokusatu 2020.
Era twalaga omuwendo gw’abalwadde abazuulibwa mu buli ggwanga nga bwe gugenda gweyongera nga 15 Ogwokusatu 2020 ku ssaawa 2:00 ez’okumakya nga gugeraageranyiziddwa n’ogwa Italy mu kiseera 31 Janwali–15 Ogwokusatu.
Enneeyisa ya COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK
Entambula y’emiwendo gy’abantu abafuna COVID-19 egikutuddwakutuddwamu mu nnaku 14 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK okutwaliza awamu gyagoberera egyo egya Hubei Province (China) (Ekifaananyi 1).
Mu EU/EEA ne UK okutwaliza awamu, omuwendo gw’abantu abafuna COVID-19 gwatandika okweyongera awo nga 21 Ogwokubiri ate era ne gweyongera nnyo awo nga 28 Ogwokubiri 2020 (Enkookero).
Kino kyali bwekityo olw’okweyongera mu bwangu okw’omuwendo okuva mu Italy, naye ng’amawanga ga EU/EEA amalala gonna ne UK gaalimu okweyongera kw’abantu abafuna COVID-19 okufaanana (Enkookero).
Ekifaananyi 2 kiraga omuwendo gw’abantu abafuna COVID-19, mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK nga gugeraageranyiziddwa n’ogwa Italy mu kiseera 31 Janwali–15 Ogwokusatu 2020.
Kiraga nti, nga 15 Ogwokusatu ku ssaawa 2:00 ez’okumakya, amawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK amalala 15 gaalimu omugatte gw’abalwadde ogwali gwenkana n’ogwa Italy mu wiiki 3 zokka emabega oba obutawera.
Bye tuzudde biraga nti omuwendo gw’abalwadde ba COVID-19 gweyongerera ku misinde mingi mu EU/EEA ne UK.
Embeera ezuuliddwa mu muwendo gw’abantu abafuna COVID-19 gutegeeza nti ekizibu kino kyeyongerera ku misinde gyegimu mu mawanga gonna.
Kino kisigala bwekityo amawanga ne bwe gabeera n’ebyobujjanjabi ebiri ku mitendera egy’enjawulo, n’ebisinziirwako eby’enjawulo okusalawo oba omuntu alina obulwadde awamu n’ebigobererwa eby’enjawulo mu kusalawo abantu ab’okukebera okukakasa nti balina COVID-19, nga mw’otwalidde n’okwongera ku muwendo gw’abantu abakeberwa.
Ng’Ogwokusatu 2020 gwakatandika, abasawo mu bitundu ebikoseddwa mu Italy bannyonnyola embeera nti ebitundu 10% eby’abalwadde ba COVID-19 baali beetaaga obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi era amawulire ne gategeeza nti amalwaliro n’ebisenge by’obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi mu bitundu bino byali bijjudde.
Ebikwata ku balwadde ba COVID-19 abali ku bitanda mu ddwaliro ne/oba mu kisenge eky’obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi ebifunika ku mutendera gwa EU/EEA biri ebitundu 6% ne 1% byokka, (obubaka buno tebulagiddwa).
Wabula, bino birina okukuŋŋaanyizibwa mu ntegeka ennungi nga bikkaanya n’obubaka obulagibwa obukwata ku muwendo gw’abalwadde n’abafudde.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu 2010–11 kwalaga enjawulo ey’amaanyi mu bitanda by’obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi n’ebyobujjanjabi obusaamusaamu mu Bulaaya, nga mu Germany biri ebitanda 29.2 so nga mu Portugal biri 4.2 ku buli bantu 100,000.
Kino kitegeeza nti waliwo amawanga agalina ebyobujjanjabi ebisinga oba ebitatuuka ku bya Italy (ebitanda 12.5 eby’obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi n’obusaamusaamu ku buli bantu 100,000 mu 2010–11).
Ebiyinza okutuukawo nga byekuusa ku kujjula kw’ebikozesebwa mu byobulamu, nga bisinziira ku kugeraageranya abalwadde ba COVID-19 abali ku bitanda mu buli ggwanga lya EU/EEA ne UK awamu n’obuzibu bw’okuba ng’obwetaavu bw’ebitanda by’obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi bususse ebitundu 90%, biragiddwa mu mawulire ag’omulundi ogwomukaaga aga ECDC rapid risk assessment on COVID-19.
Olw’okuba ng’abalwadde bakyali mu bitundu ebimu mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK, so ng’amalwaliro n’obusenge bw’obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi gaweereza abantu b’omu bitundu ebimanyiddwa, ebikwata ku balwadde n’ebitanda eby’obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi byandibadde bifunirwa mu ngeri ya Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Ekibadde mu Italy n’ekigenda mu maaso mu mawanga amalala kiraga nti ekizibu kya COVID-19COVID-19 kyeyongerera ku misinde gya maanyi mu EU/EEA ne UK.
Noolwekyo, amalwaliro n’obusenge bw’obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi birina okweteekateekera embeera ey’okusaasaanyizibwa kwa SARS-CoV-2 mu bantu b’omu bitundu n’okweyongera kw’omuwendo gw’abalwadde ba COVID-19 abeetaaga obujjanjabi, n’okusingira ddala obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi, okugeza ng’eyo eri mu bitundu bya Italy ebikoseddwa.
Nga bwe kyalagibwa mu kwekenneenya kwa ECDC okw’obuzibu okw’amangu, okweteekateeka obulungi okw’amangu kukulu nnyo mu kulemesa okusaasaana kwa SARS-COV-2, nga kw’otadde n’okuseetuka okuva ku kulemesa okusaasaana okudda ku kuwonya, olw’okuba ng’okweyongera okw’amangu mu muwendo gw’abalwadde okusuubirwa kuyinza obutasobozesa ba buyinza na malwaliro kufuna budde bumala okutegeera, okukkiriza n’okutuukiriza enkola zaabwenga bwe kyetaagisa singa ziba teziteereddwa mu nkola nga bukyali.
Okwekenneenya obuzibu okw’amangu kulaga enkola z’ebyobulamu ez’okulwanyisa obuzibu bw’ekizibu kino.
Waliwo omwagaanya mutono amawanga mwe galina obusobozi bw’okwongerera amaanyi gaago mu kukendeeza okusaasaana kwa SARS-CoV-2 n’okukendeeza omunyigirizo oguteereddwa ku byobujjanjabi.
Kino bwe kirema, kisuubirwa nti ebyobujjanjabi mu mawanga ga EU/EEA amalala gunyigirizibwa olw’omuwendo gw’abalwadde ogweyongera ennyo nga beetaaga obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi mu nnaku oba wiiki ezijja.
Obulwadde bwa Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19), obuleetera severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), bwakwatta abantu abasoba mu 3,000 era ng’abantu abasoba mu 80,000 be baakabufuna mu China n’awalala mu nsi, nga kino kireeseewo akatyabaga mu bantu.
Nga bwe guli ku kawuka akakafaanana aka SARS-CoV, akaaleeta SARS mu nkumi z’abantu mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 nako kayinza okutambuzibwa obuwundo era kaleeta obubonero obufaanana mu ngeri efaanana.
Wabula, COVID-19 si wa maanyi kwenkana SARS era asse abantu batonotono naye atambuzibwa okusingako era akosa abantu abakuluko n’abasajja okusinga abavubuka n’abakazi.
Mu kwanukula ebifulumiziddwa ebingi ku bulwadde buno obubaluseewo, olupapula luno lugenderera okulaga okwekenneenya okunoonyereza okubaluseewo embagirawo mu bujjuvu.
Tujja kwogera ku bisookerwako ku bulwadde, ekibuleeta, obuwuka, enkebera, enzijanjaba, okuteebereza eby’omu maaso, n’enneewala yaabwo.
Newankubadde nga waliwo ebibuuzo bingi ebikyetaaga okwanukulwa, tulowooza nti okwekenneenya kuno kujja kuyamba mu kutegeera n’okumalawo obulwadde buno obweraliikirizza abantu.
Ebikujjuko bya Spring ebya Janwali 25, 2020 byafuuka omukolo ogutayinza kwerabirwa eri Abachina abaasabibwa okusigala mu mayumba gaabwe okumala oluwummula lwonna ne wiiki ezaddirira olw’okubalukawo kw’obulwadde obuleetebwa akawuka akaali tekamanyiddwa novel.
Akawuka kano kafaananira ddala aka coronavirus (CoV) akaaleeta severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) mu 2003; noolwekyo, World Health Organization (WHO) yakatuuma SARS-CoV-2 nga 11 Ogwokubiri 2020, era n’obulwadde bwe kaleeta ne butuumibwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Obulwadde buno bwatandikira mu Wuhan, China, era mangu ddala ne busaasaanira eggwanga lyonna n’amawanga amalala nga 50 okwetooloola ensi yonna.
Mu Gwokusatu nga 2, 2020, akawuka kaali kamaze okuviirako abantu abasoba mu 80,000 abakakasiddwa okuba ne COVID-19, ng’abasoba mu 40,000 bawonye ate ng’abasoba mu 3,000 bafudde.
WHO erabula nti COVID-19 ye “mulabe w’omuntu nnamba 1” era ayinza okuba nga wa bulabe okusinga obutujju.
Okusinziira ku PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu kiseera ekitaweza myezi ebiri, empapula ezisoba mu 200 zifulumiziddwa ku COVID-19 omuli ezikwata ku kawuka, obulwadde, ekibuleeta, enkebera n’enzijanjaba okuva ku alipoota esooka nga Janwali 7, 2020 eyazuula endagabutonde y’akawuka akaayawulwa okuva mu balwadde ab’enjawulo.
Okwekenneenya kuno kugenderera okufunza okunoonyereza okukoleddwa mu kisaawe kino ekipya ekikulaakulanira ku misinde emingi.
We kinaasokeranga, tujja kugezaako okugeraageranya COVID-19 ne SARS n’obulwadde obulala obuleetebwa CoV, Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS, eyabalukawo mu 2012).
Era tujja kukubaganya ebirowoozo ku ebyo bye twakayiga ebikwata ku kwewala obulwadde buno n’ebyo ebiteeberezebwa awamu n’ebibuuzo ebitannayanukulwa so nga bikulu.
CoVs bwatwalibwanga ng’obuwuka obutali bwa bulabe nnyo eri abantu, ng’okusinga buleeta ebitundu nga 15% ebya ssenyiga owa bulijjo 4.
Wabula, mu kyasa kino, tufunye obuwuka bwa CoVs obw’omutawaana eri abantu emirundi ebiri, kwe kugamba, SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV, obwavaako obulwadde okusooka mu China mu 2003 ne Saudi Arabia mu 2012, amangu ddala ne busaasaanira amawanga amalala ne bulwaza awamu n’okutta abantu abawerako.
Noolwekyo, COVID-19 aliwo mu kiseera kino ye CoV ow’omulundi ogwokusatu okubalukawo mu byafaayo by’omuntu ebimanyiddwa.
Nga bwe kiragiddwa mu Kifaananyi. ​Ekifaananyi.1,1, abalwadde ba lubyamira eyali tamanyiddwako nsibuko baasooka kutegeezebwa mu Wuhan nga Deesemba 31, 2019 eri China National Health Commission.
Oluvannyuma lw’ennaku musanvu endagabutonde ya CoV yafulumizibwa.
Nga Janwali 15, 2020 omulwadde eyasooka okuyisibwa obubi okuva mu Wuhan yayogerwako.
Mu kiseera kino, obulwadde buno bwasaasaana mangu nnyo mu bibuga ebyetoolodde, n’amawanga.
Nga Janwali 20, okulwala kw’abasawo kwayogerwako, ekyategeeza nti abantu baali basobola okufuna obulwadde buno nga babuggya ku bantu.
Nga Janwali 23, ekibuga ky’e Wuhan kyaggalwawo n’entambula yaakyo ey’olukale yonna n’eyimirizibwa.
Nga Janwali 24 okunoonyereza kw’ekisawo okusooka ku bulwadde buno kwategeeza nti, ku balwadde 41 abaali bakakasiddwa, 21 bokka be baatuukako obutereevu mu katale k’e Wuhan ak’ebyennyanja nga ke kaalowoozebwa okuba ng’obulwadde gye bwatandikira nga buva ku kisolo ekitamanyiddwa.
Nga Janwali 30, WHO yalangirira ng’obulwadde buno bwe bwali ekizibu ky’ebyobulamu eky’amangu mu nsi yonna.
Mu kiseera alipoota eno w’ekoleddwa, obulwadde bumaze okusaasaanira China ne mu mawanga agawera nga 50 okwetooloola ensi (Ekifaananyi ​(Ekifaananyi.2).2).
Embeera nga bw’egenda ekyuka, ekinaavaamu n’obunene bw’ekizibu tebunnaba kutegeerwa.
Mu Gwokubiri nga 11, 2020, okunoonyereza okwakolerwa mu bifo eby’enjawulo ku bantu 8,866 omwali n’abakakasiddwa okubeera ne COVID-19 4,021 kwawa ennyinyonnyola empya ey’akawuka bw’eti (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 akwata abantu ab’emyaka gyonna, naye okusinga emyaka 30-65.
Kyenkana amakkati (47.7%) g’abantu abaalina obulwadde baali basussa emyaka 50 egy’obukulu, batono nnyo abaali wansi wa 20, so ng’abalwadde 14 bokka be baali wansi w’emyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yali mu basajja bangiko (0.31/100,000) okusinga abakazi (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 yeeyongera mu bantu okusinga mu Hubei n’okwetoololawo.
COVID-19 yamala ennaku nga 5 (2-9) okuva lwe yatadika okutuuka lwe yazuulibwa.
Ekiseera obubonero mwe bweyolekera kyali ennaku nga 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
Ekiseera okuva ku kumufuna okutuuka okufa kyali ennaku 9.5 (4.8-13).
Abantu omulwadde omu b’asiiga (basic reproductive number, R0) baali 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51-4.05), so ng’omuwendo gwa R0 ogwakyusibwamu gwali 2.23-4.82.
Omuwendo gw’abalwadde gwatumbuka nga 23 Janwali 2020 terunnatuuka, olw’abantu abangi ennyo abaatambula ng’ebikujjuko bya Spring Festival mu China tebinnatuuka.
Abalwadde abaafa baali ebitundu 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%), so ng’omuwendo gw’abalwadde abaafa ogwakyusibwamu gwali ebitundu 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Obuzibu bwa COVID-19 obusatu obw’amaanyi bwali okwegatta (abasajja), emyaka (≥60), ne lubyamira ow’amaanyi.
Obuwuka bwa CoVs bugwa mu kika ky’obuwuka obunene era obwetooloddwa olububi nga bulina RNA ya luguwa lumu.
Busobola okugabanyizibwamu ebika (genera) bina, kwe kugamba, alpha, beta, gamma, ne delta, nga ku bino alpha- ne beta-CoVs bwe bumanyiddwa nti bulwaza abantu.
Olububi lwa (S) glycoprotein lwekwata ku butaffaali bwako obwa angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ne dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) ku buwuka SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV, mu nsengeka eyo, olwo embubi z’amasavu zombi nne zeegatta.
Endagabutonde ya RNA ey’akawuka esindikibwa mu kataffaali; oluvannyuma lw’okukubisaamu endagabutonde y’akawuka, endagabutonde ya RNA ng’eri n’olububi lwa glycoproteins ne nucleocapsid proteins ekola obutaffaali obulimu akawuka, nga kano ke keegatta n’akabubi k’omusaayi okufulumya akawuka.
Endagabutonde ya SARS-CoV-2 eyasooka yafulumizibwa nga Jamwali 10, 2020.
SARS-CoV-2 kaazuulwa nga kaali ka kika kipya ekya beta-CoV nga bufaanana mu ndagabutonde ebitonde ebitundu 99.98% mu sampolo 10 ezaakeberwa nga zino zaggyibwa mu kifo ekyasookera ddala okubaamu akawuka kano, ekya Huanan Seafood Market mu Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 kafaanana nnyo SARS-CoV mu ndagabutonde okusinga MERS-CoV.
Mu kukozesa ebyuma ebitangaaza, obutundutundu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwazuulwa mu bitundu by’ekkubo ly’omukka ogussibwa.
Enzyme zi ACE2 zaasangibwa nga zisika SARS-CoV-2 awamu ne SARS-CoV.
Wabula, puloteni ya S eya SARS-CoV-2 yeekwata ku enzyme za ACE2 naye nga teyeenweza nga bwe guba ku SARS-CoV, nga kino kikwatagana n’eky’okuba nti SARS-CoV-2 atuusa obulabe butonoko mu bantu bw’ogeraageranya ne SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 era asobola okukola puloteni ennyimpi etalabwangako eyinza okutuumibwa orf3b ne puloteni efulumizibwa eyinza okutuumibwa orf8.
orf3b eya SARS-CoV-2 eyinza okuba nga y’evunaanyizibwa ku kulwaza abantu era n’eremesa IFNβ okweyoleka; wabula, orf8 teriimu kirungo kikola.
Mu Gwokubiri nga 18, 2020, Zhou, ne banne, baalaga obuzimbe bwa cryo-EM obujjuvu obwa enzyme ya ACE2 ku bwawule (resoulution) obwa 2.9 Å mu kabubi ka amino acid aka B0AT1.
Baakizuula ng’omugatte guno, ogwalimu atomu ez’emirundi ebiri, gwali gusengekeddwa nga molecule eya atomu engatte era ng’omugatte gwa ACE2-B0AT1 gusobola okugatta puloteni za S, nga kino kiraga obukakafu bw’okulaba CoV n’oyo gw’akutte.
B0AT1 eyinza okuba nga yeeruubirirwa okujjanjabwa olw’okukebera eddagala ery’okunafuya SARS-CoV-2.
Ensibuko n’ebikatambuza
Kimanyiddwa nti SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV bwombi bwasibuka mu buwundo era ne butuuka ku bantu nga buyitira mu mafumbe n’eŋŋamiya, mu busengeke obwo.
Mu kugeraageranya SARS-CoV-2 n’obuwuka bwa CoVs obulala, obuwundo butwalibwa okuba nga bwe bunnansangwa mu kutambuza SARS-CoV-2 olw’okuba ng’akawuka kano kafaananya ebitundu 96% n’obuwuka bwa CoVs obulala bubiri obufaanana SARS nga nabwo bubeera mu buwundo nga buyitibwa bat-SL-CoVZX45 ne bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Wabula, ekisolo kyennyini ekyayamba okubuuka omuziziko okutuuka mu bantu tekinnamanyika, era n’ekkubo lye kayitamu terinnakakasibwa.
Ji, ne banne balowooza nti emisota gyaggya akawuka mu buwundo okukatuusa mu bantu nga kino kyalimu okuwaanyisiganya endagabutonde za S protein.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza, abanoonyereza mu Guangzhou, China, baalaga nti olugave (pangolin) - ekisolo eky’omumwa omusongovu, ekirya ebiwuka nga kitera okukozesebwa mu bujjanjabi bw’Ekichina obw’ekinnansi - lusobola okuba nga lwe lutambuza SARS-CoV-2 okumutuusa mu bantu okusinziira ku bufaanane bw’endagabutonde obw’ebitundu 99% mu CoV obwazuulwa mu lugave ne mu SARS-CoV-2.
Wabula, enjawulo ey’ekitundu 1% wakati w’endagabutonde ebbiri eba ekyali nnene; noolwekyo, obukakafu bwenkomeredde tebunnafunibwa (Fig. ​(Ekifaananyi 33).
Ebikwata ku bukole bwa SARS-CoV-2 ebisinga tebinnamanyibwa.
Obuwuka bwa SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV busobola okumala mu ggiraasi essaawa 48 nga nkalu n’ennaku eziwera 5 mu lutuuyo lw’ebbugumo 20 °C ne 40%-50%.
SARS-CoV-2 ayinza okuba n’embeera zeezimu.
Kiragiddwa nti akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 tekakwatagana na magulu ga njuba (ultraviolet rays) n’ebbugumu eriweza 56 °C okumala eddakiika 30; walagi ebitundu 75%, eddagala eririmu chlorine, peracetic acid, kalifoomu, n’ebiyiika ebirala eby’ekyovu, naye nga si chlorhexidine, bisobola bulungi okutta akawuka kano.
Abantu bonna okutwaliza awamu tebalina busibage (immunity) bulwanyisa SARS-CoV-2 nga noolwekyo basobola okukosebwa akawuka kano.
Mu kiseera kino, tewali kunoonyereza kwakoleddwa kulaga busibage eri SARS-CoV-2.
Noolwekyo, tusobola kwesigama ku kunoonyereza kwokka okwakolebwa edda ku CoVs, naddala SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV (Ekifaananyi ​(Ekifaananyi 4).4).
Okutwaliza awamu, akawuka bwe kalumba ekisolo ekikatambuza, kasooka kuzuulibwa enkola y’obusibage bw’ekisolo ekyo okuyita mu pattern recognition receptors (PRRs) omuli ezo ez’ebika bya C-type lectin-like receptors), Toll-like receptor (TLR), NOD-like receptor (NLR), ne RIG-I-like receptor (RLR).
Nga kayita mu makubo ag’enjawulo, akawuka kaleetawo okuzimba, okukula kwa dendritic cells, n’okuleetawo interferons ez’ekika I interferons (IFNs) eziremesa okusaasaana kw’akawuka ne kyongera obutaffaali bwa macrophage okulwanyisa akawuka.
Wabula, puloteni ya N eya SARS-CoV esobola okukayamba okutoloka ku busibage.
Mu bwangu, obusibage obufunibwa (adaptive immune response) bwegatta ku lutalo lw’okulwanyisa akawuka.
T lymphocytes omuli CD4+ ne CD8+ T cells zikola omulimu munene mu kulwanyisa akawuka.
CD4+ T cells zizuukusa B cells okukola abasirikale abalwanyisa akawuka, ate CD8+ T cells zitta butereevu obutaffaali obulumbiddwa akawuka.
T helper cells zikola proinflammatory cytokines okuyamba mu kukuuma obutaffaali.
Wabula, akawuka ka CoV kasobola okulemesa emirimu gya T cell nga kaleetera T cells okufa.
Obusibage obuyitibwa humoral immunity nga mw’otwalidde ne puloteni nga C3a ne C5a ne antibodies nabwo bwa mugaso mu kulwanyisa akawuka kano.
Okugeza, antibodies ezaggyibwa mu mulwadde eyawona zaasannyalaza MERS-CoV.
Ku ludda olulala, obusibage okukola ennyo kireetera okufulumya molekyu ennyingi (free radicals) eziviirako okukosa ennyo amawuggwe n’ebitundu ebirala, olumu ne kireetera ebitundu by’omubiri bingi okulemererwa n’oluusi okufa.
Akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2, akaasangibwa mu bantu abaasooka okukeberwa, kalabika nga kasinga kukosa bakadde abalina ebirwadde ebirala n’abakazi ab’embuto.
Kya bulijjo abantu abalina obuwuka obw’enjawulo oba abalina obusibage obutono, baba n’emikisa mingi okulwala okusinga ku balala.
Ekiseera akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 kye katwala okulaga obubonero kya nnaku 1-14, ebiseera ebisinga ennaku 3-7 okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku balwadde 425 abaasooka mu Wuhan.
Wabula, okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu balwadde 1,099 kulaga nti okutwalira awamu akawuka kano kamala ennaku 3 okulaga obubonero era ng’ennaku ziba wakati wa 0 ku 24.
Okunoonyereza okukyali okupya, okwogeddwako waggulu, kulaga nti kamala ennaku 4.8 (3.0-7.2) okusinziira ku bikwata ku balwadde 8,866.
Kikulu nnyo ab’ebyobulamu okuteeka ennaku za kalantiini nga beesigama ku kiseera ekituufu akawuka kye kamala okulaga obubonero, basobole okwewala abantu abalina akawuka naye nga tebalina bubonero okusiiga abalala akawuka.
Ekitera okukolebwa, abantu ababeera mu mbeera erimu akawuka oba abalina akawuka baba beetaaga okubeera mu kalantiini okumala ennaku 14.
Ekiseera abantu kye bamala mu kalantiini kyetaaga okwongezebwayo kituuke ku nnaku 24?
Omusujja ke katera okubeera akabonero ka COVID-19 akakulu era akasooka, nga gusobola obutagobererwa kabonero konna oba obubonero obulala ng’akakololo akakalu, okukaluubirirwa mu kussa, okulumwa ebinywa, kammunguluze, okulumwa omutwe, amabwa mu bulago, eminyira mu nnyindo, okulumwa ekifuba, okuddukana, okusiikuuka emmeeme, n’okusesema.
Abalwadde abamu baafuna okukaluubirirwa mu kussa ne/oba okubulwa empewo mu musaayi nga wayise wiiki emu okuva bwe baafuna obulwadde.
Mu mbeera enzibu ennyo, abalwadde baayanguwa okufuna obuzibu bw’amazzi okugenda mu mawuggwe, puleesa eya wansi (septic shock), metabolic acidosis, ne coagulopathy.
Abalwadde abalina omusujja ne/oba obubonero obwekuusa ku kussa n’omusujja ogw’amangu, ne bwe baba nga tebalina buzibu ku mawuggwe, basaana okukeberwa nga bukyali okuzuula oba nga balina akawuka.
Okunoonyereza kw’ebikwata ku balwadde okwakolebwa mu Deesemba wa 2019 kwalaga nti ebitundu by’obubonero ku buli kikumi byali 98% ku musujja, 76% ku kakololo akakalu, 55% ku kukaluubirirwa mu kussa, ne 3% ku kuddukana; abalwadde ebitundu 8% baali beetaaga ebyuma ebiyamba mu kussa.
Ebyazuulwa ebifaananako n’ebyo byalagibwa mu kunoonyereza okw’emirundi ebiri okwakakolebwa ku balwadde ab’enju emu n’abalwadde abaasiigibwa omuntu ataalaga bubonero.
Mu kugeraageranya, okunoonyereza kw’ebikwata ku bantu okwakolebwa mu 2012 kwalaga nti abalwadde ba MERS-CoV nabo baalina omusujja (98%), akakololo akakalu (47%), n’okukaluubirirwa mu kussa (55%) ng’obubonero bwabwe obukulu.
Wabula, ebitundu 80% ku bo baali beetaaga ebyuma ebiyambako mu kussa, okusingira ddala abalwadde ba COVID-19 era nga kino kigendera wamu n’eky’okuba nti MERS yali wa bulabe okusinga ku COVID-19.
Okuddukana (26%) n’amabwa mu bulago (21%) nabyo byalabwa mu balwadde ba MERS.
Mu balwadde ba SARS, kiragiddwa nti omusujja (99%-100%), akakololo akakalu (29%-75%), okukaluubirirwa mu kussa (40%-42%), okuddukana (20-25%), n’amabwa mu bulago (13-25%) bwe bwali obubonero obukulu era ng’ebyuma ebiyamba ku kussa byali byetaagisa mu balwadde nga 14%-20%.
Mu Gwokubiri nga 14, abantu abaali baakafa COVID-19 baali ebitundu 2% ng’abalwadde abakakasiddwa bali 66,576 mu nsi yonna.
Mu kugeraageranya, abantu abaali bafudde SARS mu Noovemba 2002 baali ebitundu 10% ku balwadde abakakasiddwa 8,096.
Ate ku MERS, okusinziira ku kunoonyereza kw’ebikwata ku bantu okwakolebwa mu Gwomukaaga 2012, abantu abaali bafudde baali ebitundu 37% ku balwadde abakakasiddwa 2,494.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa emabegako kwalaga nti R0 ya SARS-CoV-2 yali waggulu nga ya 6.47 ng’omuwendo ogwateeberezebwa (confidence interval, CI) gwali ebitundu 95% nga gwali 5.71-7.23, so nga R0 ya SARS-CoV yali wakati wa 2 ku 4 yokka.
Okugeraageranya SARS-CoV-2 awamu ne MERS-CoV ne SARA-CoV ku bikwata ku bubonero bwabwo, enzita yaabwo, ne R0 kulagiddwa mu Mweso ​Omweso1.1.
Emiwendo egyo giraga nti SARS-CoV-2 alina obusobozi bw’okusaasaana bungi okusinga ku MERS-CoV ne SARS-CoV, naye nga si ka bulabe kwenkana obulala obubiri.
Noolwekyo, kizibu nnyo okukkakkanya ekizibu kya SARS-CoV-2 okusinga ekya MERS-CoV ne SARS-CoV.
Abantu abalwalira okumu batera okubeera mu maka gamu oba mu lukuŋŋaana lumu oba mu kidduka kimu nga ku lyato.
Abalwadde ab’engeri eno baba baatambula okuva oba nga baabeerako mu Wuhan oba ebifo ebirala ebyalimu obulwadde oba nga baaliko n’abantu abaalina akawuka oba abalwadde wiiki bbiri nga tebannafuna bulwadde.
Wabula, kitegeezeddwa nti abantu basobola okubeera n’akawuka naye ne batalaga bubonero okumala ekiseera ekisukka wiiki ebbiri era n’abalwadde abawonye ne basiibulwa mu malwaliro nabo basobola okuddamu okubeera n’akawuka, nga kino kiraga obwetaavu bw’okwongera ku kiseera kya kalantiini.
Abalwadde baba n’omuwendo ogwa bulijjo oba ogukendedde ogw’obutaffaali bw’omu mu musaayi obweru mu musaayi ogutambula (peripheral white blood cells) (naddala lymphocytes) mu kiseera ekisooka.
Okugeza, lymphopenia awamu ne white blood cell count &lt; 4×109/L nga mw’otwalidde ne lymphocyte count &lt; 1×109/L, ne aspartate aminotransferase ayongezeddwa ne viremia byasangibwa mu balwadde ba COVID-19 abawera 1,099 COVID-19.
Omuwendo gwa enzyme z’ekibumba ne myoglobin gwalinnyisibwa mu musaayi gw’abalwadde abamu, era ne C-reactive protein ne erythrocyte sedimentation nabyo byalinnya mu musaayi gw’abalwadde abasinga.
Mu balwadde abaali obubi ennyo, omuwendo gwa D-dimer, ng’eno fibrin degradation product ebeera mu musaayi, yeeyongera, n’omuwendo gwa lymphocyte ne gukendeera.
Waliwo obuzibu obulabwa mu kifuba mu balwadde ba COVID-19 abasinga obungi era nga kino kigendera wamu n’obuzibu mu mawuggwe gaabwe (bilateral patchy shadows oba ground glass opacity).
Abalwadde batera okufuna lubyamira atali wa bulijjo, okukosebwa okw’amangu mu mawuggwe, n’obuzibu mu kkubo ly’omukka ogussibwa (acute respiratory distress syndrome, ARDS).
ARDS bw’ebaawo, wabaawo okuzimba n’okufuna amazzi amangi, n’ennyama n’ebikka ebiwundu ekireetawo obuzibu mu kuwaanyisiganya kw’omukka.
Pneumocytes ez’ekika I ne II (type-I and type-II pneumocytes) zikendeeza omuwendo gwa surfactant ne zongeza okunyigirizibwa kungulu, ekyo ne kikendeeza obusobozi bw’amawuggwe okugaziwa ne kyongera emikisa gy’amawuggwe okulemererwa.
Noolwekyo, ebyazuulibwa ebikyasinze okubeera ebibi mu kukebera ekifuba bitera okuba nga byenkanankana n’embeera y’obulwadde ekyasinze okubeera embi.
Mu Gwokubiri nga 18, 2020, okwekenneenya obulwadde bwa COVID-19 okwasooka mu ggezeserezo kwalaga okuyubuka kwa pneumocytes, okukolebwa kw’olububi lwa hyaline, n’okwatika kw’olususu, ne multinucleated syncytial cells mu mawuggwe g’omulwadde eyafa obulwadde buno, nga kino kifaanana n’okwekenneenya abalwadde abalina obuwuka ne ARDS era nga kifaanana n’eky’abalwadde ba SARS ne MERS.
Okuzuula RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 okuyita mu reverse-transcriptase polymerase chain reaction (RT-PCR) kyakozesebwa ng’enkola eyasinga mu kukebera COVID-19.
Wabula, olw’okuba nga waliwo bangi abazuulwa nti tebalina kawuka so nga bakalina, ekiyinza okusajjula ekizibu ky’obulwadde, obubonero bw’embeera y’obulamu bwatandika okukozesebwa mu kukebera (nga tebakyesigama ku RT-PCR yekka) mu China mu Gwokubiri nga 13, 2020.
Embeera y’emu era yaliwo ne ku kukebera SARS.
Noolwekyo, okugatta ebyafaayo by’obuwadde, obubonero, okukebera kw’omu ggezeserezo, n’okukuba ekifaananyi kikulu era kisaanye okukolebwa okusobola okuzuula obulungi obulwadde.
Mu Gwokubiri nga 14, 2020, Feng Zhang group yannyonnyola enkola y’okukozesa akakodyo CRISPR-based SHERLOCK technique okuzuula SARS-CoV-2, nga kano kazuula obutundutundu bwa SARS-CoV-2 RNA ku 20 × 10-18 mol/L okutuuka ku 200 × 10-18 mol/L (kkopi 10-100 buli microliter y’ekikeberwa) nga bakozesa akati (dipstick) mu kiseera ekitaweza ddakiika asatu awatali kwetaaga kupima bintu bingi.
Kisuubirwa nti akakodyo kano akapya kasobola okuyamba ennyo mu kukebera singa kaba kakasiddwa mu sampolo ezikeberwa mu mageserezo.
Olw’obutabaawo bumanyirivu ku kawuka ka CoV akabadde tekamanyiddwa, abasawo okusinga basobola kulabirira bulabirizi balwadde ba COVID-19, nga bwe bagezaako eddagala ery’enjawulo eryali likozeseddwako oba nga lyalagirwako emabega mu kujjanjaba obuwuka bwa CoV obulala nga SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV n’obulwadde bw’obuwuka obulala (Omweso ​(Omweso2).2).
Eddagala lino mulimu erikozesebwa mu kiseera kino n’eryo eriyinza okujjanjaba obuwuka, erikendeeza ku busibage, steroids, omusaayi (plasma) okuva ku bantu abawonye, eddagala ly’Ekichina, n’okubudaabudibwa.
Ne plasma okuva ku bantu abawonye naye yateesebwa okukozesebwa ng’eddagala.
Kampuni ezikola eddagala zikola butaweera okukola antibodies n’eddagala erigema akawuka kano.
SARS-CoV-2 kasinga kulumba mawuggwe mu kusooka era nga kirabika oluvannyuma ne kalyoka kalumba ebitundu ebirala ebirina ACE2, omwo nga mwe muli omuyungo gw’ebyenda (gastrointestinal system) n’ensigo.
Wadde nga guli bwegutyo, obuzibu bw’okulemererwa okussa kye kizibu ekisinga mu balwadde era kye kisinga okuviirako okufa.
Noolwekyo, ebyuma ebiyamba mu kussa bikulu nnyo mu kukola ku buzibu bw’okussa n’okutaasa obulamu era nga kino kizingiramu ebintu nga general oxygen therapy, high-flow oxygen, noninvasive ventilation, ne invasive mechanical ventilation okusinziira ku bungi bw’obulwadde.
Abalwadde abalina obuzibu obw’amaanyi mu kussa balina okuyambibwako ne extracorporeal membrane oxygenation (ECMO), nga y’enkola ekozesebwa mu kujjanjaba ababa balemereddwa ddala okussa ekiyinza okubaviirako okufa.
Ekirala, okukuuma ekigero kya electrolyte, okwewala n’okujjanjaba akawuka akalala akayinza okulumba omulwadde n’akawuka okusaasaanira omubiri, n’okukuuma ebitundu by’omubiri ebikulu ne bisigala nga bikola nabyo bikulu nnyo mu balwadde ba SARS-CoV-2.
Kibadde kimanyiddwa nti cytokine storm ava ku busibage okukola ekisusse (overreaction of the immune system) mu balwadde ba SARS ne MERS.
Cytokine storm kwe kwanukula kw’omubiri okulimu okuzimba olw’okufulumya cytokines ez’enjawulo omuli TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, ne MCP-1.
Cytokines zino zireetera obutaffaali obulwanyisa endwadde okufulumya molekyu ennyingi nga zino ze zisinga okuviirako ARDS n’ebitundu by’omubiri eby’enjawulo okulemererwa.
Okukendeeza ku busibage kikulu mu kujjanjaba cytokine storms, naddala mu balwadde abali obubi.
Corticosteroids ne tocilizumab, ng’eno anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody, zikozeseddwa okujjanjaba cytokine storm.
Enzijanjaba ya cytokine storm endala ey’okukendeeza ku busibage mwemuli okutuukanya T cell-directed immune response; okuggalira IFN-γ, IL-1, ne TNF; JAK inhibition; blinatumomab; suppressor of cytokine signaling 4; ne HDAC inhibitors.
Steroids, nga zikozesebbwa okukendeeza ku busibage, zaakozesebwa nnyo mu kujjanjaba SARS okukendeeza ku kukosebwa kw’okuzimba.
Wabula, steroids bwe zikozesebwa mu bungi tezaayamba ku bulabe obutuusibwa ku mawuggwe mu balwadde ba SARS ne COVID-19.
Mpozzi ate, ziyinza okuviirako obukosefu (side effects) obw’amaanyi, naddala avascular osteonecrosis, ekiyinza okukosa ebyo ebisuubirwa okuvaamu.
Newankubadde guli gutyo, kiteeseddwa nti corticosteroids akozesebwe mu balwadde ba COVID-19 abayi ennyo mu doozi entonotono.
Mu kiseera ky’okuwandiikiramu olupapula luno, tewali ddagala lyakakasiddwa kuwonya kawuka kano.
Wabula, okuweebwa remdesivir ng’ayisibwa mu misuwa, ng’eno nucleotide analog, kyazuulibwa nga kyakola ku mulwadde wa COVID-19 Omumerika.
Remdesivir ddagala lya buwuka ppya nga lyakolebwa Gilead nga mu kusooka lyakozesebwa mu kujjanjaba endwadde ezireetebwa obuwuka bwa Ebola ne Marlburg.
Oluvannyuma, remdesivir era kyazuulibwa ng’asobola okujjanjaba obuwuka obulala obulina single stranded RNA omuli MERS ne SARS.
Nga beesigama ku bino, aba Gilead baawa China eddagala lino okuligezesa ku bantu abalina SARS-CoV-2, era ebinaavaamu birindiriddwa n’amaddu mangi.
Ekirala, baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir, ne ribavirin nalyo liteeseddwa ng’eddagala eriyinza okujjanjaba abalwadde abalina obuzibu obw’amaanyi mu kussa.
Ekiddukano, okusiikuuka emmeeme, okusesema, okukosebwa ekibumba, n’obuzibu obulala obw’amaanyi busobola okujjawo nga lopinavir/ritonavir agattiddwa n’eddagala eddala.
Entabagana y’eddagala lino n’eddagala eddala nga likozeseddwa ku balwadde esaanye okulondoolwa n’obwegendereza.
Plasma okuva mu balwadde abawonye n’okukola zi antibody
Okuggya omusaayi ku bantu abawonye obulwadde obusiigibwa okusobola okujjanjaba abalwadde abalala abalina obulwadde bwebumu obwo oba okutaasa abantu abalamu obutafuna bulwadde obwo kibaddewo okumala ekiseera.
Mu butuufu, abantu abawonye obulwadde batera okuba ne antibody nnyingi ezisobola okulwanyisa obulwadde obwo mu musaayi gwabwe.
Antibodies buba butaffaali obukolebwa B lymphocytes okulwanyisa obuwuka n’ebintu ebirala ebitalina kubeera mu mubiri era bukenga molekyu ez’enjawulo eziba mu buwuka ne bubunafuya butereevu.
Nga basinziira ku kino, plasma yaggyibwa mu musaayi gw’ekibinja ky’abalwadde abaawona COVID-19 n’akubwa mu balwadde 10 abaali obubi ennyo.
Embeera yaabwe yalongooka mu ssaawa 24, era n’okuzimba ne kukendeera n’omuwendo gw’akawuka ne gukendeera era n’entambula y’empewo mu musaayi n’etereera.
Wabula, walina okubaawo okwekakasa n’okutangaaza okusobola okuyisa enkola yonna okukozesebwa ku bantu abangi ng’enkola eyo tennaba kukulaakulanyizibwa.
Ekirala, olw’ebyo ebiva mu kukozesa eddagala, ebibi ebyekuusa ku plasma birina okusooka okutunuulirwa.
Okugeza, antibodies zisobola okuviirako obusibage okweyongera ennyo ne kireetawo cytokine release syndrome, nga kino kivaamu obutwa obw’obulabe ennyo.
Antibodies ezibeera mu musaayi zitera kubeera ntono, ate ng’obwetaavu bwa plasma bubeera bungi okusobola okujjanjaba abantu abalwadde ennyo.
Kizibu okukulaakulanya n’okufulumya antibody mu bwangu ezimala okulwanyisa ekizibu ky’obulwadde obuli mu nsi yonna.
Noolwekyo, ekiba kisoboka kwe kwawula B cells okuva mu bantu abawonye ne tumanya koodi z’endagabutonde za antibody ezirwanyisa obulwadde oba okukebera ne tulaba antibody ezirwanyisa obulwadde puloteni z’akawuka enkulu.
Mu ngeri eno, tusobola okwongera ku bungi bwa antibody ezikolebwa.
TCM akozeseddwa okujjanjaba endwadde eziwerako mu China okumala enkumi n’enkumi z’emyaka.
Wabula, obukozi bwe bwesigama nnyo ku kugatta ebirungo eby’enjawulo mu ddagala ebikyukakyuka okusinziira ku kiba kizuuliddwa ku bulwadde okusinziira ku binnyonnyola (theory) TCM.
Ebirungo ebikola ebisinga tebimanyiddwa oba tebitegeerekeka bulungi olw’okuba nga kizibu okukenenulamu ebirungo ebyo ne bikakasibwa oba ebibikola.
Mu kiseera kino, olw’okuba nga tewali ddagala limanyiddwa kujjanjaba COVID-19, TCM lye limu ku ddagala erisinga okukozesebwa mu kujjanjaba abalwadde abalina obubonero obutonotono oba abo abawonye emitendera emingiko.
Okugeza, kapiso za Shu Feng Jie Du n’eza Lian Hua Qing Wen zaazuulibwa nga zikola bulungi ku kujjanjaba COVID-19.
Abalwadde bangi baawona COVID-19 province eziwerako mu China nga bajjanjabwa ne TCM mu bitundu 87% eby’abalwadde, omuli Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%), ne Hunan (50%), so nga mu Hubei province, eyakozesa TCM mu bitundu nga 30% byokka eby’abalwadde bwa COVID-19, okuwona gye kwasinga okubeera wansi (13%).
Wabula, okugeraageranya kuno si kwa bwenkanya olw’okuba nga waliwo ensonga endala nnyingi ng’omuwendo n’embeera y’abalwadde ezirina okussibwa mu kwekaliriza.
Mu Gwokubiri nga 18, 2020, Boli Zhang ne bakozi banne baafulumya ebyava mu kunoonyereza nga bageraageranya okujjanjabisa eddagala ly’ekizungu (western medicine) lyokka n’obujjanjabi obugattiddwa nga mulimu eddagala ly’ekizingu ne TCM.
Baakizuula nti ebiseera ebyetaagisa ebbugumu ly’omubiri okuddawo, obubonero okubula, n’okubeera ku kitanda byali bimpi nnyo mu kibinja eky’eddagala ly’ekizungu+TCM okusinga mu kibinja eky’eddagala ly’ekizungu lyokka.
Ekisinga okusanyusa, okusajjuka kw’obubonero (okuva ku kubeera obutonotono okufuuka obw’amaanyi ennyo) kwali kutono nnyo mu kibinja ky’eddagala ly’ekizungu+TCM okusinga mu kibinja ky’eddagala ly’ekizungu lyokka (7.4% bw’ogeraageranya ne 46.2%) ate era okufa kwali kutono mu kibinja ky’eddagala ly’ekizungu+TCM okusinga mu kibinja ky’eddagala ly’ekizungu lyokka (8.8% bw’ogeraageranya ne 39%).
Weewaawo guli bwegutyo, obukozi n’obulungi bwa TCM bukyetaaga okugezesa okulimu ensonga endala nga kukolebwa ku balwadde abasingako ne mu bifo ebisingako.
Era kyandinyumye nnyo okunnyonnyola ebikolebwa n’okutangaaza ku bikolo bya TCM ebijjanjaba oba ebibikola bwe kiba nga kisoboka.
Abalwadde abateeberezebwa oba abakakasiddwa okuba ne COVID-19 batera okuba n’okutya okungi okw’obulwadde buno obusiigibwa ennyo era obw’obulabe, n’abantu abateereddwa mu kalantiini nabo bafuna ekiwuubaalo, ettuulawamu, n’obusungu.
Okwongereza ku ekyo, obubonero bw’obulwadde okugeza omusujja, okubulwa omukka mu mubiri, n’okukolola awamu n’obuzibu obw’amaanyi obuva ku ddagala ng’okubulwa otulo ebireetebwa corticosteroids bisobola okwongera ku kweraliikirira n’okutabuka omutwe.
Mu biseera ebyasooka nga SARS yaakabalukawo, waaliwo endwadde nnyingi ezeekuusa ku mutwe omuli okwennyika ebirowoozo okutatadde, okweraliikirira, okutya ennyo, okupakunkana, okulowooza ebitaliiyo, obutassaayo mwoyo, n’okwetta.
Okunoonya abantu ababaddeko n’omulwadde n’okubassa mu kalantiini okw’obuwaze, ng’ekimu ku bikolebwa mu kulwanyisa COVID-19, kisobola okuleetera abantu okweyongera okweraliikirira n’okuwulira ng’abalina omusango olw’ebiva mu bulwadde buno obusiigibwa, kalantiini, n’okusosolwa kw’ab’omu maka gaabwe ne mikwano gyabwe.
Noolwekyo, obulabirizi mu mbeera z’emitwe busaanye okuweebwa abalwadde ba COVID-19, abateeberezebwa okuba naye, n’abantu ababeera nabo awamu n’abantu bonna ababwetaaga.
Obuyambi mu by’ebirowoozo bulina okubaamu okuteekawo tiimu z’abasawo mu bintu eby’enjawulo ebikwata ku mitwe, okutegeeza abantu mu budde era mu ngeri etegeerekeka ku bikwata ku SARS-CoV-2 n’enteekateeka z’okujjanjaba n’okukozesa ebyuma bikalimagezi okwewala okusembereragana.
Eddagala erigema lya mugaso mu kutaataaganya entambula y’akawuka okuva mu nsolo mwe kabeera ne mu bantu abalwadde okudda mu bintu ebiyinza okukatambuza era litera okukolera awamu n’eddagala erijjanjaba obuwuka mu kulwanyisa obulwadde obuleetebwa obuwuka obuba bubaluseewo.
Waliwo kaweefube akoleddwa okukulaakulanya eddagala erigema eryesigamiziddwa ku S protein okukola antibody empangaazi era ez’amaanyi ezisannyalaza ne/oba obusibage obulwanyisa SARS-CoV.
Eddagala erigema erikolebwa mu buwuka bwennyini lyekalirizibwa mu nsolo ku SARS.
Wabula, enkola y’eddagala erigema lino mu bantu abakadde ne mu lethal-challenge models n’enkola yaalyo mu kutangira obuwuka mu nsolo erina okumala okukakasibwa nga terinnakolwako kunoonyereza kwa kisawo.
Kino kirabika okuba nga kiri bwekityo kubanga SARS yafa emyaka 17 egiyise era tewali yali azzeemu kumufuna okuva olwo.
Okwawukanako n’ekyo, waliwo abantu abatera okufuna MERS mu Middle East era n’asaasaanira ebitundu ebirala olw’ensolo z’abeeramu ezibeera mu bitundu ebyo.
Eddagala erigema MERS lyakolebwa nga bakozesa akawuka akanafuyiziddwa, DNA plasmids, viral vectors, nanoparticles, obutaffaali obwefaanaanyiriza akawuka ne recombinant protein subunits era lyagezesebwa mu nsolo.
Okukulaakulanya eddagala erigema SARS-CoV-2 mu bantu ab’obusibage obutono kyetaagibwa nnyo era mu bwangu okusobola okulwanyisa ekizibu ekiriwo.
Wabula, kisoomooza okuvvuunuka obuzibu buno olw’ekiseera ekinene (emyezi nga 18) ekyetaagisa okulikulaakulanya n’okukyukakyuka kwa CoVs.
Olw’okubeera obulwadde obupya, enneeyisa ya COVID-19 enzijuvu yaakatandika okweyoleka mu nkumi z’abalwadde.
Mu mbeera ezisinga, abalwadde basobola okuwona empolampola awatali kusigala na bubonero.
Wabula, nga bweguli ku SARS ne MERS, abalwadde ba COVID-19 batera okulwala ennyo n’okufa.
Noolwekyo, okuteebereza obuzibu obuyinza okuleetebwa obulwadde kikulu eri ebitongole byobujjanjabi okuteekateeka obuweereza bwabwe, naddala mu bifo ebitatuukamu bulungi buweereza.
Nga twesigama ku kunoonyereza kw’ekisawo okwakakolebwa, ensonga zino ziyinza okuba nga zeekuusa ku buzibu obuyinza okutuuka ku balwadde ba COVID-19 (Omweso ​(Omweso33):
Obukulu: Obukulu ye nsonga eyasinga obukulu mu kuteebereza obuzibu obuyinza okutuuka ku balwadde ba SARS, era nga kino kituufu ne ku COVID-19.
COVID-19 yasinga kukwata bantu ba myaka 30-65 ng’ebitundu 47.7% eby’abalwadde abo basussa emyaka 50 mu kunoonyereza ku bantu 8,866 nga bwe kiragiddwa waggulu.
Abalwadde abaali beetaaga obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi okusinga baalina endwadde endala ze baasangibwa nazo era baali bakulu nnyo okusinga abo abataalina (ku myaka nga 66 bw’ogeraageranya ne 51), nga kitegeeza nti obukulu nsonga nkulu mu kuteebereza obuzibu obuyinza okutuuka ku balwadde ba COVID-19.
Ekikula: SARS-CoV-2 akutte abasajja bangi okusinga abakazi (0.31/100,000 bw’ogeraageranya ne 0.27/100,000), nga bwe kiragiddwa waggulu.
Endwadde n’obuzibu obulala: Abalwadde ba COVID-19 abeetaaga obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi baba n’emikisa mingi egy’okufuna obuvune ku mutima (acute cardiac injury) ne arrhythmia.
Obuzibu ku mutima era ye yali ensonga enkulu eyaviirangako okufa mu balwadde ba SARS.
Kyazuulibwa nti SARS-CoV-2 era asobola okwekwata ku ACE2-positive cholangiocytes, ekiyinza okuleetera ekibumba obutakola bulungi mu balwadde ba COVID-19.
Kikulu okumanya nti obukulu n’endwadde endala bikwatagana nnyo era buli kimu kiyinza okubaako engeri gye kikosa ekirala.
Ebizuulibwa mu mageserezo ebitali bya bulijjo: Omuwendo gwa C-reactive protein (CRP) mu musaayi gulaga obunyiinyiitivu bw’okuzimba oba okukosebwa kw’ennyama era eragiddwa ng’obuzibu obuyinza okutuuka ku balwadde, ekibaawo ng’eddagala likola, n’okuwonera ddala.
Akakwate wakati w’omuwendo gwa CRP n’obunyiinyiitivu n’obuzibu obuyinza okutuuka ku balwadde ba COVID-19 nako koogeddwako.
Ekirala, okweyongera kwa lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), ne creatine kinase (CK) nabyo biyinza okuyamba mu kuteebereza ebiyinza okuvaamu.
Enzyme zino zeeyolekera mu bungi mu bitundu eby’enjawulo, naddala mu mutima n’ekibumba, era zifulumizibwa nga waliwo ekikoseddwa.
Noolwekyo, ze zitera okulaga obuzibu obuba butuuse ku mutima oba ekibumba.
Obubonero bw’ekisawo obukulu: Okukuba ekifaananyi mu kifuba n’okulondoola obubonero okumala ekiseera bisaana okukolebwa awamu n’ensonga endala okusobola okuteebereza obuzibu obunaaleetebwa COVID-19.
Okukozesa steroids: Nga bwe kyannyonnyoddwa waggulu, steroids zikkakkanya ku busibage era zikozesebwa nnyo mu kuyamba ku kujjanjaba obulwadde obusiigibwa okukendeeza ku bunyiinyiitivu bw’obuvune bw’okuzimba.
Olw’okuba nga doozi ennene eya corticosteroids yakozesebwa nnyo mu balwadde ba SARS abayi, abalwadde abaawona bangi baafuna okusannyalala kw’amagumba (avascular osteonecrosis) ne basigala n’obulemu okumala ekiseera ekiwanvu n’omutindo gw’obulamu omubi.
Noolwekyo, bwe kiba kyetaagisizza, steroids zisaanye okukozesebwa mu doozi entono era okumala ekiseera kitono mu balwadde ba COVID-19.
Obuzibu bw’obwongo: Nga kinnyonnyoddwa waggulu, mu kiseera ky’okubalukawo kwa COVID-19 abalwadde bangi banyigiriziddwa nnyo mu bwongo olw’okumala ebiseera bingi mu kalantiini n’okuba nga tebamanyi kiddirira era balabye ab’eŋŋanda zaabwe ne balwadde bannaabwe nga bafa.
Abalwadde bano bateekwa okubudaabudibwa n’okuwagirwa okumala ekiseera okubayamba okuwona okunyigirizibwa kuno n’okudda mu bulamu obwa bulijjo.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku bikwata ku bantu, COVID-19 alabika okuba n’obubonero obwawukana ne SARS.
Ng’oggyeeko eky’okuba nti yeekubisiza mu kitundu ky’omussizo ekya wansi, SARS-CoV-2 asobola bulungi okwekubisiza mu kitundu ky’omussizo ekya waggulu n’ataleetawo bubonero obutono oba n’ataleetawobubonero mu biseera ebisooka nga yaakakwata omuntu, nga kino kifaanana ne ku buwuka bwa CoVs obulala obuleeta ssenyiga owa bulijjo.
Noolwekyo, abalwadde mu kiseera ekisooka oba mu kiseera ng’akawuka tekanneeyoleka basobola okufulumya omuwendo gw’akawuka mungi mu mirimu gyabwe egya buli lunaku, ne kizibuwaza omulimu gw’okulwanyisa obulwadde.
Wabula, okusaasaanya SARS-CoV kwalowoozebwa nti kwalingawo ng’abalwadde bayi nnyo, so ng’okusaasaana tekwali kungi mu biseera ebisooka.
Noolwekyo, ekizibu kya COVID-19 ekiriwo mu kiseera kino kya maanyi nnyo era kizibu okulwanyisa okusinga ku kizibu kya SARS.
Kaweefube wa maanyi agenda mu maaso mu China omuli okuggalawo Wuhan n’ebibuga ebyetooloddewo n’okussa mu kalantiini kyenkana abantu bonna nga balowooza okutaataaganya ensaasaana ya SARS-CoV-2.
Newankubadde ebikolwa bino bibadde bikosa nnyo ebyenfuna n’ebitongole by’eggwanga ebirala, omuwendo gw’abalwadde abapya gukendeera, ekiraga nti ekizibu kigenda kikendeera.
Okuteebereza okusinga obulungi kuli nti ekizibu kijja kuggwaawo mu Gwokusatu era nti okukendeera kujja kumala emyezi 3-4.
Wabula, abakugu abalala tebalina ssuubi lino.
Paul Hunter, ne banne, baateebereza nti COVID-19, gy’alabika ng’asiigibwa nnyo okusinga SARS, tajja kuggwaawo mu 2020.
Ira Longini, ne banne, baazuula engeri y’okuteebereza ebinaava mu kizibu ky’obulwadde era ne bateebereza nti SARS-CoV-2 ayinza okukwata ebitundu bibiri-byakusatu eby’abantu b’omu nsi yonna.
Ekibinja ky’Abakanada kyalaga nti SARS-CoV-2 yazuulibwa mu balwadde abaawona ne bava mu ddwaliro wiiki 2 emabega, ekiraga nti akawuka kano akaakazuulibwa kayinza okuba nga kabeera kakomawo nga ssenyiga.
Wabula, obubonero obuzzaamu essuubi bulabiseeko e China okusinziira ku muwendo gw’abalwadde abapya okukendeera, ekiraga nti enkola eziriwo ziyinza okuba nga zikola.
Mu kusooka Ebola yateeberezebwa nti yali wa kukwata abantu abawera akakadde kamu era atte abantu emitwalo ataano.
Wabula, olw’okugoberera obulungi enkola ya kalantiini n’okweyawula, obulwadde buno busobodde okulwanyisibwa.
Kisoboka, nga bwe kyali ku SARS-CoV, nti akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 kayinza okunafuwa mu ngeri gye kakwatamu abantu n’oluvannyuma ne kaggwaawo oba ne kanafuwa ne kabeerawo bulungi n’abantu.
Okugeraageranya obulwadde bwa COVID-19 n’obwa SARS n’obwa MERS kulagiddwa wammanga (Ekifaananyi. ​(Ekifaananyi.55).
SARS-CoV-2 asiigibwa nnyo okuyita mu kukolola oba okwasimula, era oboolyawo n’okuyita mu kukwata ku bintu ebiriko akawuka.
Akawuka kano era kaazuulibwa ne mu bubi, ekiraga nti kiyinza era okusoboka okusiiga akawuka kano ng’omuntu alidde obubi.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa gye buvuddeko katono ku balwadde 138 kwalaga nti abalwadde ebitundu 41% akawuka baakaggya mu malwaliro, omuli n’abalwadde 17 abaasangibwa n’endwadde endala n’abasawo 40.
Noolwekyo, walina okubaawo okwegendereza kungi okusobola okutaasa abantu, naddala abasawo, ababudaabuzi, ab’awaka, ab’oku mirimu, n’abantu ababa bayimiridde obuyimirizi okumpi n’abalwadde oba abantu abalina akawuka.
Enkola esooka eyinza okukozesebwa okukendeeza ku buzibu bw’okufuna akawuka kwe kwambala obukookolo ku maaso (face masks); okukozesa obukookolo obukozesebwa mu kulongoosa n’obwa N95 (series # 1860s) bwombi kiyamba okukendeeza ensaasaana y’obuwuka.
Obuukokolo obukozesebwa mu kulongoosa buziyiza ebintu ng’amalusu g’omuntu ayinza okuba n’akawuka okutambulira mu mpewo oba okusigala ku bintu ebirala, we biyinza okutuusizibwa ku bantu abalala.
Wabula, obukookolo bwa N95 (series # 1860s) bwe bwokka obusobola okulemesa omuntu okuyingiza obuwuka obwenkana 10 ku 80 nm, ng’obuwuka ebitundu 5% byokka bye bisobola okuyitiramu ddala; SARS-CoV-2 yenkana ne SARS-CoV mu bunene era bwonna bwenkana 85 nm.
Olw’okuba ng’akawuka kasobola okuyita ne mu bukookolo obukozesebwa ku kulongoosa obutaano nga bussiddwa wamu, abasawo abasemberera abalwadde bateekwa okwambala obukookolo bwa N95 (series # 1860s) so si obwo obukozesebwa mu kulongoosa.
Okwongereza ku bukookolo, abasawo balina okwambala amaganduula okwongera okukendeeza ku kusemberera obuwuka.
Obuwuka era busobola okukwata omuntu nga buyita mu maaso.
Mu Janwali nga 22, 2020, omusawo yafuna SARS-CoV-2 newankubadde nga yali ayambadde akakookolo ka N95; akawuka kayinza okuba nga kaayingira omubiri gwe nga kayita mu maaso ge agaali gazimbye.
Noolwekyo, abasawo era basaanye okwambala ebibikka amaaso ebitangaala oba ebigaalubindi nga bakola ku balwadde.
Ku bantu aba bulijjo mu bitundu ebirimu oba ebiyinza okubaamu obuwuka, kyandibadde kirungi buli muntu okunaaba mu ngalo ne ssabbuuni emirundi mingi okusinga ku bwe bakola bulijjo, okugezaako okubeera munda nga beekuumira mu kalantiini n’okukendeeza ku nsisinkano n’abantu abayinza okuba n’akawuka.
Ebbanga erya fuuti essatu litwalibwa okuba nga limala omuntu okwesuula omulwadde.
Ebikolwa bino nkola nnungi mu kukendeeza ku mikisa gy’okufuna awamu n’okusaasaanya akawuka.
Newankubadde nga SARS-CoV-2 yajja ng’akawuka akapya mu bantu, engeri gye kafaanana ennyo SARS-CoV nga bwe kyalagibwa nga 7 Janwali 2020 kyandibadde kiwa China essomo lya maanyi okusinziira ku by’ejjukira ku kubalukawo kwa SARS mu 2003.
Wabula, okutuukira ddala nga 19 Janwali 2020 omukulu wa Center of Disease Control mu Wuhan yali akyagumya bannansi ng’agamba nti akawuka kano akapya kaali tekasiigibwa nnyo era nga tekatambula nnyo kuva ku muntu kudda ku mulala era nti obulwadde buno tebwali buzibu kwewalwa na kulwanyisa.
Obubaka buno bwakkakkanya nnyo amaloboozi g’abantu, naddala eggwanga bwe lyali lyetegekera ebikujjuko by’omu Spring, era ekiseera ekituufu eky’okulwanyisizaamu obulwadde ne kifiirwa nga bukyali butono nnyo mu Wuhan.
Ebitongole ebirwanyisa obulwadde mu China biyinza okukozesa essomo lino lye byafuna okukola obulungiko gye bujja.
Okugeza, ebitongole bino byandibadde (1) byongera okwegendereza nga biriko bye bitegeeza abantu kubanga buli kigambo kirina kye kitegeeza eri bannansi era kisobola okukyusa endaba n’ensalawo yaabwe; (2) byongera okufaayo n’okwanukula obubaka obutali bwa bulijjo okuva mu malwaliro okusinga okulinda alipoota entongole okuva eri basawo oba abakungu; (3) byongeramu amaanyi okusobola okulwanyisa endwadde eyinza okufuuka ey’omutawaana nga yaakabalukawo mu ky’okugezaako okukkakkanya abantu; era (4) buli kiseera okukola okwegezaamu nga bongera okumanyisa abantu ku bulwadde obw’omutawaana n’okugezesa awamu n’okulongoosa engeri abantu b’omu bitundu gye bakwatamu ensonga zonna mu buli biseera ebigere.
Obulwadde bwa COVID-19 obuleetebwa akawuka akapya aka SARS-CoV-2 bwatandika ku nkomerero ya Deesemba 2019.
Mu kiseera ekitaweza myezi ebiri, busaasaanidde China yonna n’ensi endala kyenkana 50 mu nsi yonna mu kiseera ky’okuwandiika bino.
Olw’okuba ng’akawuka kafaanana nnyo ne SARS-CoV nga n’obubonero bufaanana wakati wa COVID-19 ne SARS, obulwadde bwa COVID-19 bulowoozesezza abantu nti SARS y’akomyewo.
Wabula, zino ze njawulo ennene wakati wa COVID-19 ne SARS, nga zino za mugaso mu kusobola okulwanyisa obulwadde buno n’okujjanjaba abalwadde.
COVID-19 bukwata nnyo abantu abakuze mu myaka okusinga abavubuka n’abasajja okusinga abakazi, era n’obunyiinyiitivu n’okufa bingiko mu bakadde okusinga mu bavubuka.
SARS atta nnyo okusinga COVID-19 (10.91% bw’ogeraageranya ne 1.44%).
Abalwadde ba COVID-19 basiiga akawuka ne bwe baba nga tebalaze bubonero so ng’abalwadde ba SARS basiiga bwe baba nga balwadde nnyo, nga kino kikifuula kizibu nnyo okulwanyisa okusaasaana kwa COVID-19 okusinga SARS.
Kino kye kimu ku binnyonnyola lwaki SARS-CoV-2 atambula mangu nnyo era n’atuuka wala nnyo okusinga SARS-CoV.
Okukebera SARS-CoV-2 ne RNA kusobola okulaga nti omuntu tamulina mu balwadde ba COVID-19 abamu.
Ekirala, abalwadde abawonye basobola okuddamu okuba n’akawuka.
Ebizuuliddwa bino byongera nnyo emikisa gy’akawuka okusaasaana.
Newankubadde ng’okunoonyereza kuno kukoleddwa mu bwangu ku COVID-19, ensonga enkulu nnyingi tezinnaba kumulungulwa, nga zino:
SARS-CoV-2 yava wa?
Newankubadde waliwo okufaanana kwa bitundu 96% mu ndagabutonde wakati wa SARS-CoV-2 n’obuwuka bwa Cov obw’omu buwundo bubiri obufaanana SARS, era tetunnasobola kusalawo nti SARS-CoV-2 ava mu buwundo.
Nsolo ki eyali wakati awo eyaggya akawuka mu nsolo gye kaasookeramu, ka tugambe obuwundo, okukaleeta mu bantu?
Awatali kumanya kya kuddamu ku #1 ne 2, tetusobola kuziyiza bulungi kusaasaana, era obulwadde busobola okuddamu okubalukawo obudde bwonna.
Newankubadde enkola za molecular modeling ne biochemical assays ziraze nti SARS-CoV-2 yeekwata ku ACE2, akawuka kayingira katya mu butaffaali bw’omu mussizo (airway cells) ne kaleeta obulwadde?
Akawuka era keekwata ku butaffaali obulina ACE2 mu bitundu by’omubiri ebirala?
Awatali byakuddamu bitangaavu ku bibuuzo bino, tetusobola kukebera mangu era mu butuufu n’okufuna eddagala ettuufu.
Obulwadde bunaamala kiseera ki?
Endagabutonde y’akawuka ekyuka etya nga kasaasaanyizibwa mu bantu?
Kanaafuuka kizibu kya nsi yonna, kanaggwaawo nga SARS oba kanaakomangawo buli luvannyuma lwa kiseera nga ssenyiga?
Kikulu naye nga kiyinza okutwala obudde okunoonya ebyokuddamu ku bibuuzo ebyo waggulu n’ebirala bingi.
Wabula, ne bwe kineetaaga kukola ki, tetulina kya kukola kirala wabula okukomya obulwadde amangu ddala nga bwe kisoboka tuddemu okubeera mu bulamu obwa bulijjo.
Obuwuka bwa corona okusibuka mu nsolo
Enkyukakyuka mu ndagabutonde zireetedde obuwuka bwa corona (CoVs) n’ensolo mwe bubeera byombi okukyuka, nga mwemuli n’abantu, okumala enkumi n’enkumi z’emyaka.
Nga 2003 tannatuuka, obuwuka bwa CoVs obw’omu bantu (HCoVs) bwa mirundi ebiri bwali bumanyiddwa okuleeta obulwadde obutali bwa maanyi, okugeza ssenyiga owa bulijjo.
Okubalukawo kwa severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) ne Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS) bukyusizza ebintu ne bwoleka engeri akawuka ka HCoV gye kayinza okuba ak’omutawaana era n’okutta.
Okubalukawo kwa SARS-CoV-2 mu masekkati ga China ku nkomerero ya 2019 kakomezzaawo obuwuka bwa CoVs mu ddiiro era ne katwewuunyisa n’engeri gye kasiigibwa ku misinde emingi so nga tekalwaza nnyo bw’okageraageranya ne kannaako ka SARS-CoV.
Akawuka ka HCoV kaba kasibuka mu nsolo era okutegeera ensibuko y’obuwuka bwa HCoVs ey’omu nsolo kiba kituyamba nnnyo.
Obuwuka bwa HCoVs obusinga busibuka mu buwundo era nga bwo tebubulwaza.
Ensolo obumu ku buwuka bwa HCoVs mwe busooka okwewogoma nga tebunnajja mu bantu nazo zimanyiddwa.
Okumanya ensolo ezisiiga abantu obuwuka kiyamba nnyo mu kulwanyisa endwadde z’abantu.
Okwekenneenya enkolagana y’ensolo ezibeeramu CoV nakyo kiyinza okuyamba mu kumanya obulabe bwa CoV mu bantu.
Mu kwekenneenya kuno, tulaga mu bufunze ebyakazuulibwa ku HCoVs omusanvu, ng’essira tuliteeka ku byafaayo by’okuzuulwa kwabwo awamu n’ensibuko yaabwo mu nsolo n’ensaasaana yaabwo wakati w’ensolo ez’enjawulo.
Ekikulu mu kino, tulaga ebifaanana n’ebyawuka wakati w’obuwuka bwa HCoVs obw’enjawulo nga tutunuulira enkyukakyuka y’akawuka (virus evolution) n’okuwaanyisiganya endagabutonde (genome recombination).
Obulwadde obuliwo olwaleero obwa CoV disease 2019 (COVID-19) bwe bwogerwako mu mbeera eno.
Ekirala, ebisobozesa ensolo ezirimu akawuka okukyuka n’okukyukakyuka kw’akawuka kye kutegeeza ku bukambwe bw’obulwadde nabyo byogerwako.
Obuwuka bwa corona (CoVs) bugwa mu kika kya Coronaviridae, nga kino kirimu ekibinja ky’obuwuka obwetooloddwa olububi, buli ‘positive-sensed’, era nga bulina RNA ya luguwa lumu.
Obuwuka buno nga bulina genome esinga obunene eya 26 ku 32 kilobases mu buwuka bwa RNA bwatuumibwa “CoVs” olw’ekikula kyabwo ekifaanana engule bwe bulabirwa mu kyuma ekizimbulukusa.
Mu buzimbe, obuwuka bwa CoVs bulina genome ezitakutuddwakutuddwa era nga ziri wamu.
Ebitundu nga bibiri byakusatu ebya genome zirimu fuleemu bbiri ennene ezikwatagana (ORF1a ne ORF1b), nga zino zivaamu pp1a ne pp1ab replicase polyproteins.
Polyproteins nazo oluvannyuma zikolwako ne zivaamu puloteni 16 ezitalina buzimbe (non-structural proteins), eziyitibwa nsp1~16.
Ekitundu kya genome ekisigadde kibaamu ORFs ku puloteni ez’obuzimbe (structural proteins), omuli spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) ne nucleoprotein (N).
Puloteni ez’ennyiriri (lineage-specific accessory proteins) nnyingi nazo zissibwa mu nnyiriri ez’enjawulo eza CoVs.
Okusinziira ku njawulo mu busengeke bwa puloteni, obuwuka bwa CoVs bussibwa mu bika ebinene bina (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV ne delta-CoV), nga mu byo ekika kya beta-CoV kye kirimu obuwuka bwa HCoVs obusinga obungi era nga kigabanyizibwamu ennyiriri (lineages) nnya (A, B, C ne D).
Ebyazuulibwa mu kubinjawaza biraga nti obuwundo n’ebimese ye nsibuko y’obuwuka bwa alpha-CoVs ne beta-CoVs esinga, so ng’ebinyonyi ye nsibuko ya gamma-CoVs ne delta-CoVs esiinga.
Okumala enkumi n’enkumi z’emyaka, CoVs bubaddenga bukutula ne buva mu bisolo mwe busibuka era obumu bufuuse ensibuko y’obulwadde bw’abantu.
Okutuuka olwaleero, human CoVs (HCoVs) musanvu bwe bumanyiddwa.
Mu buno HCoV-229E ne HCoV-NL63 bwa kika kya alpha-CoVs.
Obulala bu beta-CoVs obutaano mulimu HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus (SARS-CoV), Middle East respiratory syndrome coronavirus (MERS-CoV) ne SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 ne HCoV-NL63 butera okuleeta obulwadde butonotono, nga ssennyiga owa bulijjo ne/oba ekiddukano.
Okwawukanako n’ekyo, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV ne SARS-CoV-2 akaakazuulibwa bulwaza nnyo, nga bukosa nnyo ekitundu ky’omussizo ekya wansi mu balwadde abasingako obungi era waliwo emikisa mingi egy’okufuna obuzibu mu kkubo ly’omukka ogussibwa (acute respiratory distress syndrome, ARDS) n’okukosebwa ebweru w’amawuggwe (extrapulmonary manifestations).
Ekika kya HCoV-229E ekyasooka, B814, kyazuulibwa mu minyira gy’abalwadde abalina ssenyiga owa bulijjo mu masekkati g’egya 1960.
Okuva olwo, waliwo ebizuuliddwa ebirala okuyita mu kunoonyereza okw’amaanyi ku HCoV-229E ne HCoV-OC43, nga bwonna buleeta obulwadde obuwona amangu (self-limiting symptoms).
Mu butuufu, kyali kikkiriziddwa nnyo nti okufuna obuwuka bwa HCoVs okutwaliza awamu si kya bulabe okutuusa SARS bwe yabalukawo.
SARS yabalukawo mu 2003 era ke kamu ku bukyasinze okuba obw’omutawaana mu byafaayo ebyakayita, nga kaakwata abantu abasoba mu 8,000 ng’ebitundu 10% baasuubirwanga okufa.
Nga wayise emyaka kkumi, Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS) yaleeta obulwadde obwalwawo mu Kyondo kya Buwalabu nga bwe kasaasaanirako n’ebitundu by’ensi ebirala.
2019 novel HCoV (2019-nCoV), oluvannyuma akaatuumibwa SARS-CoV-2, ke kaleeta obulwadde obuliwo kati obwa coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19), obwakatta abantu abasukka mu 3,120 n’okukwata abantu abasukka mu 91,000 olwa 3 Ogwokusatu 2020 we lwatuukira.
Akagombe kabadde kavuga era ensi erina okwetegekera ekizibu ky’obulwadde bw’ensi yonna obwa SARS-CoV-2.
Obuwuka bwa HCoVs bwonna omusanvu busibuka mu buwundo, emmese oba ensolo ezirundwa awaka.
Obujulizi bungi obukakasa nti HCoVs bwonna busibuka mu buwundo, nga muno obuwuka bubeeramu bulungi era nga tebubulwaza naye nga bulina endagabutonde za njawulo nnyo.
Obulwadde bwa COVID-19 buleeseewo okusoomoozebwa kwa maanyi mu byobujjanjabi, ebyekinnasaayansi, embeera z’abantu n’eneeyisa eri China n’ensi yonna.
Okulondoola ensibuko ya HCoVs mu nsolo kitusobozesa okutegeera ebyafaayo, ebisindiikiriza n’ebiremesa obuwuka okuva mu bisolo ebimu okudda mu birala.
Kino era kiyinza okuluŋŋamya n’okwanguya omulimu gw’okunoonya ensolo etambuza SARS-CoV-2 okuva mu nsolo mwe yasooka okubeera okumutuusa mu bantu, nga kino kirina kye kitegeeza kya maanyi mu kwewala embeera okusajjuka gye bujja.
Mu kwekenneenya kuno tulaga ebikwata ku nsibuko za HCoVs mu bisolo, okusaasaana kwabwo mu bisolo eby’enjawulo n’obulwadde bwe buleeta.
Okusingira ddala, tulaga era ne tukubaganya ebirowoozo ku nsonga ey’awamu nti obuwuka obwa HCoVs mwe buva tebulina mutawaana mu nsolo gye buva naye bufuuka bwa bulabe bwe busala okudda mu kisolo ekirala.
Era twekenneenya engeri akawuka ka HCoV gye kakyukakyukamu nga buli lwe keeyongera okusiigibwa ate katera okukendeera mu bulabe bw’okulwaza.
Ebiva mu kubalukawo kwa SARS-CoV-2 aliwo kati nabyo byogerwako mu mbeera eno.
Obuwuka bwa CoVs obw’omu nsolo bubadde bumanyiddwa okuva mu gya 1930 nga giggwaako.
Ng’akawuka ka HCoV-229E ak’ekika B814 tekannayawulwa mu minyira gy’abalwadde abaali bafunye ssenyiga owa bulijjo, obuwuka bwa CoVs bungi bwali bwawuddwa mu nsolo nnyingi endwadde, omuli ssekkoko, emmese, ente, embizzi, kkapa n’embwa.
Mu byasa ebiyise, obuwuka bwa HCoVs musanvu bwe buzuuliddwa.
Ebyafaayo mu bufunze eby’okuzuulibwa kwa HCoV mu nziriŋŋana yaabyo (Omweso ​1) bijja kuba ne kye bituyigiriza.
Ekika kya HCoV-229E ekyasooka kyasangibwa mu mussizo gw’abalwadde abaalina obuvune mu kitundu ky’omussizo ekya waggulu mu mwaka 1966, era ne kazuulibwa nga kakulira mu nnyiriri z’obutaffaali bw’amawuggwe obwa WI-38.
Abalwadde abaalina HCoV-229E baalina obubonero bwa ssenyiga owa bulijjo, omuli okulumwa omutwe, okwasimula, ekimenyoomenyo n’amabwa mu bulago, n’omusujja n’okukolola mu balwadde ebitundu 10~20%.
Oluvannyuma mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 kaazuulibwa mu nkola ya organ culture n’oluvannyuma mu nkola ya serial passage mu bwongo bw’emmese eziyonka.
Obubonero bw’ekisawo obuleetebwa akawuka ka HCoV-OC43 bulabika okufaanana n’obwo obwa HCoV-229E, ng’obubonero bwabwo tebwawukana na buwuka bw’omu mussizo bulala nga ng’obuwuka bwa influenza A ne rhinoviruses.
HCoV-229E ne HCoV-OC43 bwombi butambula mu nsi wonna, era butera kutambula nnyo mu biseera by’obutiti mu mbeera y’obudde etali nkaalaamufu.
Okutwaliza awamu, obuwuka buno bwombi bumala ekiseera ekitaweza wiiki okulaga obubonero, era nga kino kigobererwa ekiseera ky’obulwadde kya wiiki nga 2.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza ku bantu abeewaayo, abantu abalamu abassibwamu HCoV-229E baafuna ssenyiga wa bulijjo omutonotono.
Abalwadde batono abaalina obusibage obutono be baafuna obuvune obw’amaanyi mu kitundu ky’omussizo ekya wansi.
SARS, ng’era amanyiddwa nga “atypical pneumonia”, ye yasooka okuwandiikibwako obulungi mu bulwadde obusaasaanira ensi yonna nga buleetebwa HCoV mu byafaayo by’abantu era nga buleetebwa SARS-CoV, akawuka ak’ekika kya HCoV akookusatu okuzuulibwa.
Omulwadde wa SARS eyasooka yali ku nkomerero ya 2002 mu Guangdong Province mu China.
Obulwadde bwa SARS bwakwata abantu 8,096 abaamanyika era ne butta abantu 774, nga bwasaanira amawanga ne ssemazinga nnyingi.
Ng’oggyeeko ebibusaasaanya ebisinga okumanyibwa, kyateeberezebwa nti buli mulwadde yali asobola okusiiga abantu abalala babiri, ng’obubonero bulabikira mu nnaku 4 ku 7 ng’entikko y’omuwendo gw’obuwuka mu muntu (peak of viral load) ebeerawo ku lunaku olwa 10 olw’obulwadde.
Abalwadde abalina SARS-CoV mu kusooka balumwa ennyingo, omutwe, omusujja, ekimenyoomenyo n’ekitengo, ne bigobererwa okukaluubirirwa mu kussa, okukolola n’oluvannyuma okufuna amazzi mu mawuggwe.
Lymphopenia, deranged liver function tests, ne elevated creatine kinase bwe bumu ku buzibu bwa SARS obulabirwa mu kukebera kw’omu ggezeserezo.
Obuzibu ku mawuggwe (diffuse alveolar damage), okuzaala obutaffaali (epithelial cell proliferation) n’okweyongera mu butaffaali obuyibwa macrophages nabyo birabwa mu balwadde ba SARS.
Ebitundu nga 20-30% eby’abalwadde baba beetaaga obujjanjabi obw’amaanyi n’ebyuma by’amasannyalaze ebiyamba mu kussa.
Ng’oggyeeko ekitundu ky’omussizo ekya wansi, ebitundu bingi omuli omumenyoomenyero gw’emmere (gastrointestinal tract), ekibumba n’ensigo nabyo bisobola okufuna obuvune mu mbeera zino ez’amaanyi, nga butera okugendera awamu ne cytokine storm, nga buyinza okuviirako okufa naddala mu balwadde abalina obusibage obutono.
Akawuka kano kaasooka kuzuulibwa mu kanyama akaggyibwa mu mawuggwe g’owooluganda lw’omulwadde eyasooka okuzuulibwa eyagenda mu Hong Kong ng’ava mu Guangzhou.
Okuva olwo, kaweefube mungi ateekeddwa mu kunoonyereza ku HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 kaazuulibwa mu mwana ow’emyezi 7 egy’obukulu okuva mu Netherlands ku nkomerero ya 2004.
Mu kusooka kaasangibwa nga kali nnyo mu baana abato, abakadde n’abalwadde abalina obusibage obutono era nga balina obulwadde obwekuusa ku mussizo.
Okubeera ne coryza, ejjanga, omusujja, n’okuzimba kw’amawuggwe (bronchiolitis) kisangibwa nnyo mu bulwadde obuleetebwa HCoV-NL63.
Okunoonyereza okulala kwalaga okusangibwa kw’akawuka ke kamu kano mu bikeberwa okuva mu nnyindo y’omwana omulenzi ow’emyezi 8 eyalina lubyamira mu Netherlands.
Newankubadde nga kaalabibwa mu Netherlands, mu butuufu kaasaasaanira ensi yonna.
Kiteeberezebwa nti HCoV-NL63 kaleeta ebitundu nga 4.7% eby’obulwadde obwekuusa ku kussa obwa bulijjo, era nga kasinga kwegiriisa ku ntandikwa y’ekiseera ky’ekyeya (summer), ttoggo (spring) n’obutiti (winter).
HCoV-NL63 kalina akakwate n’okuzimba kw’akavuumiro (obstructive laryngitis, oba croup).
Mu mwaka gwe gumu, HCoV-HKU1 kaazuulibwa mu musajja ow’emyaka 71 eyali aweereddwa ekitanda olwa lubyamira n’okuzimba amawuggwe mu Hong Kong.
Ng’oggyeeko lubyamira n’okuzimba amawuggwe, HCoV-HKU1 era yazuulibwa ng’alina akakwate ne acute asthmatic exacerbation.
Okufaananako ne HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E ne HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 yasangibwa okwetooloola ensi, ng’aleeta obulwadde obwekuusa ku kussa obutali bwa maanyi.
Obuwuka bwa HCoVs buno bwonna obuna abantu babumanyidde bulungi era okutwaliza awamu tebusuubirwa kukyukakyuka okuleeta endwadde ez’omutawaana, newankubadde nga waliwo obubenje obwali bubaddewo olw’ensonga ezitamanyiddwa nga mu mbeera etasangikasangika ekika kya HCoV-NL63 eky’omutawaana, ekyalagibwa gye buvuddeko nga kyaviirako obuvune obw’amaanyi mu kitundu ky’omussizo ekya wansi mu China.
Okutwaliza awamu, obuwuka bwa HCoVs buno bufuna obusobozi obw’okutambula obulungi n’okubeerera ddala mu bantu, era butandika okubeera nga tebukyali bwa bulabe nnyo.
MERS-CoV kaasooka kuzuulibwa mu 2012 mu mawuggwe g’omulwadde ow’emyaka 60 eyali afunye lubyamira ow’amaanyi n’okulemererwa kw’ensigo mu Saudi Arabia.
Newankubadde ng’abalwadde bonna abakakasiddwa basibuka mu Middle East, abalwadde abavudde ebweru n’abamu nga babuggye ku balwadde be basemberedde bazuuliddwa mu mawanga ga Bulaaya mangi ne Tunisia.
Omulundi omulala obulwadde buno bwe bwabalukawo gwali mu South Korea mu 2015 era abalwadde 186 be baakakasibwa.
Enneeyoleka z’ekisawo eza MERS zifaanana eza SARS, nga zirimu lubyamira ow’amaanyi (progressive acute pneumonia).
Obutafaananako na SARS, abalwadde ba MERS bangi era baafuna okulemererwa kw’ensigo, nga mu kiseera kino kiri ku MERS yekka mu ndwadde ezireetebwa HCoV.
Abalwadde abasukka mu bitundu 30% babeera n’obuzibu mu byenda, ng’ekiddukano n’okusesema.
Mu Gwokubiri nga 14, 2020, abalwadde abasukka mu 2500 abaakakasibwa mu magezeserezo baalimu omuwendo gw’abaafa munene nga gwa bitundu 34.4%, ekifuula MERS-CoV akamu ku buwuka obukyasinze okuba obw’omutawaana mu bantu.
Mu masekkati ne ku nkomerero ya Deesemba 2019, abalwadde ba lubyamira nga bamanyiddwa okuba nga baalinako SARS-CoV-2 emabega baasangibwa mu Wuhan, Hubei Province, China.
World Health Organization yalangirira obuzibu obuliwo mu kiseera kino obw’obulwadde bw’ekitundu ky’omussizo ekya wansi obuleetebwa SARS-CoV-2 ng’Ekizibu ky’Ebyobulamu mu Nsi Yonna (Public Health Emergency of International Concern) era obulwadde buno n’ebutuuma COVID-19.
Mu Gwokusatu nga 3, 2020, abalwadde 90,053 be baali bakakasiddwa mu nsi yonna, ng’ebitundu 3.4% be bafa.
Ekikulu okumanya, abalwadde abafa mu Hubei, China bali ebitundu 4.2%, so ng’ebweru waakyo bali ebitundu 1.2%.
SARS-CoV-2 aleeta obuvune obw’amaanyi mu mussizo nga bwekiri ku SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV, nga bweyola ng’omusujja, okukolola n’okukaluubirirwa mu kussa.
Ekiddukano nakyo kisangibwa mu balwadde abamu.
Lubyamira ke kamu ku bubonero obusinga okuba obw’amaanyi era ng’ayinza okweyongera mangu n’aleeta obuzibu mu kkubo ly’omukka ogussibwa.
Newankubadde nga SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV-2 bufaanana nnyo olw’obufaanane bw’endagabutonde obungi (high nucleotide sequence homology) obw’ebitundu 82%, bugwa ku matabi ga njawulo ku muti gw’ensibuko (phylogenetic tree).
SARS-CoV-2 ka bulabe butonoko naye nga kasaasaanyizibwa nnyo bw’ogeraageranya ne SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV.
Abalwadde ba SARS-CoV-2 abatalaga bubonero balabiddwako era bayinza okuyamba ku kwanguya ku kusaasaanyizibwa kwako okwetooloola ensi.
Okugeraageranya n’okukontanya SARS-CoV-2 n’obuwuka bwa HCoVs obulala omukaaga kwoleka obufaanane n’enjawulo ebisaanye okumanyibwa.
Ekisooka, ekiseera obubonero mwe bweyolekera n’ekiseera obulwadde bwa HCoV kye bumala bifaanana nnyo.
Mu ngeri eno, SARS-CoV-2 agoberera enneeyisa ey’awamu ey’obuwuka bwa HCoVs obulala omukaaga.
Ekyokubiri, obunyiinyiitivu bw’obubonero bwa COVID-19 buli wakati wa SARS-CoV n’obuwuka bwa HCoVs obuna (kwe kugamba HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 ne HCoV-NL63).
Ku ludda olumu, omuntu alina SARS-CoV-2 aba n’obubonero obutera okulabibwa mu muntu alina HCoVs, omuli obubonero obutamanyiddwa bulungi, obutali bwa maanyi oba obutaba na kabonero konna.
Ku ludda olulala, abalwadde ba COVID-19 abatonotono nga bayi nabo basobola okulabwa nga bwe kiri ku bantu abalina SARS-CoV, newankubadde ng’ettundutundu lyabwe si ddene.
Ekyokusatu, ensaasaana ya SARS-CoV-2 nayo eraga embeera ezisangibwa mu nsaasaana ya HCoVs ne SARS-CoV.
Ku ludda olumu, ensaasaana ya SARS-CoV-2 ya maanyi nga bwe kiri ku HCoVs.
Ku ludda olulala, tekinnaba kukakasika oba ng’okusiigibwa kwa SARS-CoV-2 kukendeera oluvannyuma lw’okuyita mu bantu nga bwe kiri ku SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV.
Ekisembayo, nga bwe kiri ku buwuka bwa HCoVs obulala, SARS-CoV-2 kasobola okulabikira mu sampolo z’obubi.
Eky’okuba ng’omuntu asobola okufuna SARS-CoV-2 ng’alidde obubi nga bwe kiri ku SARS-CoV mu mbeera ezimu kirina kumala kukakasibwa mu kunoonyereza okunaakolebwa gye bujja.
Era kikulu nnyo okulaba oba nga SARS-CoV-2 ayinza okuba ng’aliko ekiseera kye yeegirisizaamu nga bwe kiri ku HCoVs.
Newankubadde guli gutyo, ebikwata ku SARS-CoV-2 omuli okusiigibwa, obulwadde bw’aleeta n’okuba ng’asigala ng’akyasiigibwa ng’ayise mu bantu bujja kuba bwa mugaso ku ekinaava mu bulwadde bwa COVID-19 obuliwo kaakano.
Obubonero bwonna obutali bwa maanyi obuleetebwa HCoVs abantu babugumidde bulungi.
Bwe kitunuulirwa mu ngeri endala, kiyinza era okubeera ekituufu nti abantu bagumidde bulungi obuwuka bwa HCoVs buno.
Mu bigambo ebirala, buno bwombi buyinza okubeera nga bwe bukaawonawo ku bulwadde bwa HCoV obw’omutawaana obwaliwo edda.
Obuwuka bwa HCoVs obuleeta obulwadde obw’omutawaana mu bantu n’abantu abaafuna obulwadde bwa HCoV obw’amaanyi baasaanawo.
Kino okusobola okubaawo, HCoVs bulina okwekubisaamu mu bantu emirundi egimala okusobozesa omuwendo ogwekubisizzaamu okugumira ebijjawo ku muntu oba ku kintu kwe bubeera.
Mu ngeri eyo, SARS-CoV-2 gye kakoma okulemerako era ne gye kakoma okukwata abantu abangi, n’omukisa gwako ogw’okumanyiira abantu gye gukoma okweyongera.
Bwe kamanyiira obulungi, okusaasaana kwako mu bantu kuba kuzibu okuyimiriza nga bakozesa omuggalo oba engeri endala ez’okuziyiza okusaasaana kw’obulwadde.
Okumala emyaka egiwera, obuwuka bwa CoVs bwa mirundi ena obusaasaanidde mu bantu nga bubaleetera ssennyiga owa bulijjo mu bantu abalina obusibage obulungi.
Obuwuka obwo tebwetaaga kwekweka mu nsolo.
Mu kugeraageranya, obuwuka bwa SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV obuleeta ennyo endwadde tebunnamanyiira bantu bulungi era ensaasaana yaabwo mu bantu tesobola kubeezekawo.
Buba bulina okubeerawo n’okuzaalukukira eyo gye bubeera era ne bunoonya omukisa okwekwata ku bantu abanafu oboolyawo nga buyitira ku muntu omu oba abangi abanafu mu mubiri ne babuwa amaanyi.
Akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 kalina obubonero obufaanaganako ne SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV wamu n’obuwuka obuna obukwata abantu mu bitundu gye babeera obuyitibwa HCoVs.
Kasaasaana nnyo okufaananako n’obwo obukwata abantu obuyitibwa HCoVs, waakiri nga bwe kiri mu kimanyiddwa mu kiseera kino.
Wabula, kaleeta nnyo endwadde okusinga obwo obukwata abantu obuyitibwa HCoVs ate era tekaleeta nnyo ndwadde kwenkana na SARS-CoV oba MERS-CoV.
Kikyalina okwetegerezebwa oba nga kanaamanyiira abantu mu bujjuvu era ne kasaasaanira mu bantu nga tekalina we keekutte oba okubeera ku nsolo ebeerako akawuka etasaasaanya.
Nga tetunnaba kwogera ku nsolo ezaavaako akawuka ka HCoVs, kijja kutuyamba okwogera ku nnyinyonnyola y’ebigambo n’obubonero bw’ebigambo bino, enfuukafuuka, obutonde, obusaasaaniro, ekibeerako akawuka ekitasaasaanya n’ekibeerako akawuka ekisaasaanya HCoVs.
Ensolo ekola ng’ekisaasaanya ekifuulafuula HCoV bwe kiba nga kirina enkula eyeefaanaanyiriza obujjajja nga kigabana endagabutonde ku mutendera gw’obutaffaali bw’omubiri.
Akawuka akazaala katera okuba nga kaamanyiira era nga tekaleeta bulwadde ku kintu kwe kabeera.
Mu ngeri y’emu, akawuka we keekwata wabeerawo HCoV ebbanga lyonna okumala ebbanga ggwanvu.
Mu mbeera zombi, ekibeerako akawuka kiba kirwadde era nga kye kitonde ekibeerako HCoV oba ekizadde ky’akawuka.
Okwawukanako n’ekyo, akawuka ka HCoV bwe kateekebwa ku kibeerako akawuka ekitasaasaanya nga tekannaba oba nga mu kiseera kye kimu kateekeddwa mu bantu, kaba tekannamanyiira kintu ekyo kwe kabeera era katera okusaasaanya endwadde.
Ekibeerako akawuka ekitasaasaanya kisobola okubeera ng’ensibuko y’obulwadde mu bantu era ne kizannya ekifo ky’ekibeerako akawuka ekisaasaanya nga kiganya akawuka okuzaalukana era ne kakwata abantu ate ne kasaasaanyiza ddala obulwadde mu bantu.
HCoV tekasobola kusaasaana bwe kaba nga tekasobola kwebeezaawo ku ekyo ekibeerako akawuka ekitasaasaanya.
Mu ngeri endala, akawuka ka HCoVs kasobola okumanyiira ku kibeerako akawuka ekitasaasaanya era ne kabeera nga kye kalwaza okumala ekiseera ekinene.
Mu ngeri eyo, ekibeerako akawuka ekitazaala kifuuka ekyekwatwako akawuka eky’obutonde.
Obubaka obukwata ku byendwadde buzze nga bulaga nti ensaasaana ya SARS yalina akakwate n’ensolo ez’omu nsiko.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku luzzizzi kwalaga nti abasuubuzi b’ebisolo baalina abasirikale abalwanyisa SARS-CoV IgG bangi mu mibiri bw’ogeraageranya n’abantu abalala.
Amafumbe (Paguma larvata) n’embwa erabika ennyo mu Asia eyitibwa racoon zaasangibwa nga zirimu obuwuka obulinga SARS-CoV nga bufaananira ddala n’obwa SARS-CoV.
Kino kyayongera okuwagirwa mu ngeri nti oluvannyuma lw’okutta ensolo ezo ezaali mu butale bwonna, akawuka ka SARS tekaddamu kulabikako.
Wabula, n’amafumbe g’omu nsiko oba agabeera mu ddundiro nga tegannaba kugenda mu butale gaali tegalina kawuka ka SARS-CoV, nga kitegeeza nti akasolo ako kandiba nga kabeerako bubeezi kawuka naye nga tekasaasaanya naye nga si kye kintu eky’obutonde ekyekwatako akawuka ka SARS-CoV.
Awo nno, olw’okuba nti ebitundu 80% eby’ensolo ez’enjawulo mu butale bw’e Guangzhou zirina abasirikale abalwanyisa SARS-CoV obusobozi bw’okuba nti obusolo obutono buyinza okuba nga nabwo bukola ng’ekibeerako akawuka ekisaasaanya SARS-CoV tetubosola kububuusa maaso.
Bino byonna bifaanana okuba nga bibeerako akawuka ka SARS-CoV naye nga tekasaasaana.
N’ekyava mu ekyo, ekisolo ekitonde ekibeerako akawuka ka SARS-CoV kyalaga nga kyefaanaanyirizaako akawundo CoV, akayitibwa SARS Rhinolophus bat CoV HKU3 (SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3), akabeera mu buwundo bw’e China obuyitibwa horseshoe bats.
Obuwundo buno bulina abasirikale abalwanyisa SARS-CoV n’obutaffaali obuli mu kika kya BatCoV HKU3.
Kano n’obuwuka bwa CoV obulala obw’obuwundo bugabana ebitundu 88-92% by’endagabutonde ne SARS-CoV.
Okunoonyereza kuno kwateekawo omusingi ogw’entegeera empya nti obuwundo bubeeramu endwadde empya ezikwata abantu.
Obuwuka obulala bungi obwefaananyirizaako ne SARS CoVs (SL-CoVs) nabwo buzuuliddwa mu buwundo naye nga tewali n’akamu okuggyako akayitibwa WIV1 akasobola okwawulibwa ng’akawuka akalamu.
Ekirungo ky’omu mubiri ekiyitibwa angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) kimanyiddwa ng’ekisembeza SARS-CoV.
WIV1 kaava mu sampolo z’obubi bw’obuwundo era kaalagibwa ng’akakozesa akawundo, effumbe ne ACE2 mu bantu ng’ekisembeza obutaffaali okuyingirirwa akawuka.
Ekisanyusa, oluzzizzi lw’akawuka ka SARS mu balwadde abagenda bawona lwali lusobola okusaabulula WIV1.
Ne gye buli eno, WIV1 kakiikirira oluganda olusinga okuba okumpi ne SARS-CoV mu buwundo, obugabana ebitundu 95% eby’endabutonde.
Ng’oggyeeko endagabutonde efaanana ennyo wakati w’obuwuka buno bwombi, kikkirizibwa wonna nti WIV1 si ke kawuka ka SAR-CoV akazaala obulala akali okumpi ate n’obuwundo si ke kali okumpi ku byekwatako akawuka ka SARS-CoV.
Enneekenneenya y’enfuukafuuka y’obuwuka eteeka MERS-CoV mu kibinja kye kimu ne CoV-HKU4 wamu ne CoV-HKU5.
Akawundo CoV-HKU4 ne MERS-CoV bukozesa ekibeerako akawuka kye kimu, dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4), okuyingiza akawuka.
Endagabutonde (RNA) ya MERS-CoV yeefaananyiriza n’eyo erabikira mu buwundo beta-CoVs obwalabibwa e Bulaaya ne mu Afrika.
Ne gye buli eno, tewali kawuka ka MERS-CoV kalamu kasobola kusangibwa mu buwundo.
MERS-CoV n’abooluganda lwe akawundo CoV-HKU25 bigabana ebitundu 87% byokka eby’endagabutonde.
Awo nno, obuwundo buyinza okuba nga si bwe bwekwatako akawuka ka-MERS-CoV amangu.
Ku ludda olulala okunoonyereza okukoleddwa mu mawanga agagwa mu kitundu kya Middle East kulaze nti eŋŋamiya ziraga nti zirina MERS-CoV-mu basirikale abalwanyisa endwadde mu mubiri, era nga bwe kiri mu ŋŋamiya eziri mu mawanga ga Afrika ezaava mu mawanga ga Middle East.
Obuwuka obulamu bu-MERS-CoV obufaanagana n’akawuka akasangibwa mu bantu obwayawulwa nga buva mu lunyira lw’eŋŋamiya, ne kyongera okulaga nti eŋŋamiya ze zikola ng’ekyekwatwako akawuuka ka-MERS-CoV.
Kikulu nnyo nti obubonero obutonotono naye nga bweyolekeramu obuwuka buyitirivu bwalabibwa mu ŋŋamiya ezaalina MERS-CoV.
Genderera, eŋŋamiya endwadde ziba n’obuwuka si miyitiro gy’omukka gyokka, ate ng’era gwe muyitiro omukulu ogw’akawuka mu buwundo.
Wabula, ebibuuzo bikyaliwo kubanga abalwadde ba MERS abakakasiddwa tebalina be bakwatagana nabo mabega na ŋŋamiya ng’obubonero obuliwo tebunnalabika, obwandiba nga bukwanyizibwa na muntu-ku-muntu oba emiyitiro gy’okusaasaanya egitamanyiddwa omuli ebika by’ebisolo ebitamanyiddwa ebirimu MERS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 egabana ebitundu by’endagabutonde 96.2% n’akawundo CoV RaTG13 akaayawulwa okuva mu buwundo buyitibwa Rhinolophus affinis bats.
Era nga bwe kiri ku SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV, enjawulo wakati wa SARS-CoV-2 ne RaTG13 ya maanyi nnyo mu ngeri nti kizibu okulengera oluganda oluli wakati w’obuwuka obwo.
Kwe kugamba, obuwundo buyinza okuba nga si bwe bwekwatibwako amangu okubeerako akawuka ne busaasaanya SARS-CoV-2 okuggyako nga eyo gye bujja waliwo obuwundo bu-CoVs obubufaanana obuzuuliddwa.
Mu ngeri y’okuteebereza, ekisolo ekibeerako akawuka ekitasaasaanya SARS-CoV-2 kirina okuba nga kimu ku bika ebyo ebibeera mu nsiko nga bitundibwa era ne bittibwa mu katale ka Huanan Seafood Wholesale Market, nga mu kusooka obulwadde bwa COVID-19 obwasooka kwe bwakwanyizibwa nga kirabika, waliwo okusaasaanyizibwa kw’obulwadde okuva ku nsolo-okudda-ku-muntu.
Okunoonyereza okuwerako okukoleddwa emabegako awo nga kwesigamiziddwa ku ntereeza y’endagabutonde kulaze nti ekibinja ky’ensolo eziri mu katyabaga eziyitibwa pangolins (Manis javanica) zandiba nga nazo zirimu obuzadde obwekwanya ku beta-CoVs obufaananako ne SARS-CoV-2.
Obusolo buno bu-Pangolin obutalabwangako obulimu endagabutonde ya CoV bugabana ebitundu 85-92% ne SARS-CoV-2.
Wabula, bufaanaganira ddala ne RaTG13 n’ebitundu nga 90% ku ddaala ly’entereeza y’endagabutonde.
Zeegabanyizzaamu ennyiriri 2 entonotono ez’obuwuka obulinga SARS-CoV-2 mu neeyoleka y’endabutonde ng’emu ku yo egabana obukole ne (RBD) SARS-CoV-2, ng’ebitundu 97.4% eby’ekirungo ky’endagabutonde bifaanagana.
Mu ngeraageranya ey’enjawulo, obukole bwa RBDs obwa SARS-CoV-2 ne RaTG13 bweyawudde nnyo naye nga bweyawulidde mu busiŋŋanyi bwa ntereeza ya ndagabutonde.
Okunoonyereza okwasooka ku pangolin ezaali endwadde nakwo kwalaga okukengebwa kw’obuwuka obwali mu sampolo z’amawuggwe obulina oluganda ne SARS-CoV-2.
Okunoonyereza kuno kwakozesa obukodyo obw’enjawulo omuli n’obwokukyusiriza okufuna entereeza y’endagabutonde erimu ebitundu 86.3% eby’enfaanana y’akawuka.
Tetusobola kuggyawo busobosi bwa kuba nti pangolin ke kamu ku busolo obubeerako akawuka obutasaasaanya SARS-CoV-2.
Mu kiseera kino, tewali bubaka bukakasa buvo bwa SARS-CoV-2 owa pangolin olw’entereeza eyawukana wakati wa SARS-CoV-2 ne SARS-CoV-2 beta-CoVs owa pangolin .
Mu ngeri y’emu, ebbanga wakati wa SARS-CoV-2 ne RaTG13 limpiko okusinga ku eryo eriri wakati wa SARS-CoV-2 ne SARS-CoV-2-related beta-CoVs owa pangolin .
Enfuukafuuka y’omuyitiro gwa SARS-CoV-2 mu buwundo, pangolin n’ensolo endala eziringa abantu tennaba kutegeerekeka.
Weewaawo entereeza mu ndagabutonde ezuuliddwa wakati wa RBDs ne SARS-CoV-2 ne pangolin, obuwuka obwekwanya ku SARS-CoV-2 beta-CoVs, SARS-CoV-2 ne RaTG13 bugabana endagabutone eyaawamu.
Kisuubirwa nti obufaanane obw’amaanyi wakati wa RBDs mu buwuka obwekwanya ku pangolin SARS-CoV-2 beta-CoVs ne SARS-CoV-2 bufugibwa enfuukafuuka eyeeyawudde.
Ekiteeso ekirala ekyawukana ku ekyo kiwagira engattagatta wakati w’obuwuka bwa pangolin SARS-CoV-2 beta-CoV ne RaTG13 mu kika ky’ensolo ez’omu nsiko.
Ng’amaanyi agasindiikiriza mu kufuukafuuka, okugattagatta kuli nnyo mu beta-CoVs.
Okusalawo tekunnatuukiibwako ku nsolo esibukako SARS-CoV-2.
Ng’oggyeeko obuwuka obuleeta ennyo endwadde obwa HCoVs, ensibuko ya HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-NL63 ne HCoV-HKU1 ey’omu nsolo nayo enoonyerezeddwako.
Obuvo obukwata ku kunoonyereza ku nfuukafuuka y’ebitonde bulaga nti HCoV-NL63 ne HCoV-229E bwandiba nga bwava mu CoVs mu buwundo, ate nga muzadde w’akawuka ka HCoV-OC43 ne HCoV-HKU1 azuuliddwa mu mmese.
Kitegeezeddwa nti CoV ey’akawundo eyitibwa ARCoV.2 (Appalachian Ridge CoV) kaakengebwa mu Amerika ey’obukiikakkono (North American) nga ka langi ssatu era nga kaalaga nti kalina oluganda olw’okumpi ne HCoV-NL63.
Mu ngeri endala, HCoV-229E yakwanyizibwa n’endagabutonde n’akawundo CoV, akayitibwa Hipposideros/GhanaKwam/19/2008, akaalangibwa e Ghana, ate nga n’eŋŋamiya nazo ziteeberezebwa okubeera ekibeerako akawuka ekitasaasaanya.
Olw’okutangaazamukko, amagezi agaliwo ku nsibuko y’ensolo ku HCoVs obumanyiddwa gafunziddwa mu Kifaananyi​ 1 n’Omweso 2.
Obwekenneenyi bw’enfuukafuuka buleese obubaka obulaga nti HCoVS busaasaana mu bika by’ensolo eby’enjuwulo nga bwe kiri mu byafaayo.
HCoV-OC43 bwe kaabuka okuva mu kika ekimu ne kadda mu bantu okuva mu bisolo ebirundibwa ewaka eyo mu 1890, ekirwadde ekikwata omuyungo gw’okussa kyazuulibwa.
Ebyafaayo by’okusaasaana kw’ebika eby’enjawulo ebya HCoV-229E tebitangaala bulungi.
Obuwuka obuyitibwa bat alpha-CoVs obulina oluganda olw’amaanyi ne HCoV-229E buzuuliddwa.
Wakati waabyo waliwo ekiyitibwa alpaca alpha-CoV.
Obubaka obw’enjawulo buwerako obuwagira okusaasaana kw’akawuka okuva mu buwundo okudda mu bantu obutereevu.
Okusooka, abantu naye nga si nsolo eyitibwa alpacas birina enkwatagana n’obuwundo mu kugabana ebifo mwe bibeera.
Wabula, abantu balina enkwatagana ey’okumpi ne alpacas.
Ekyokubiri, akawuka ka HCoV-229E-related bat alpha-CoVs kalimu enjawulo ate tekalwaza buwundo so ng’ate alpaca alpha-CoV kaaleeta ekirwadde mu muyungiro gw’okussa mu nsolo endwadde.
Ekisembayo, alpaca alpha-CoV tekazuuliddwa mu nsolo ezaava ewaka ne zidda mu nsiko.
Awo nno, obusobozi tebuyinza kuggyibwawo nti alpacas zijja HCoV-229E-related alpha-CoV okuva mu bantu.
Mu butuufu, obuwundo y’ensibuko y’obuwuka obusaasaanya endwadde mu bantu omwo nga mwe muli n’akawuka rabies virus, Ebola virus, Nipah virus ne Hendra virus.
Awo nno tekyewuunyisa nnyo nti obuwundo busobola okusaasaanya HCoV-229E obutereevu mu bantu.
Mu ngeri endala, weewaawo bat alpha-CoVs bukola nga ensibuko y’endagabutonde eya HCoV-229E, alpacas n’eŋŋamiya (dromedary camels) ziyinza okukola ng’ekibeerako akawuka ekitasaasaanya ekitambuza obuwuka mu bantu nga bwe kiri ddala ku MERS-CoV.
MERS-CoV kakola ng’ekyokulabirako ekirungi ddala eky’ensaasaanya okuva mu kika ekimu okudda mu kirala okuva mu buwundo okudda ku ŋŋamiya (dromedary camels) ate n’okuva mu ŋŋamiya (dromedary camels) okudda mu bantu.
Ensibuko y’okufuukafuuka kwa MERS-CoV okuva ku buwundo emanyibwa okuva ku ntandikwa eyasooka era okumanyibwa okwo ne kunywezebwa mu bizze nga bizuulibwa.
Kyoleka lwatu nti obuwundo bulina ebika by’obuwuka bingi ddala ebitambula mu bika eby’enjawulo ebyeyawulayawula mu bika eby’enjawulo ate ne busaasaana mu bika eby’enjawulo.
Obuwangaazi, ebibinja by’obuwundo obungi, okukwatagana ennyo wamu n’obusobozi bw’okubuuka ennyo byonna bisobozesa obuwundo okubeera ‘ekisaasaanya akawuka’.
Ku ludda olulala, MERS-CoV kateekeddwa mu ŋŋamiya (dromedary camels) okumala ebbanga eriwera.
Kabeera bulungi mu ŋŋamiya ezo ezaafuuka okuva ku kibeerako akawuka ekitasaasaanya okudda ku kitonde ekyekwatako akawuka.
MERS-CoV kaleeta obulwadde obutonotono era kazaalukuka kitono nga kali mu nsolo ezo.
Okusaasaanya kwakwo okw’ebbalirirwe mu bantu kwa ngeri ya kabenje era abantu basigala nga beekwatako akawuka MERS-CoV ako naye ne katasaasaana kubanga okusaasaana kwako tekubeezekawo.
Mu kugeraageranya omulimu gw’eŋŋamiya mu kusaasaanya MERS-CoV, omulimu gwa pangolins, bwe guba nga weeguli, mu kusaasaanya SARS-CoV-2 gwa njawulo.
Okusinga ennyo, obuwuka bu-pangolin beta-CoVs buleeta nnyo endwadde mu pangolins.
Buyinza okuba ekibeerako akawuka ekitasaasaanya SARS-CoV-2-related beta-CoVs, nga bwe kiri ku ffumbe ku SARS-CoV.
Obusobozi bwa maanyi obw’okusaasaanya SARS-CoV-2 mu bika eby’enjawulo okuva ku nsolo okudda mu bantu obulina okukakasibwa oba okusazibwamu mu kunoonyereza okujja eyo mu maaso.
Okusooka, obuwundo buyinza okuba ekyekwatwako ky’obuwuka obwekwanya ku SARS-CoV-2 nga kumpi bufaanagana ne SARS-CoV-2.
Abantu bayinza okufaananya engeri gye bibeerawo mu ndya ne mu kusima.
Ekyokubiri, pangolin zisobola okubeera ekibeerako akawuka ekisaasaanya obuwuka obwekwanya ku SARS-CoV-2 kwe bwakateekebwa.
Abantu bakwatibwa akawuka nga kayitira mu kutta n’okulya ennyama enjigge.
Kisoboka nti ensolo eziringa omuntu omwo nga mwe muli n’ezirundibwa ewaka zisobola okukwatibwa SARS-CoV-2.
Okunoonyereza ku nsolo z’awaka n’ez’omu nsiko okuzuula abasirikale b’omubiri abazirimu kwetaagisa.
Ekyokusatu, nga bwe kyogeddwako waggulu, okugattagatta endagabutonde n’okumanyiira kwa SARS-CoV-2 kuyinza okuba nga kwagwawo mu kika ekyokusatu ekikwatagana n’obuwundo ne pangolin.
Okunoonyereza ku nsibuko ya SARS-CoV-2 mu nsolo kukyagenda mu maaso.
Ng’oggyeeko ebika by’ensolo ebyekwatwako obuwuka, ensonga enkulu ssatu ku ludda lw’obuwuka nazo nkulu mu kubeezaawo CoVs okusala ebiziyiza okubuuka okudda mu bika ebirala.
Ekisookera ddala, okuzaalukana kwabwo okulabika nga kuli waggulu ddala mu kuzaalukana kw’endagabutonde (RNA).
Mu kugeraageranya obuwuka obulala obukozesa endagabutonde (single-stranded RNA viruses), omuwendo gw’obuzaalukanyi bw’obuwuka guteeberezebwa okubeera wakati “w’omusaamusaamu” ne “ogwa waggulu” nga guliko omuwendo omukkati oguli wakati wa ~10-4 buli mwaka buli kifo 2, okusinziira ku mutendera gwa CoV ogw’okumanyiira n’ekyekwatako akawuka ekibadde tekimanyiddwa.
Obuwuka bwa CoVs bumanyi okutebuka ekirungo ki exoribonuclease, era nga bwe kisangulwa kivaamu okufuukafuuka okw’amaanyi n’okukendeera oba oluusi n’obutasoboka.
Ekyewuunyisa, ekirungo nucleotide analogue Remdesivir kimanyiddwa ng’ekinyigiriza okuzaalukana kwa CoV nga kiyitira mu kuziyiza exoribonuclease n’endagabutonde (RNA) eyeesigamye ku RNA polymerase.
Remdesivir kye kimu ku birungo ebirwanyisa SARS-CoV-2 ebigezesebwa mu kugezesa kw’ekisawo.
Ebyo ng’obiggyeeko, ekigero ky’okufuukafuuka ekya CoVs kiri awo nga mu mirundi kakadde nga kiri waggulu w’ekyo eky’ekyekwatibwako akawuka.
Mu ngeri y’emu, ekigero ky’okufuukafuuka kitera okuba waggulu bu CoV bwe buba nga tebumanyidde kintu kwe bwekutte.
Bw’ogeraageranya ne SARS-CoV akalina ekigero ky’okufuukafuuka ekya waggulu, ekigero ky’okufuukafuuka ekya SARS-CoV-2 kirabika nga kiri wansi, era ng’ekyo kiraga nti kati kagenze kamanyiirira ddala abantu.
Kyandiba nga kaamala dda okumanyiira ekintu ekirala ekifaananako n’abantu.
Ng’oggyeeko SARS-CoV-2, kino kikola ne ku MERS-CoV, akaamanyiira edda eŋŋamiya.
Mu kulowooza, kirabika nga enkyukakyuka mu ndagabutonde eyinza okuleetera eddagala erigema n’erirwanyisa obuwuka bwa SARS-CoV-2 obutakola mu bwangu.
Ekyokubiri, ekirungo kya RNA genome ekinene mu CoVs kinyigiriza enfuula ya genome olw’enfuukafuuka n’engattagatta, olwo ne kyongera omukisa gw’ebika ebyenjawulo okubeerana mu nkula yaabyo, ekintu ekirungi mu kusibuka kw’akawuka ka CoV akatamanyiddwa embeera bw’eba ng’eganya.
Kino kiwagirwa enkola ya copious unique open reading frames n’omugaso gwa puloteyini ebeera mu 3′ end eya genome.
Ekyokusatu, CoVs butera ate mu ngeri ya kulabira awo okukyusa obutiba mu kiseera ky’okuzaalukana nga buyita mu nkola eya “koppa-kyolonzeeko”.
Mu kibeerako akawuka ekikola ng’ekikompe ekitabula, enkyukakyuka ebaawo nnyo mu kiseera kya CoV RNA transcription.
Endagabutonde (RNAs) ezifaanagana ennyo wamu ne subgenomic RNAs zisobola okwegattagatta okufunamu bu CoV obulala.
Obubaka bw’enfuukafuuka y’obuwuka ey’okwegattagatta okw’obutonde erabiddwa mu HCoV-HKU1 ne mu HCoV-OC43, wamu ne CoV ow’ensolo gamba nga bat SL-CoV ne batCoV-HKU9.
Enkolagana y’akawuka n’ekibeerako akawuka mu nsaasaana y’obulwadde
Ng’oggyeeko ensonga z’akawuka essatu ezoogeddwako waggulu, enkolagana y’akawuka n’ekibeerako akawuka nayo nsonga nkulu ekola mu nsaasaanya y’obulwadde mu bika eby’enjawulo.
Mu kiwandiiko kino, okwegattagatta kwa SARS-CoV kutwalibwa ng’ekyokulabirako ekimanyiddwa ekyalaba n’obubaka mu kiseera ky’okusaasaanya obulwadde ekiyitibwa positive selection.
Okusinziira ku kwekenneenya wakati w’ebyawuliddwa okwekalirizibwa eby’abantu n’eby’effumbe SARS-CoVs, SARS-CoV kalowoozebwa okufuna amangu okumanyiira ebibeerako obuwuka, naddala mu kufuukafuuka ku RDB mu S protein.
Okutwaliza awamu, RBD mu S protein eya CoV ekolagana n’ekifuna obutaffaali era nga kirondebwa nnyo abasirikale b’omubiri mu kibeerako obuwuka.
Mu SARS-CoV, RBD eri mu amino acid owa 318 okutuuka ku 510 ku S1 fragment, eyeekwata ku ACE2 mu bantu wamu n’ebyo ebifuna obuwuka okuyingirirako.
RBD eya SARS-CoV esobola okukenga ebifuna obuwuka ACE2 mu nsolo ez’enjawulo, omuli akawundo, effumbe, emmese n’embwa (raccoon dog), ekkiriza okusaasaana kw’akawuka mu bika eby’enjawulo.
Mu butuufu, ebisigalira bya amino acid 6 byalabibwa nga bya njawulo okuva ku ebyo ebyawulibwa mu bantu n’effumbe mu RBD ate nga 4 ku byo bisangibwa mu nfaanana y’ebifuna obuwuka olw’okukolagana n’ekifuna obuwuka ACE2.
SARS-CoV ow’effumbe alimu okufuukafuuka kwa K479N ne S487T RBD we, ekiyinza okwongeza enkwatagana y’enkolagana ya spike protein ne ACE2 ey’ekifuna akwuka mu bantu.
Kwe kugamba, ebika bya amino acid ebibiri ebisikira ebirala biyinza okuba nga bya maanyi nnyo mu kumanyiira kw’akawuka mu bantu.
Kikulu okumanya nti SARS-CoV-2 kagabana ekifuna obulwadde eky’obutaffaali obufaanagana ne SARS-CoV.
Enjawulo ey’ebitundu 30% wakati wa SARS-CoV-2 ne SARS-CoV mu kigero ekya S1 ekya S protein kitegeeza nti y’enyweza oluganda eya S protein ne ACE2 mu bantu eyinza okuba nga yakyuka.
Mu butuufu, okunoonyereza kwa cryo-EM kulaga 10- ku-20 kulimu oluganda lwa maanyi mu kunyweza kuno okusinga ACE2 mu bantu ne SARS-CoV S protein.
Kijja kuba kirungi era okulaba oba nga ekintu ekirala ekifuna obuwuka kiyinza okwetaagisa mu kusaasaanya SARS-CoV-2.
Mu ngeri eyeewuunyisa, HCoV-NL63 nakyo kinyweza ACE2 naye nga kikozesa akatundu ka S akalala.
Waliwo n’ebifuna HCoV ebirala bingi, gamba nga aminopeptidase N ku HCoV-229E, ne 9-O-acetylated sialic acid ku HCoV-OC43.
Busobola era okunnyonnyola okumanyiira obulungi okw’obuwuka bwa CoV mu bantu oluvannyuma lw’okusaasaanira mu bika ebyenjawulo nga buva ku nsolo kwe bubeera.
Ng’oggyeeko ebifuna obuwuka eby’obutaffaali, ekiva mu HCoV okusaanasaanira mu bika eby’enjawulo kifugibwa ensonga endala ezeesigama ku kibeerako obuwuka n’ebikugira.
Enjawulo mu host proteins wakati w’abantu n’ebitonde ebisaasaanya HCoVs gamba ng’obuwundo, eŋŋamiya n’emmese ( rodents) biyinza okukola ng’omuziziko mu kusaasaanya obulwadde mu bika eby’enjawulo.
HCoVs bunaayiza ekibeerako obuwuka era ne kyewala ebikugira by’ekibeerako obuwuka olw’okusaasaanya obulungi obulwadde mu bika eby’enjawulo.
Mu ngeri eyo, ebisalawo ku molecule mu kitundu kino ekikulu eky’akawuka-ekibeerako obuwuka kikyetaaga okulengerwa n’okunnyonnyola.
Okusunsula mu genome okw’awamu okutaliimu kyekubiira (genome-wide screening) okw’ekibeerako obuwuka n’ebikugira bya SARS-CoV-2 omuli okukozesa tekinologiya ow’ekika ekya waggulu kiyinza okuvaamu ebibala.
Okubalukawo kwa HCoVs abadde tamanyiddwa: okuddayo ku ntandikwa
Enjawulo mu CoVs ow’obuwundo aleetawo emikisa gya maanyi mu kubalukawo kwa HCoVs obubadde tebumanyiddwa.
Mu ngeri eno, CoV ow’obuwundo bukolanga ng’ensibuko ya giini eza HCoVs.
Okwongereza ku ekyo, okufuukafuuka okw’amangu n’okwegattagatta kwa giini nabyo bifuga enkula ya HCoV era bikola ng’emitendera ebiri emikulu mu nkwajja eno.
Okugeza, okufuna oba okufiirwa entereeza ya giini za protein (protein-coding genes) okubadde kutamanyiddwa kulimu obusobozi bw’okukyusiza ddala enfaanana y’obuwuka.
Mu SARS-CoV accessory proteins, ORF8 zirowoozebwa okubeera enkulu mu kumanyiira abantu, ng’obuwuka bwa SARS-CoV obwekwanya ku buwundo bwayawulibwa naye ate ne busangibwa nga bulina divergent ORF8 proteins.
Akabonero ka 29-nucleotide deletion aka SARS-CoVs kasangiddwa mu bwawuzi obwayawulibwa ku ntandikwa ya nawookeera w’ekirwadde kino mu bantu.
Okusangula kuno kwawulamu ORF8 mu ORF8a ne ORF8b era nga kirowoozebwa okubeera enfuukafuuka y’okumanyiira etumbula okukyusakyusa ekibeerako obuwuka.
Ng’oggyeeko ekyo, SARS-CoV kalina ebyafaayo by’obusobozi bw’okwegattagatta mu nnyiriri za alpha- ne gamma-CoVs, omwalabibwa omuwendo gw’okwegattagatta mu nkula omutono mu RNA-dependent RNA polymerase.
Ebifo ebimu eby’okwegattagatta byalengerwa mu nsp9, ebisinga mu nsp10, n’ebitundu bya nsp14.
Mu ngeri y’emu, kiragiddwa nti nawookeera w’ekirwadde kya MERS-CoV yalimu okwegattagatta wakati w’ennyiriri ez’enjawulo, okwaliwo mu ŋŋamiya mu Saudi Arabia.
Ng’oggyeeko SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV, emirundi gy’okwegattagatta era girabiddwa mu HCoVs obulala, HCoVs mwe bwegattira ne CoVs ez’ensolo mu giini zaazo eziyitibwa non-structural genes.
Kisaana era okulabula nti okulondoba okukolebwa abantu kusobola okuleetawo enkyukakyuka ezitalabiddwa mu viral genomes, ng’okusinga ennyo kiva ku kuwewula ku buwuka ku kunyigirizibwa kw’okulondoba, gamba ng’okwo okuva ku busibage bw’ekibeerako obuwuka.
Ekyokulabirako ky’okukosebwa kuno kwe kufiirwa okw’amaanyi okwa ORF4 mu HCoV-229E prototype strain, nga kiva ku kusangula kwa nucleotide kwa mirundi ebiri.
Weewaawo nga ORF4 atafuusefuuse asobola okulabibwa mu buwuka bw’obuwundo ne mu ŋŋamiya obwekwanya ku HCoV-229E, alpaca alpha-CoV kooleka okusonsekebwa kwa nucleotide, okuva ku frameshift.
Ekisembayo naye nga si kye kisemberayo ddala, okukula kwa HCoVs akabadde tekamanyiddwa era kufugibwa okusindiikirizibwa kw’okulonda mu kibeerako obuwuka.
Obutalaga bubonero oba obubonero obutono bwalabibwa ng’obuwundo bulwadde CoVs, nga kiraga okumanyiira okw’awamu wakati wa CoVs n’obuwundo.
Kyalabika nti obuwundo bwamanyidde bulungi CoVs mu nkula yaabwo (anatomically) ate ne mu mbeera z’obulamu obwa bulijjo.
Okugeza, obunafu mu kuzimba okujjawo mu buwundo bukendeeza embeera etali ya bulijjo ereetebwa CoVs.
Okwongereza ku ekyo, okufa kw’obutaffaali okw’obutonde mu buwundo kuzibikirwa nga kiva ku kukendeeza kwa butaffaali bw’obutonde obw’ekifuna obuwuka NKG2/CD94 wamu n’okweyoleka okwa wansi okw’amaanyi okw’obukolaganyi bwa molecules ez’ekibinja I.
So ng’ate, ebika bya oxygen species (ROS) ava mu kukola emmere mu mubiri mu buwundo kuyinza okunyigiriza okuzaalukana kwa CoV n’okukosa proofreading by exoribonuclease, ne kivaamu okunyigiriza kw’okulonda okuleeta ebika by’akawuka ebireeta ennyo endwadde nga biteereddwa mu kitundu ekirala ekibeerako obuwuka.
Obuwuka bwa CoV obulala nabwo buyinza okukula nga bwegattagatta, ne kireetawo protein ezibadde tezimanyiddwa oba obubonero bwa protein obusobozesa ekibeerako obuwuka okumanyiira.
Awo nno, si kya mukisa bukisa nti HCoVs obubadde tebumayiddwa bubaluseewo mu myaka abiri egiyise.
CoVs tebuleeta ndwadde oba buleeta obubonero butono mu ekyo ekisaasaanya gamba ng’obuwundo n’eŋŋamiya.
Buzaalukana nnyo ate nga tebuleeta busibage bwa maanyi ku kintu ekibeerako endwadde.
Muno mwe muli ekyama ekireetera ebisaasaanya endwadde ebitalina bubonero okulabibwa n’ekireetawo obulwadde obw’akabi ennyo mu bantu.
Obubonero obw’akabi businga kuva ku kutanula obusibage n’obubonero obw’akabi ennyo (cytokine storm) ne kiba nti obusibage gye bukoma okuba obw’amaanyi, n’okukosebwa kw’amawuggwe gye kukoma okuba okw’omutawaana.
Mu kugeraageranya n’abantu abatalabikirako bubonero, obusibage bulemesebwa okwekubisaamu mu kuzaalukana kwa CoV.
Akakodyo ke kamu ak’okuggyawo obukwatane bw’obusibage kuyinza okuba n’emiganyulo mu kujjanjaba SARS-CoV-2.
Enkola ya interferon ya maanyi nnyo mu buwundo.
Awo nno, okukola ku type I interferon waakiri ng’okukosebwa kwa SARS-CoV-2 kwakalabika mu bantu kuteekwa oba nga kuvaamu ebirungi.
Mu ngeri y’emu, okuleetera okukola kwa NLRP3 inflammasome mu buwundo tekivaamu kantu.
Mu ntegeera eno, okukugira kwa NLRP3 inflammasome nga kuli wamu ne MCC950 kuyinza okuyamba mu bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19.
Okubalukawo kwa SARS-CoV-2 kugoberera omulamwa ogw’awamu omwasibukira SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV.
Weewaawo kizuuliddwa nti beta-CoV kagabana ebitundu 95% ebya nucleotide ne SARS-CoV, waliwo era ka CoV k’akawundo akagabana ebitundu 96% ebya nucleotide ne SARS-CoV-2.
Weewaawo effumbe n’ensolo endala ezitundibwa mu butale zizuuliddwa okukweka obuwuka obufaananako ne SARS-CoV, ekibeerako obuwuka ekitasaasaanya SARS-CoV-2 tekinnazuulibwa.
Pangolin beta-CoVs obwewuunyisa okufaanagana ne SARS-CoV-2 buzuuliddwa, ekiraga nti pangolin ziyinza okukola ng’ekibeerako obuwuka ekitasaasaanya oba pangolin beta-CoVs kayinza okuba nga kalina obutundutundu bwa giini bwe kaleeta ku nkula ya SARS-CoV-2 esembayo.
Weewaawo nga wakyaliwo ebibuuzo, tewali bubaka bulaga nti SARS-CoV-2 yakolebwa muntu mu bugenderevu oba mu ngeri etali ŋŋenderere.
CoVs bukomyewo okumanyika mu bantu olw’okubalukawo kwa SARS-CoV-2 okuzzeewo emabegako.
Okunoonyereza ku CoVs mu buwundo n’ensolo endala kukyusizza mu ngeri ey’amangu entegeera y’omugaso gw’endwadde eziva mu nsolo n’ensolo ezibeerako obuwuka bwa HCoVs mu kusaasaanya endwadde mu bantu.
Obubaka obw’amaanyi bulaze nti SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV ne SARS-CoV-2 buva mu buwundo era nga busaasaanyizibwa mu bantu nga buyitira ku bintu ebibeerako obuwuka ebitasaasaanya.
Olw’okuba nti obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV buva mu nkwatagana wakati w’abantu n’amafumbe mu butale, okuggala obutale obutundibwamu ebintu ebibisi n’okutta amafumbe kyandiyambye nnyo mu kukomya nawookeera wa SARS.
Mu ngeri y’emu, pangolins zirina okuggyibwa mu butale obutundibwamu ebintu ebibisi olw’okuziyiza okusaasaanya endwadde eziva mu nsolo okudda mu bantu, nga tutunuulira okuzuula ennyiriri ez’enjawulo eza pangolin beta-CoVs ezeekwanya ennyo ku SARS-CoV-2.
Wabula, oba nga SARS-CoV-2 asaasaanyibwa mu bantu ng’ayitira mu pangolins n’ensolo endala eziringa abantu n’engeri gy’asaasaanyizibwamu kijja kuzuulibwa eyo mu kunoonyereza okujja eyo mu maaso.
Ku ludda olulala, MERS-CoV kabadde mu ŋŋamiya okumala ebbanga eriwera.
Eŋŋamiya za mugaso nnyo mu ntambula ate ng’era zivaako nnyo ennyama, amata, amaliba n’ebyoya eri abantu.
Ziri nnyo mu bitundu bya Middle East ne Afrika.
Awo nno kizibu nnyo okutta eŋŋamiya zonna olw’okuziyiza MERS, ng’ekyakolebwa mu butale bw’ensolo ez’omu nsiko mu China okuziyiza okusaasaana kwa SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV-2.
Okusobola okuziyiza okubalukawo kwa MERS okutatadde, enkwata y’obulwadde buno erina okukulaakulanyizibwa okukola eddagala erigema MERS-CoV ery’eŋŋamiya, nga likolera wamu n’engeri endala eziziyiza obulwadde.
Olw’okuba nti tetusobola kumalawo buwuka buno, ekika ky’obuwuka obulala kisobola okubalukawo okuleeta nawookeera omulala.
Obuwuka obw’enjawulo obwa CoV obusaasaanya endwadde okuva mu nsolo okudda mu bantu bubunye mu nsiko.
N’okusingira ddala, bu CoV obw’obuwundo obulina obusobozi bw’okusaasaanya endwadde okuva mu nsoolo okudda mu bantu bwa ngeri nnyingi.
Waliwo emikisa mingi nti bu CoV obusaasaanya endwadde okuva mu nsolo okudda mu bantu bwegattagatta nga kiva mu kubalukawo bu CoV obupya obutambuzibwa amangu ne/oba mu bantu eyo gye bujja.
Empisa y’okulya ensolo ez’omu nsiko mu bifo ebimu mu China erina okusuulibwa okukendeeza ku nkwatagana eteetaagisa wakati w’abantu n’ensolo.
Nga tuli mu katyabaga ka SARS, MERS ne COVID-19, okweteekateeka okusingako obulungi n’enteekateeka ey’okubyaŋŋanga zirina okubeerawo.
Mu butuufu, obuwuka bungi bubaddewo mu nsi okumala ebbanga ddene ddala.
Bubeera mu bifo byabwo eby’obutonde okutuusa lwe walabikawo omukisa ne bubuukayo okugenda ewalala.
Newankubadde ng’obuwundo bulina obukole bungi obubusobozesa okusaasaanya obuwuka, omukisa gw’abantu okukwatagana n’obuwundo n’ebika ebirala eby’omu nsiko gusobola okukendeezebwa abantu bwe bategeezebwa okwewala okubisemberera.
Okwekaliriza entakera kwetaagisa mu nsolo eziringa abantu olw’okutegeera enkula ya CoVs mu ngeri esingako wamu n’ebyo ebibeerako obuwuka ebyobutonde ebijja okulabika nga bya mugaso mu kuziyiza okusaasaanya endwadde okuva ku nsolo-okudda-mu-bantu wamu ne nawookeera ow’omu maaso.
Mu kufundikira, engeri esinga obulungi ey’okuziyiza obuwuka obuva ku nsolo okudda mu bantu be bantu okuva ku bintu eby’obutonde ebibeerako obuwuka obusaasaanya endwadde okuva ku nsolo okudda mu bantu.
Waliwo ebintu bingi ebitannaba kutegeerekeka ku nsibuko y’obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 obuva mu nsolo okudda mu bantu.
Okusookera ddala, oba ng’obuwundo busaasaanya akawuka akasibukamu SARS-CoV-2 mu pangolin, kiba kisaana okulaba embeera obuwundo ne pangolin mwe bigabanira okubeerana mu bifo gye bibeera.
Ekyokubiri, oba ng’obuwundo buzannya ekifo ky’okusaasaanya obulwadde obutereevu mu bantu, olwo nno engeri abantu gye bakwataganamu n’obuwundo erina okufiibwako.
Ekyokusatu, ensolo eringa omuntu bw’eba nga y’ekola nga ekibeerako obuwuka ekitasaasaanya ekituufu, engeri gye kitabaganamu n’ebika ebirala omuli n’abantu, obuwundo ne pangolin erina okutangaazibwa.
Ekisembayo, olw’okubanga ensolo nnyingi eziringa abantu omwo nga mwe muli n’ez’awaka ziyinza okuba nga zikwatibwa mangu SARS-CoV-2, okwekaliriza n’okugezesa kw’obulwadde byombi birina okukolebwa.
Singa kanaaba kawundo, pangolin oba ensolo endala eringa omuntu, kisuubirwa nti SARS-CoV-2 oba obuwuka obulala obusibukako obulwadde nga kumpi bufaanagana bujja kuzuulibwa mu kibeerako obuwuka obwo eky’obutonde eyo gye bujja.
Okunoonyereza entakera ku nsonga eno kujja kutangaaza omugendo gw’enkula ya SARS-CoV-2 mu nsolo, omuli n’ebivaamu eby’omugaso mu kutangira n’okuziyiza COVID-19 mu bantu.
Okutuukanya ebisinziirwako okukakasa omulwadde “ateeberezebwa” ne “akakasiddwa” okubeera ne COVID-19 kyetaagisa
Nga 6 Ogwokubiri 2020, tiimu yaffe yali efulumizza ebigobererwa eby’amangu mu kukebera n’okujjanjaba abantu abalina 2019 novel coronavirus (2019-nCoV), era ng’ebigobererwa bino byali biraga obumanyirivu bwaffe n’okulaga engeri y’okulwanyisaamu obulungi nawookeera ono mu nsi yonna.
Wabula, obulwadde bwa coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) bulwadde bupya, bye tubumanyiiko bigenda byeyongera okusinziira ku bizuulibwa mu kunoonyereza okugenda mu maaso n’ebiyitibwamu mu kujjanjaba; noolwekyo, enkebera n’enzijanjaba nabyo bigenda bikyusibwamu.
Mu bbaluwa eno, twayanukula ekibuuzo kimu ku bigobererwa byaffe era ne tuwa ebigobererwa ebisinga obupya mu kusalawo “ateeberezebwa” ne “akakasiddwa” okusinziira ku bigobererwa ebikyasembyeyo mu Kukebera n’Okujjanjaba CoVID-19 (Diagnosis and Treatment Guidelines for COVID-19 (seventh version)) ebyayisibwa National Health Committee of the People’s Republic of China.
Mu Deesemba 2019, 2019 novel coronavirus (2019-nCoV) yaleetawo obulwadde, kati mu butongole obwatuumibwa coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) era n’akawuka ne katuumibwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Nga 11 Ogwokusatu 2020, WHO yalangirira nti COVID-19 kizibu kya byabulamu mu nsi yonna.
Okusobola okulwanyisa SARS-CoV-2, tiimu yaffe ekulaakulanyizza ebigobererwa eby’amangu nga byafulumizibwa ku yintaneeti mu Military Medical Research nga 06 Ogwokubiri 2020.
Byettaniddwa nnyo okuva lwe byafulumizibwa.
Wabula kisaanye okwetegerezebwa nti COVID-19 bulwadde bupya, bye tubumanyiiko bigenda byeyongera okusinziira ku bizuulibwa mu kunoonyereza okugenda mu maaso n’ebiyitibwamu mu kujjanjaba; noolwekyo, enkebera n’enzijanjaba nabyo bigenda bikyusibwamu.
Okugeza Ebigobererwa mu Kukebera n’Okujjanjaba CoVID-19 ebyayisibwa National Health Committee of the People’s Republic of China (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), wakati wa 16 Janwali 2020 ne 3 Ogwokusatu 2020, yaakafulumya enfulumya musanvu mulamba ng’embeera ezimu zikyukidde ddala.
Ebigobererwa byaffe byayogerwako Zhou ne banne, baateesa enkola ennyangu ey’okwekenneenya nga basinziira ku bye bazudde mu kujjanjaba mu ddwaliro.
Omulimu gwabwe gwayongera obukakafu ku bigobererwa byaffe era boogera ne ku kizibu kino ekiri mu nsi yonna.
Omulimu gwabwe omulungi tugukkiriza era tubeebaza.
Wabula, omulimu gwabwe nagwo gwetaaga okuzzibwa obuggya okusinziira ku Bigobererwa mu Kukebera n’Okujjanjaba COVID-19 ebipya (Olufulumya owomusanvu) n’okunoonyereza okupya.
Okusinziira ku lufulumya olwomusanvu (3 Ogwokusatu 2020), okukakasa omulwadde ateeberezebwa kyeetaagisa okugatta ekimu ku bigobererwa ebikwata ku byafaayo by’obulwadde n’ebigobererwa bibiri eby’ekisawo mu ddwaliro okusobola okukola okusalawo okw’enkomeredde, oba kyetaagisa okutuukiriza ebigobererwa bisatu eby’ekisawo mu ddwaliro singa waba tewali bikwata byafaayo bya bulwadde bitegeerekeka:
Ebyafaayo by’obulwadde: (1) okuba ng’omuntu yagendako oba yabeerako mu kibuga Wuhan n’ebitundu ebyetooloddewo, oba ebitundu ebirala ewaazuulwa abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu nnaku 14 ng’obubonero tebunneeyoleka; (2) okuba ng’omuntu yasemberera abantu abalina SARS-CoV-2 (mu kukebera kwa positive nucleic acid test); (3) okuba ng’omuntu yasemberera abalwadde b’omusujja oba abalina obuzibu bw’okussa okuva mu kibuga Wuhan n’ebitundu ebiriraanyeewo, oba ebitundu ebirala ewaazuulibwa abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu nnaku 14 ng’obubonero tebunneeyoleka; (4) okuba ng’omuntu yasemberera abalwadde abakakasiddwa (abalwadde ≥ 2 abalina omusujja ne/oba obuzibu mu kussa baazuulwa mu wiiki 2 mu bifo ebifunda, ng’awaka, woofiisi, ebibiina ku ssomero, n’ebirala).
Obubonero bw’ekisawo: (1) omusujja ne/ oba obuzibu mu kussa; (2) n’obubonero bw’okukubwa ekifaananyi obulaga okukosebwa COVID-19; (3) omuwendo gw’obutaffaali obulwanyisa endwadde (white blood cells) obulaga omuwendo gwa lymphocyte omulungi, oba ogukendedde mu kiseera ekisooka.
Okukakasa omulwadde kulina kukolebwa ku mulwadde ateeberezebwa ng’aliko obukakafu bw’obulwadde oba okukeberwa amazzi g’omubiri nga bwe kiragiddwa wammanga: (1) ng’okukebera kwa PCR okw’embagirawo kulaze nti omuntu alina SARS-CoV-2; (2) nga viral whole genome sequencing eraze okufaanana okw’amaanyi n’obuwuka bwa coronaavirus obupya; (3) ng’okukebera amazzi g’omu mubiri kulaze nti omuntu alina IgM antibody ne IgG antibody zennyini ezirwanyisa SARS-CoV-2; oba okukyuka kwa lgG antibody za SARS-CoV-2 zennyini okuva ku negative okudda ku positive, oba titer rising ez’emirundi ≥4 mu kiseera ky’okuwona okusinga ku ezo ez’omu kiseera ky’okubeera obubi.
Tulaba nti okukebera kwa PCR okw’embagirawo okuzuula nucleic acid mu mussizo oba omusaayi kwagattibwa ku lufulumya olwokubiri (18 Janwali 2020) n’olw’okusatu (22 Janwali 2020).
Okuzuula obulwadde mu sampolo y’omusaayi kwagattibwa ku nfulumya olwokuna (27 Janwali 2020) n’olwokutaano (8 Ogwokubiri 2020); ate obukakafu bw’okukebera amazzi g’omu mubiri bwagattibwa ku lufulumya olwomusanvu.
Okukyusaamu kuno kwesigamizibwa ku mirimu gy’abanoonyereza okugezaako okufuna ekintu ekiyinza okukenga obulungi nucleic acid olw’okukebera okw’amangu, awamu ne sampolo okuva mu mussizo omuli sampolo z’omusaayi, nga kino kyayongera ku busobozi bw’okufuna ebikeberwa eby’enjawulo, era ne kiwagira eky’okubeera ne antibody zennyini ng’ekimu ku bisinziirwako okukakasa omulwadde.
Ng’oggyeeko ekyo, waliwo obukakafu obulala bungi obutujjukiza okwegendereza abalwadde abalaga n’abatalaga bubonero mu ngeri etali ya bulijjo.
Noolwekyo, ekipande kya Zhou ne banne kisaanye okuzzibwa obuggya, kubanga kyalaga omuntu atalina bubonero bwa bulwadde nga “alina emikisa emitono (low risk)”.
Enkebera eno (score system) era yeetaaga okukakasibwa mu kujjanjaba okulala mu malwaliro ne mu kunoonyereza okulala.
Mu kuwumbawumba, tusuubira nti obukakafu obulala obulabikirawo bujja kulabikawo era tusaba abasomi okubwogerako.
Mu kumanya “ateeberezebwa” ne “akakasiddwa”, tuteesa eky’okulondoola n’okugondera ebiragiro ebikyasembyeyo eby’amawanga gaawe.
Tiimu yaffe ejja kuzza obuggya mu budde ebigobererwa byaffe okusobola okuyambako.
Bangladesh etegeezezza nti abantu bataanu abalala bafudde olwa COVID-19, nga gwe muwendo omunene ogusinga ku bafa buli lunaku
Eggulo, Bangladesh yakakasizza nti abantu bataano abalala baafudde olwa COVID-19 ku lunaku olwo.
Guno gwe muwendo ogusingayo obunene mu lunaku abafudde olw’akawuka kano.
We bwatuukidde eggulo, Ekitongole kya Bangladesh Institute of Epidemiology, Disease Control and Research (IEDCR) kyawandiise abalwadde 114 ate abawonye 33 nga bo bali waka.
Omugatte gw’abantu 17 abafudde.
Mu mawulire agaaweereddwa ku yintaneeti, omukungu wa IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, yagambye nti abaafudde baabaddemu abasajja bana n’omukyala omu.
Okusinziira ku Dr Meerjady, abaafudde ababiri baabadde n’emyaka egisukka mu 60, ababiri nga bali wakati wa 51 ne 60, ate omu ng’ali wakati wa 41-50 egy’obukulu.
Era yagambye nti ababiri ku bantu abo bava Dhaka.
Nga 11 Ogwokusatu, Ekitongole kya World Health Organization (WHO) kyalangirira COVID-19 ng’ekizibu eky’awamu mu nsi (pandemic).
Omukungu mu ddwaliro yategeeza Anadolu Agency, nga kitongole ky’amawulire, nti omu ku baafa ye yali Jalal Saifur Rahman, omukungu wa Bengali Anti-Corruption Commission, eyali ajjanjabibwa mu Kuwait Maitree Hospital.
Ku Lwomukaaga, Minista w’Ebyentambula mu Bangladeshi Obaidul Quader bwe yabadde ng’ayisa ekirango ekyalabikidde mu viidiyo yagambye nti entambula yonna ey’olukale egenda kuyimirizibwa okumala ebbanga ggwanvuko okusinga bwe baasooka okutegeka, okutuusa ku Lwomukaaga oluddako.
Okuyimiriza entambula y’olukale kwali kutandise nga 26 Ogwokusatu era nga kwali kutegekeddwa kukoma nga 4 Ogwokuna.
Entambula y’ebyamaguzi ebikulu -- eddagala, amafuta n’emmere - yo yali ekyakkirizibwa.
Abalwadde ba COVID-19 abaasooka mu Bangladesh baalabika nga 8 Ogwokusatu, nga baali bantu babiri abadda mu ggwanga eryo nga bava Italy ate n’omukyala w’omu ku bantu abo.
Nga 19 Ogwokusatu 19, abasatu abo baali bamaze okuwona.
SARS-CoV-2 yasussa abantu abalwadde akakadde kamu mu nsi yonna
Ku Lwokuna, omugatte gw’abalwadde ba SARS-CoV-2 coronavirus baasusse akakadde akamu mu nsi yonna nga bwe kyalagiddwa mu bubaka bwa Johns Hopkins University.
Waakiri abantu emitwalo 52 baagambibwa okuba nga bafudde COVID-19, obulwadde obuleetebwa coronavirus.
Kino kyatuukibwako ku lunaku lwe lumu Malawi lwe yakakasa omulwadde waayo asooka ate mu kiseera kye kimu Zambia n’efunayo omuntu omu afa olwa coronavirus.
North Korea yo yagambye nti ku Lwokuna y’emu ku nsi ezaali zikyasigadde nga tezinnalumbibwa bulwadde bwa coronavirus.
Ku lunaku lw’eggulo Ekibiina ky’Ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna (World Health Organization) kyategeezezza nti waabaddewo abalwadde 1,051,635 omuli abalwadde 79,332 abaafunise mu bbanga lya ssaawa 24 obutasukka ssaawa nnya ez’oku makya, mu mbala y’essaawa eya Central European Time (0800 UTC) nga 4 Ogwokuna.
Mu United States, abalwadde abasukka mu 244,000 be baategeezebwa ate ng’abafudde bali waakiri 5,900.
CBS News kyajulizza Johns Hopkins University ne kigamba nti, mu US mwalimu abantu abasukka 1,000 abaafudde ku Lwokusatu nga bafudde lwa bulwadde bwa coronavirus.
Mu nsi yonna, amawanga gaalangirira ebirina okukolebwa ebikakali olw’okuziyiza obulwadde obutasaasaana.
Ku Lwokuna, Sergei Sobyanin, meeya wa Moscow, yayongezzaayo omuggalo gw’ekibuga okutuusa nga 1 Ogwokutaano.
Mu ggwanga lyonna, Pulezidenti Vladimir Putin yalangirira nti Abarasha bajja kusasulwa wadde nga tebagenda ku mirimu gyabwe okutuusa nga 30 Ogwokuna.
Paliyamenti ya Portugal yakuba akalulu akongezaayo akaseera k’obwerende ka nnaku 15; abasinga obungi 215 baakawagira, kkumi ne batakuba ate omuntu omu n’atakiwagira.
Saudi Arabia yayongezaayo ekiseera kya kaafiyu mu bibuga ebitukuvu ebya Mecca ne Medina nga kimala olunaku lulamba; mu kusooka, kaafiyu yaliwo wakati wa ssaawa 9 ez’olweggulo ne 12 ez’oku makya.
Thailand yateekateeka kaafiyu wakati w’essaawa 4 ez’ekiro ne 10 ez’ekiro.
Gavana wa Ohio, Mike DeWine, yalangirira nti ekitundu ekyo kyongezzaayo ekiseera ky’okubeera ewaka okutuuka nga 1 Ogwokutaano.
Amaduuka g’omu Australia gassa ekkomo ku muwendo gw’ebikookooma omuntu by’alina okugula omulundi ogumu
Ku Ssande ne ku Lwomukaaga olweggulo, amaduuka g’omu Australia agabuna eggwanga lyonna, Woolworths ne Coles bassa ekkomo lyabwe ku bigulibwa ku bikookooma ng’omuntu agula obuganda bubiri oba kamu wonna mu ggwanga mu maduuka ago gombiriri.
ALDI nayo yassaawo ekkomo lya kaganda kamu ku Lwokusooka.
Okukugira kuno kwalagibwa ng’obubaka eri abantu ku miko gya Facebook egy’amakampuni ago.
Abaguzi baagambibwa okubeera nga beeterekera olw’okutya COVID-19 ng’abantu kibeetaagisizza okweyawula.
Ku Lwokusatu, Woolworths nayo yassa ekkomo ku kugula ebikookooma ebigulibwa ne biweerezebwa ewaka ng’omuntu afuna akaganda kamu buli lunaku.
Enkyukakyuka zino zigoberera okukugira okwasooka okw’akaganda ak’obuna ku buli lugula okwaleetebwa Woolworths ne Coles nga 4 ne 5 Ogwokusatu mu makampuni gombi mu ngoberegana eyo.
Mu kiwandiiko kya Coles ekya nga 8 Ogwokusatu, yategeeza nti okukugira okw’akaganda ak’ebina, "amaduuka mangi gamazaawo mu ssaawa emu yokka we babireetera", era ne bagamba nti obwetaavu obwo “tebubangawo”, so ng’ate yo ALDI, bwe yawandiika ku Facebook ku Lwokubiri yagamba nti kyali "tekisuubirwa".
Obutunzi “bwalinnyira ddala waggulu” mu wiiki ewedde okusinziira ku mwogezi wa Woolworths.
Edduuka lya Costco mu Canberra nalyo lyakugira omuwendo ogukkirizibwa ku buganda bubiri mu wiiki ewedde.
Okusobola okukendeeza ku bbula, Coles yasaba ababaweereza bakole obuganda obuneneko era ne bongeza ne ku mirundi gye babaweereza, Woolworths yalagira eyongerwe ku bye yalina, ate ALDI yaleeta ebirala nga bwe yateekateeka ku Lwokusatu olw’enjawulo bituuke nga bukyali.
Russell Zimmerman, omukungu atwala ekibiina ky’abatunzi ba lejjalejja ekya Australian Retailers Association, yagamba nti aba lejjalejja bagezaako okwongeza ku bye batereka okutunda naye okukugira kw’abakulembeze b’ekitundu ku bungi bw’emmotoka ezireeta kwabakaluubiriza.
Asuubira okulinnyisa omuwendo gw’ensimbi ezikozesebwa, ng’ababaweereza bwe bagezaako okutuukana n’obwetaavu obuliwo ate n’ennaku ez’enjawulo entono.
Ku Lwokubiri, ALDI yalangirira nti nga bagoberera okufulumya ebiterekebwa okutundibwa amangu, amaduuka agamu tegasobola kukola kya njawulo kya Lwakusatu.
Mu alipoota ya News.com.au, Dr Gary Mortimer, omukugu mu kutunda ebya lejjalejja okuva mu Queensland University of Technology, yagamba nti amaduuka galeeta eby’okutunda buli kiro.
Yagamba nti ebikookooma biba binene, ekireetera ebiterekebwa mu maduuka okutundibwa okubeera ebitono mu muwendo, ne kiba nti bwe bitundibwa ne biggwaawo, amasa agasigala nga makalu gaba mangi ne kireetawo okuwulira nti waliwo ebbula.
Russell Zimmerman yagamba mu mawulire ga ABC News nti "Coles ne Woolworths balowooza [nti] bwe waba nga waliwo ebintu bingi mu masa, ebyamaguzi ng’obuganda bw’ebikookooma n’ebinaaba mu ngalo [bigulibwa] ne bibaawo mu bungi, okupakuka kuyinza okukendeezebwa " .
Omu ku bakozi b’ebikookooma ateerya mu ntama yagamba ku Lwokusatu nti ebikookooma byali biweddewo.
Kimberly-Clark, abakola Ebikookooma, ne Solaris Paper abakola Sorbent, bakkaatiriza nti baali bakola 24/7 okulaba nti bavuganya n’obwetaavu, okusinziira ku alipoota ya News.com.au.
Omukutu gwa yintanenti Domain.com, ogutunda ettaka n’ebizimbe baagamba nti waliwo abatunzi abagaba ebikookooma eby’obwereere ku muwanguzi asooka ow’oku nnyondo mu Melbourne, nga waliwo obutunzi bw’oku nnyondo obutono olw’okuba nti abaguzi baalina obudde okuwummula ku nkomerero ya wiiki eyali empanvu omuli n’Olunaku lw’Abakozi.
Mu mawuilre g’oku Lwokuna ku NT News, olupapula olufulumira mu Darwin buli lunaku, mwalimu akatabo akasonsekebwamu nga ka miko munaana nga kalina kuggyibwamu ne kakozesebwa ng’ebikookooma.
Amaduuka mu kusooka gaagaana okussaawo ekkomo, okusinziira ku alipoota okuva mu ABC Australia nga 3 Ogwokusatu nga muno baagamba nti baali tebateekateeka kussa kkomo ku bigulibwa.
Russell Zimmerman yayongeddeko nti ebyamaguzi nabyo biri ku ttunzi omwo nga mwe muli obukookolo, ebinaaba mu ngalo, emmere enkalu, ssabbuuni w’omu ngalo n’obuwunga.
Mu ngeri y’emu, ebweru wa Australia, ekawungeezi ku Ssande Ssemaduuka w’oku yintaneeti Ocado yalabibwa ng’akugira okugula ebikookooma eby’ekika kya Andres ng’omuntu agula ebiri wakati wa 2 n’akaganda akalimu 12.
Ekitongole ky’Ebyobulamu eky’Ensi yonna (WHO) kirangirira COVID-19 ng’ekizibu ky’ensi yonna
Ku Lwokusatu, World Health Organization (WHO) yalangirira okubalukawo kwa COVID-19 — ng’endwadde ereetebwa akawuka akayitibwa coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 — ng’ekizibu eky’ensi yonna.
Newankubadde ng’ekigambo "ekizibu eky’ensi yonna" kitegeeza butegeeza engeri obulwadde gye busaasaanye, so si kutegeeza ngeri balwadde abamu gye bali ab’obulabe, WHO yalaga nti gavumenti zisaana okwesowalayo zibeeko kye zikola:
"Ensi zonna zisobola okukyusa engeri ekizibu kino eky’ensi yonna gye kisaasaanamu.
Singa ensi zikenga, zikebera, zijjanjaba, zaawula, zirondoola era ne zikunga abantu ku nsonga eno," bye bigambo by’Omukungu wa WHO, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus.
"Tuwulira nga tukwatiddwako nnyo olw’engeri obulwadde buno gye busaasaanamu ate n’obulabe bwabwo era n’obuteefiirayo obuyitiridde."
Okusinziira ku Dr. Tom Frieden eyali Ssenkulu w’Ekitongole kya America Ekirwanyisa Endwadde (CDC) yagamba nti ekizibu kino "kyali tekisuubirwa."
Yagamba, mu bigambo ebyafulumira ku CNN mu Gwokubiri nti, "ng’oggyeeko yegu, tewali kawuka kalala kalumba muyungiro gwa kussa kaali kalondoddwa okuva lwe kabalukawo okutuusa lwe kabuna wonna mu nsi."
Ghebreyesus naye yawa ekirowoozo kye kimu, n’agamba nti "tetulabangako ku kizubu kya nsi yonna kireetebwa kawuka ka coronavirus."
Yeeyongera okugamba nti, "era tetulabanga ku kizibu kya nsi yonna kisobola kuziyizibwa."
Ekifo ekipya eky’ekizibu ky’ensi yonna kyajja luvannyuma lwa kitongole kya WHO okusalawo mu Janwali okulangirira okubalukawo kw’obulwadde obwo ng’ekizibu ky’ebyobulamu mu bantu bonna ekikwatibwako ensi yonna.
Ye omukulu w’ekitongole ki United States' National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Disease, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yayogera ku kubalukawo kuno nga, "ekitabuusibwabuusibwa kyekino, kigenda kusajjuka."
Olwokuna we lwatuukira, Associated Press kyo kyategeeza nti waaliwo waakiri abalwadde ba COVOID-19 abawera 126,000 mu nsi yonna, nga mu bo 4,600 baafa.
Ekizibu ky’ensi yonna ekya coronavirus 2019–20 kizibu ekigenda mu maaso eky’obulwadde bwa 2019 (COVID-19), ekireetebwa akawuka akalumba omuyungiro gw’okussa akayitibwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ekizibu kino kyalabibwa mu Wuhan, China, mu Deesemba 2019, ne kirangirirwa ng’ekizibu ky’ebyobulamu mu bantu nga 30 Janwali 2020, ate ne kirabibwa ng’ekizibu ky’ensi yonna nga 11 Ogwokusatu 2020.
Nga 10 Ogwokuna 2020, abalwadde abakunukkiriza mu kakadde 1.61 aba COVID-19 bategeezeddwa mu mawanga ne mu bifo 210 era n’abantu nga 97,000 bafudde.
Abantu nga 364,000 bawonye.
Ekigero ky’abalwadde abafudde kiteeberezebwa okuba ebitundu 4% mu China, ate mu nsi yonna kiri ebitundu 13.04% mu Algeria ne .08% mu New Zealand.
Obubonero obusinga okulabika buzingiramu olusujja, okukolola n’okubaka omukka.
Obuzibu bw’obulwadde buno buyinza okuzingiramu lubyamira n’obuzibu obw’amaanyi mu muyungiro gw’okussa.
Ekiseera okuva ku kukwatibwa obulwadde n’okulaga obubonero kiri awo nga mu nnaku ttaanu naye nga kiva ku nnaku bbiri okutuuka ku kkumi na nnya.
Tewali ddagala ligema limanyiddwa oba ddagala lirwanyisa kawuka kano mu bujjanjabi.
Obujjanjabi obusookerwako bukola ku bubonero na kuyamba okutonotono. Ebisembebwa okukolebwa okwetangira obulwadde mulimu, okunaaba mu ngalo, okubikka ku mimwa ng’okolola, okwewa ebbanga okuva ku balala, okulondoola n’okweyawula oli bw’aba ng’alowooza nti obulwadde abulina.
Aboobuyinza mu nsi yonna baanukudde nga bassaawo okukugira ku ntambula, kalantiini, kaafiyu, okwegendereza ku mirimu n’okuggalawo ebifo ebimu.
Nawookeera ono ataataaganyizza ebyobulamu n’ebyenfuna y’abantu mu nsi yonna, okwongezaayo oba okusazaamu ebyemizannyo, emikolo gy’eddiini, emikolo gy’ebyobufuzi n’ebyobuwangwa, wamu n’okuleetawo ebbula ly’ebintu ebimu erivudde ku bantu okugula ebintu nga babuguutana.
Amasomero ne yunivaasite byaggalawo ku mutendera gw’eggwanga lyonna oba mu bitundu mu mawanga 193, ne kikosa kumpi abayizi ebitundu 99.4 ku kikumi mu nsi yonna.
Obubaka obukyamu obukwata ku kawuka bubunye ku yintaneeti era wabaddewo emirundi gy’okulumbagana okw’obukyayi n’okusosola eri Abachaina, abantu abalala abava mu East ne Southeast Asia oba abo ababafaanana n’abalala abava mu bitundu omuli ennyo obulwadde bw’akawuka ako.
Olw’okuggalawo entambula n’amakolero amanene, wabaddewo okukendeera ku kwonoona kw’empewo n’okusaasaanya omukka omubi (carbon emissions).
Abeebyobulamu mu Wuhan, China (ekibuga ekikulu ekya Hubei province) baategeeza nti waaliwo abantu batonotono abaalina yegu atamanyiddwako w’ava nga 31 Deesemba 2019, era okunoonyereza ne kutandika ku ntandikwa ya Janwali 2020.
Abalwadde baalabibwa ng’abalina akakwate n’emmere y’omu nnyanja ey’e Huanan (Seafood Wholesale Market) awo nno akawuka kaalowoozebwa okuba nga kava mu nsolo ne kadda mu bantu.
Akawuka akaaleeta okubalukawo kw’ekirwadde kayitibwa SARS-CoV-2, nga kawuka kapya akaakazuulibwa akafaananako n’obw’omu buwundo obuyitibwa bat coronaviruses, pangolin coronaviruses, ne SARS-CoV. Omuntu eyasooka okweyolekerako obuboero yazuulibwa oluvannyuma nga yalwala nga 1 Deesemba 2019, ate ng’omuntu oyo teyazuulibwa nti yalina akakwate konna n’obutale omutundirwa ebintu ebibisi.
Ku balwadde abaasooka okutegeezebwa mu Deesemba 2019, ebitundu bibiri byakusatu ku bo baazuulibwa nga balina akakwate ku katale ako.
Nga 13 Ogwokusatu 2020, amawulire agataategeerekeka we gaava mu ggulire lya South China Morning Post gaategeeza nti omulwadde eyalwala emabega nga 17 Noovemba 2019, ow’emyaka 55 eyava mu Hubei province, ayinza okuba nga ye yasooka. Nga 26 Ogwokubiri 2020, WHO yategeeza ng’abalwadde abapya bwe bakendedde mu China naye ate amangu ddala ne beeyongera mu Italy, Iran, ne South Korea, omuwendo gw’abalwadde abapya abali ebweru wa China gwali gususse ku ogwo ogw’abalwadde abapya abali munda mu China omulundi ogusookedde ddala.
Kyandiba nga waaliwo obutayogera muwendo gw’abalwadde mutuufu naddala abo abalina obubonero obutali bwa maanyi.
Nga 26 Ogwokubiri, abalwadde batono abaali bategeezeddwa mu bavubuka ab’emyaka 19 n’okukka wansi abakola ebitundu 2.4% eby’abalwadde mu nsi yonna. Omukulu w’abawi b’amagezi ag’ekinnassaayansi mu Bungereza, Patrick Vallance, yateebereza nti ebitundu 60% eby’abantu mu Bungereza bayinza okufuna akawuka ako ng’obusibage obw’amaanyi tebunnaba kufunibwa mu bantu.
Abalwadde kitegeeza omuwendo gw’abantu abakebeddwa COVID-19, era okukebera ne kulaga nti balina akawuka okusinziira ku nseetuka entongole.
Nga 23 Ogwokusatu, tewali ggwanga lyali likebedde bantu baalyo basussa bitundu 3%, ate amawanga mangi balina enkola ey’obutakebera abo abeeyolekerako obubonero obutali bwa maanyi, gamba nga Italy, Netherlands, Spain, ne Switzerland.
Okunoonyereza okwafulumizibwa nga 16 Ogwokusatu kwalaga nti China, okutuusa nga 23 Janwali, abalwadde abakunukkiriza ebitundu 86% baali tebannaba kukengebwa, era nti abalwadde abo abaali tebannaba kuwandiikibwa be baali basiiga abalala ebitundu 79% abaali bawandiikiddwa.
Okwekaliriza okw’ebibalo okwafulumizibwa nga 30 Ogwokusatu kwateebereza nti omuwendo gw’abalwadde mu Italy gwali munene ddala okusinga ogwo ogwali gutegeezebwa.
Okuteebereza okwasooka okw’ennamba esookerwako ezaalukanya (R0) eya COVID-19 gwali 1.4 okutuuka ku 2.4.
Okunoonyereza okwafulumizibwa mu America ekitongole kya Center for Disease Control and Prevention kulaga nti ennamba eyo eyinza okuba 5.7.
Abantu abasinga abalwala COVID-19 bawona.
Eri abo abatawona, ekiseera okuva obubonero we butandikira okujja okutuuka okufa kiri wakati w’ennaku 6 okutuuka ku nnaku 41 naye ng’ezisinga mu bantu bonna ziri 14.
Nga 10 Ogwokuna 2020, abantu abakunukkiriza 97,000 bagambibwa nti baafa COVID-19.
Mu China, nga 5 Ogwokubiri abantu abaafa nga 80% baali mu abo abasussa emyaka 60, era ebitundu 75% baalina endwadde endala omuli obulwadde bw’omutima (cardiovascular diseases) ne sukaali. Emiwendo gy’abafu emitongole egya nawookeera wa COVID-19 okusinga ennyo gyogera ku baafa abaakeberwa nga balina COVID okusinziira ku nseetuka entongole.
Omuwendo gw’abantu gwennyini abafa COVID-19 guyinza okuba wagguluko kubanga guyinza obutabeeramu bantu bafa nga tebakebeddwa - okugeza ewaka, mu maka g’abalabirira abakadde, n’ewalala.
Obubaka obw’ekitundu okuva mu Italy bwazuula nti omuwendo gw’abafu ogusukkamu mu kiseera kya nawookeera gwasukka ogwo omutongole ogwa COVID n’ennamba eyeekubisaamu emirundi 4-5.
Omukyala ayogerera U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) yakkiriza nti "Tukimanyi nti [omuwendo gw’abafa] tegulaga bituufu", bino twabikakasa n’okubuuliriza abantu mu America. Obutalaba bituufu kitera okubaawo mu biseera bya nawookeera gamba nga 2009 H1N1 swine flu. Omuntu eyasooka okukakasibwa nti afudde yali mu Wuhan nga 9 Janwali 2020.
Omuntu eyasooka okufa ebweru wa China yafa nga 1 Ogwokubiri mu Philippines, ate eyasooka okufa ebweru wa Asia yali mu France nga 14 Ogwokubiri.
Nga 28 Ogwokubiri, ebweru wa China, abantu abasukka mu 12 baafa mu buli limu ku mawanga gano, Iran, South Korea, ne Italy.
Nga 13 Ogwokusatu, amawanga n’ebifo ebisukka mu makumi ana byategeeza abantu abaali bafudde kumpi ku buli ssemazinga okuggyako Antarctica. Obukodyo bungi obutera okukozesebwa okubala omuwendo gw’abafa.
Emiwendo gino gikyuka okusinziira ku buli kitundu n’ebiseera eby’enjawulo era gyawukana olw’obungi bw’okukebera, omutindo gw’obujjanjabi, obujjanjabi obuliwo, ebbanga eriyiseewo okuva obulwadde lwe bwatandika, n’enfaanana y’abantu gamba ng’emyaka, ekikula, n’obulamu bwabwe okutwaliza awamu. Omuwendo gw’okufa bwe gugeraageranyizibwa n’abafa gulaga omuwendo gw’abafudde ng’ogabizzaamu ogw’abakebeddwa mu kiseera ekigere.
Okusinziira ku bibalo bya Johns Hopkins University, ekigero ky’abafa nga kigeraageranyizibwa n’abalwadde kiri 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) nga 10 Ogwokuna 2020.
Omuwendo gukyuka okusinziira ku kitundu.
Mu China, okuteebereza ekigero ky’abafa nga kigeraageranyizibwa n’abalwadde kyakendeera okuva ku 17.3% (ku abo abafuna obubonero ku ntandikwa 1–10 Janwali 2020) okutuuka ku 0.7% (ku abo abalaga obubonero ku ntandikwa oluvannyuma lwa 1 Ogwokubiri 2020). Obukodyo buzingiramu ekigero ky’abafa (CFR), ekiraga omuwendo ku kikumi ogw’abantu abakebeddwa abafa olw’obulwadde obumu, n’abo abakwatibwa obulwadde (IFR), ogulaga omuwendo ku kikumi ogw’abo abalwadde (abakebeddwa n’abatakebeddwa) abafa olw’obulwadde obumu.
Ebibalo bino tebikugira ku kiseera kyonna era bigoberera abantu abamu okuva lwe bakwatiddwa obulwadde okutuusa omulwadde lw’akolebwako.
Abanoonyereza abawerako bagezezzaako okubalirira emiwendo gy’abantu abamu.
Ekifo kya Yunivaasite ya Oxford ekya Centre for Evidence-Based Medicine kiteebereza nti abakwatibwa obulwadde bwa nawookera okutwaliza awamu bali wakati wa 0.1% ne 0.39%.
Omuwendo oguteeberezebwa ogwa waggulu mu kigero kino gukkaanya n’ebyava mu kukebera okwasooka okw’okulabira awo ku COVID-19 mu Germany, era okunoonyereza okw’ebibalo okwekaliriza okukebera kye kukola okuteebereza kw’abafa.
WHO kiteebereza nti ekizibu kino eky’ensi yonna kisobola okukugirwa.
Okutumbuka kw’obulwadde n’ebbanga lye buyinza okumala tebimanyiddwa era biyinza okwawukana okusinziira ku kifo.
Maciej Boni owa Penn State University yagamba, "Obulwadde obusiigibwa obubalukawo bwe butakugirwa, butumbiira ate ne butandika okukka obulwadde obwo bwe bubulwa kwe bwekwata.
Naye kumpi tekisoboka okukola okuteebereza mu kiseera kino ku kiseera kino lwe kiribeerawo".
Omuwi w’amagezi ow’oku ntikko mu Gavmenti ya China, Zhong Nanshan yagamba nti "busobola okuggwaawo Ogwomukaaga we gunaggweerawo" singa amawanga gonna gasobola okukubirizibwa okugoberera amagezi n’ebigobererwa bya WHO okukomya okusaasaanya akawuka.
Nga 17 Ogwokusatu, Adam Kucharski owa London School of Hygiene &amp; Tropical Medicine yagamba nti SARS-CoV-2 "bugenda kusaasaana, oboolyawo okumala omwaka mulamba oba ebiri".
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza kwa Imperial College okwakulemberwa Neil Ferguson, okwewa amabanga n’ebigobererwa ebirala bijja kwetaagisa "okutuusa ng’eddagala erigema lirabise (oboolyawo emyezi 18 oba n’okusingawo)".
William Schaffner owa Vanderbilt University yagamba nti, "Ndowooza nti akawuka kano aka coronavirus—olw’okuba nti kasaasaanyizibwa mangu—kajja kuggweerawo ddala "kayinza okufuukamu obulwadde obw’ekiseera nga kakomawo buli mwaka".
Obulabe bwako nga kakomyewo bujja kusinziira ku busibage obw’awamu n’obuzaalukanyi bwako.
Obubonero bwa COVID-19 busobola okubeera nga tebutegeerekeka bulungi era abantu abalwadde basobola obutalabikirako bubonero.
Obubonero obubiri obusinga okulabika mulimu olusujja (88%) n’ekifuba ekikalu (68%).
Obubonero obutatera kulabika buzingiramu ekimenyoomenyo, eminyira emingi, okutandika obutawunyiriza, okubaka omukka, okulumizibwa mu nnyingo, amabwa mu bulago, okulumwa omutwe, okuwulira empewo/okutya, okusesema, okusesema omusaayi (hemoptysis), embiro, oba cyanosis. WHO egamba nti omuntu omu ku bantu mukaaga alwalira ddala era n’azibuwalirwa mu kussa.
U.S. Centers for Diseases Control and Prevention (CDC) eraga obubonero obw’amangu ng’okubaka omukka, okulumizibwa mu kifuba okutatadde, okuwulira ng’otabuddwa embagirawo, okuzibuwalirwa okutambula, n’okumyukirira mu bwenyi oba ku mimwa; obujjanjabi obw’amangu bwetaagisa omuntu bw’afuna obubonero obwo. Obulwadde bwe bugenda mu maaso kisobola okuleeta yegu ow’amaanyi, okuzibikira omuyungiro gw’okussa (acute respiratory distress syndrome), sepsis, septic shock n’okufa.
Abamu ku balwadde bayinza obutalabikirako bubonero, nga tebalina bubonero naye bwe bakeberwa ne kikakasibwa nti balwadde, awo nno abanoonyereza bawadde amagezi nti abo abakwatagana n’abo abakakasiddwa nti balwadde balina okulondoolwa ennyo n’okwekalirizibwa okulaba nti tebalina bulwadde.
Okuteebereza kw’Eggwanga lya China okw’ekigero ky’obubonero kuli wakati w’abatono ne 44%.
Ekiseera ky’okulaga obubonero (ekiseera okuva omuntu w’afunira akawuka okutuuka obubonero we bweyolekera) kitera okuva ku lunaku lumu okutuuka ku nnaku 14; kisinga kubeera ennaku ttaano. Ekyokulabirako ekiraga obutabaawo bukakafu, okuteebereza omuwendo gw’abantu ababa ne COVID-19 ne baba nga tebakyasobola kuwunyiza mu kusooka gwali ebitundu 30% ate oluvannyuma ne gukka ku 15%.
Ebimu ku bikwata ku ngeri obulwadde gye busaasaanamu tebinnaba kutegeerwa.
Obulwadde bulowoozebwa okubeera nga busaasaanira mu abo abakwataganye n’abalwadde wamu n’okukwatibwako oluzzizzi olusaasaanyizibwa ng’omuntu akolola, ayasimula oba ayogera; era ng’okukwatagana okwo kuli wakati wa mmita 1 okutuuka ku 2 (fuuti 3 ku 6).
Okunoonyereza kulaze nti okukolola ng’oli tabisse ku mimwa kuleeta oluzzizzi okutambulira mu bbanga lya mmita 4.5 (fuuti 15 feet) okutuuka 8.2 (fuuti 27t).
Abamu bagambye nti akawuka era kasobola okusaasaanyizibwa n’oluzzizzi olusigala mu bbanga okumala ebbanga eriwerako, oluyinza okufulumizibwa mu kwogera. Oluzzizzi oluva mu kussa nalwo luyinza okufulumizibwa mu kussa omwo nga mwe muli ne mu kiseera ky’okwogera, wadde ng’akawuka ako okutwaliza awamu tekatambulira mu mpewo.
Oluzzuzzi lusobola okugenda mu kamwa oba mu nnyindo z’abantu abali okumpi oba n’okusikibwa ne lugenda mu mawuggwe.
Obujjanjabi obumu gamba ng’okussibwamu akapiira ne cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR) buyinza okuleetera okuvaamu oluzzi mu mussizo ne lufuluma bwe kityo obulwadde ne busaasaanira mu mpewo.
Kasobola era okusaasaana omuntu bw’akwata ku kintu ekyagenzeeko obuwuka omwo nga mwe muli omubiri, ate n’akwata mu maaso, mu nnyingo oba mu kamwa.
Weewaawo waliwo okutya nti kayinza okusaasaanira mu bubi, obulabe buno bulowoozebwa okuba wansi.
Gavumenti ya China yawakanya obusobozi bwa SARS-CoV-2 okusaasaanira mu bubi. Akawuka kasinga kusaasaanira mu nnaku essatu ezisooka ng’obubonero bwakalabika weewaawo ng’okusaasaana kuyinza okusoboka ng’obubonero tebunnalabika ate ne mu mitendera egisembayo egy’akawuka.
Abantu bakebeddwa ne basangibwa n’obulwadde nga wayiseewo ennaku ssatu nga tebannalabikirako bubonero ekiraga nti okusaasaana kusoboka wadde ng’obubonero obw’amaanyi buba tebunnalabika.
Alipoota ntono eziraga nti waliwo abalwadde abakakasibwa nga tebeeyolekerako bubonero, naye ng’okusaasaanya akawuka akava mu bateeyolekerako bubonero kulabiddwa mu mawanga agamu nga balondoola okukwatagana kw’omuntu omulwadde n’abantu abalala.
Ekitongole kya European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC) kigamba nti weewaawo tekitangaala bulungi ngeri bulwadde gye busaasaanamu, okutwaliza awamu omuntu omu asiiga abantu wakati w’ababiri okutuuka ku basatu. Akawuka kabeera kalamu nga kali ku bintu okumala essaawa n’ennaku eziwera.
Okusingira ddala, akawuka kaazuulwa okubeera nga kakengebwa okumala ennaku ssatu ku bintu ebya pulaasitiika (polypropylene) ne ku situula ow’ekigero kya 304, okumala olunaku lumu ku cardboard n’okumala essaawa nnya ku kkopa.
Wabula, kino kyawukana okusinziira ku luzzizzi oluli mu mpewo ne ku bbugumu. Obusolo bw’awaka n’ensolo nazo zikebeddwa ne zisangibwa ne COVID-19.
Tewali bubaka bulaga nti ensolo zisobola okusiiga abantu akawuka, wadde ng’aboobuyinza mu Bungereza bawa abantu amagezi okunaaba mu ngalo nga bamaze okukwata ku nsolo, ng’era bwe kiri ku kukwata ku bintu abantu abateeberezebwa okuba abalwadde bye baba bakutteko.
Akawuka akayitibwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) kawuka akabadde tekamanyiddwa, akaasooka okulabibwa mu bantu basatu abaalina yegu eyeekwanya ku oyo ow’amaanyi akosa omuyungiro gw’okussa eyalabibwa mu Wuhan.
Obubonero bwonna obw’akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 akaali tekamanyiddwa bubeera mu buwuka bwa coronaviruses obukafaanana mu nkula. Ebweru w’omubiri gw’omuntu akawuka ako kattibwa ne ssabbuuni akozesebwa ewaka, ssabuuni oyo atta olububi olukuuma akawuka. SARS-CoV-2 kafaanagana nnyo n’ako ka SARS-CoV akaasooka okulabibwa.
Kasuubirwa okuba nga kava mu nsolo ne kadda mu bantu.
Okwekaliriza kw’endagabutonde kulaze nti coronavirus mu nkula yaako ey’endagabutonde kafaananako ne genus Betacoronavirus, mu subgenus Sarbecovirus (lineage B) wamu ne bat-derived strains za mirundi ebiri.
Bufaanagana ebitundu 96% ku mutendera gwa genome gwonna n’obuwuka obulala obw’obuwundo mu sampolo zaabwo (BatCov RaTG13).
Mu Gwokubiri 2020, abanoonyereza ba China baazuula nti waliwo amino acid emu yokka mu bitundu ebimu ebya genome sequences wakati w’obuwuka obuva mu pangolins n’obwo obuva mu bantu.
Okutuusa leero, okugeraageranya kwa genome kwonna okusinga ennyo kuzudde nti ebitundu 92% eby’ebitundu by’endagabutonde ebigabanwa wakati wa pangolin coronavirus ne SARS-CoV-2, ekitamala kukakasa nti pangolin kwe kubeera akawuka ng’ekitasaasaanya.
Okubeera n’akawuka kisobola okulabirwa ku bubonero ng’ekisookerwako, naye ng’okukakasa kukolebwa na reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) mu bifa mu mubiri ebikoseddwa oba mu bifaananyi bya kompyuta (CT imaging).
Okunoonyereza okugeraageranya PCR ku CT mu Wuhan kulaze nti okukozesa CT kulimu nnyo okwegendereza okusinga PCR, wadde nga kyo tekiraga bulungi nsonga, era ng’ebitundu by’ekifaananyi biba bibulira mu yegu omulala n’endwadde endala.
Mu Gwokusatu 2020, American College of Radiology yali ekyasemba nti "CT erina kukozesebwa kusunsula oba kukozesebwa ng’okukebera okusookerwako okukebera COVID-19".
WHO kyafulumya enseetuka z’okukebera RNA ku SARS-CoV-2, ng’eyasooka yafulumizibwa nga 17 Janwali.
Okukebera kukozesa real-time reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR).
Okukebera kusobola okukolebwa ku sampolo z’omu muyungiro gw’okussa oba ku musaaayi.
Okutwaliza awamu, ebivaamu birabikira mu bbanga eriri wakati w’essaawa ntono n’ennaku.
Okutwaliza awamu, okukebera kuno kukolebwa ku swab eya nasopharyngeal wadde nga swab ey’omu mumiro nayo eyinza okukozesebwa. Amagezeserezo mangi ne kampuni bikulaakulanya okukebera kw’omusaayi okukenga abasirikale b’omubiri.
Nga 6 Ogwokuna 2020, tewali na kimu ku bino kyali kirabiddwa nga kikola bulungi mu ngeri ya kinnassaayansi okusobola okukakasibwa kikozesebwe wonna.
Mu America okukebera kw’omusaayi okwakulaakulanyizibwa Cellex kukakasiddwa okukozesebwa mu kaseera ak’amangu mu magezeserezo agaakakasibwa gokka.
Obubonero bw’ebifaananyi ku radiographs ne CT y’abantu abeeyolekerako obubonero mulimu asymmetric peripheral ground glass opacities ne absent pleural effusions.
Ekitongole kya Italy ekya Italian Radiological Society kiri ku kaweefube wa kukola kkuŋŋaanyizo ly’oku yintaneeti ery’ebifaananyi ebizuuliddwa mu bantu abakakasiddwa nga balwadde.
Olw’okukwatagana n’endwadde endala nga adenovirus, okukuba ebifaananyi awatali kukakasa na PCR tekusobola kukakasiza ddala mu kuzuula COVID-19.
Okunooonyereza okunene mu China kwageraageranya ebiva mu kukozesa CT ey’omu kifuba ne PCR era kiraga nti newankubadde okukuba ekifaananyi tekulagira ddala kituufu ku bulwadde, nga kiraga nti kyetaaga okufaako ng’ekikozesebwa mu kusunsula mu bifo ebirimu obulwadde.
Network eziyitibwa Artificial intelligence-based convolutional neural networks zikoleddwa okukenga obukole bw’ebifaananyi by’akawuka nga zikozesa radiographs ne CT.
Enkola z’okuziyiza okusaasaanya kw’obulwadde mulimu okukuuma obuyonjo mu buli kimu, okunaaba mu ngalo, okwewala okukwata mu maaso, mu nnyindo, oba emimwa nga tonaabye mu ngalo, n’okukolola oba okwasimula mu kagoye oba ekipapula ate n’okiteeka butereevu mu kisuulibwamu kasasiro.
Abo abayinza okuba nga balwadde baweereddwa amagezi okwambala akakookolo nga batambudde okuva ewaka.
Okwesuula amabanga nakwo kusembebwa okwewala okusaasaanya obulwadde. Gavumenti nnyingi zikugidde oba ziwadde amagezi abantu okwewala okutambula okuggyako nga tekyebeereka okugenda oba okuva mu bitundu ebikoseddwa obulwadde.
Wabula, akawuka katuuse ku ssa ly’okusaasaanira mu kitundu ekiramba mu bitundu by’amawanga bingi mu nsi yonna.
Kino kitegeeza nti akawuka kasaasaanira mu bitundu, ate abantu abamu mu bitundu tebamanyi wa oba ngeri gye baakosebwamu. Abajjanjabi/abasawo abalabirira omuntu ayinza okuba omulwadde baweebwa amagezi okwegendereza, okukwatagana n’omuntu n’obwegendereza, n’okubikka amaaso. Okulondoola abantu omuntu b’akwataganye nabo kakodyo kakulu eri abeebyobulamu okumanya eyavuddeko obulwadde ate n’okwewala okwongera okusaasaanya obulwadde.
Gavumenti okukozesa obubaka bw’ekifo omuntu w’ali okuva ku ssimu z’omu ngalo olw’ensonga eno kireeseewo okwekengera ku nsonga z’ebyama ng’ekitongole kya Amnesty International n’ebitongole ebirala ebisukka mu 100 nga bifulumya ebiwandiiko okulaga ekkomo ku bulondoozi obw’engeri eyo.
Apps ez’enjawulo ez’amasimu g’omu ngalo zikozeseddwa oba ziteeseddwa okukozesebwa mu ngeri ya nakyewa, era okuva nga 7 Ogwokuna 2020, ebibinja by’abakungu ebisukka mu 20 byali bisala amagezi ku nsonga z’ebyama gamba ng’okukozesa Bluetooth okuyunga omukozesa w’essimu ku masimu amalala.
Abakozesa bafuna obubaka bwe baba nga babadde basemberedde omuntu eyakebeddwa n’azuulibwa ng’alina COVID-19. Obubaka obubuzaabuza butambula wonna ku ngeri y’okuziyiza obulwadde; okugeza, okunaaba amazzi mu nnyindo n’okumunyunguza amazzi mu kamwa naye ebyo byonna tebikola.
Tewali ddagala ligema COVID-19, wadde ng’ebitongole bingi bikola butaweera okulikola.
Okunaaba mu ngalo kusembebwa okuziyiza okusaasaana kw’obulwadde.
CDC kiwa abantu amagezi okunaaba mu ngalo ne ssabbuuni n’amazzi buli kiseera okumala waakiri eddakiika 20, naddala nga bagenze mu kaabuyonjo oba engalo bwe ziba nga ddala zirabika nga ziddugala; nga tebannaba kulya; n’oluvannyuma ng’omuntu amaze okunyiza, okukolola oba okwasimula.
Kino kiri bwe kityo lwa nsonga nti ebweru w’omubiri gw’omuntu, akawuka kattibwa ne sabbuuni akozesebwa ewaka, sabbuuni atta olususu lw’akawuka.
CDC kyongera ne kisemba okukozesa amazzi kattabuwuka omuli omwenge gwa bitundu waakiri 60% sabbuuni n’amazzi bwe biba nga tebiriiwo.
WHO kiwa abantu amagezi okwewala okukwata mu maaso, ennyindo, oba emimwa n’engalo ezitannaba kunaabwa.
Kungulu ku bintu kusobola okuggyibwako obuwuka nga tukozesa eddagala ly’amazzi ery’enjawulo (mu ddakiika emu ekintu bwe kiba nga kyakolebwa mu steel era nga kikwatiddwako omuntu omulwadde), omwo nga mwe muli ebitundu 62–71% ebya ethanol, 50–100% isopropanol, 0.1% sodium hypochlorite, 0.5% hydrogen peroxide, ne 0.2–7.5% povidone-iodine.
Eddagala ly’amazzi eddala, gamba nga benzalkonium chloride ne chrohexidine gluconate, terikola bulungi.
CDC kisemba nti omuntu bw’ateeberezebwa nti alina COVID oba n’akakasibwa nti amulina ku kifo gamba nga ku wofiisi oba ewalabirirwa abaana, ebifo byonna gamba nga wofiisi, ebinaabiro, ebifo eby’olukale, ebintu by’amasannyalaze ebigabanibwa gamba nga tablet, touch screens, amapeesa, limooti, ne ATM machine ebikozeseddwa omuntu omulwadde, birina okuggyibwako obuwuka.
Ebitongole by’ebyobulamu bisemba abantu okubikka emimwa gyabwe n’ennyindo nga bakozesa omukono ogufunyiddwa oba akapapula (tissue) amangu ddala.
Obukookolo busembebwa eri abo abayinza okuba nga balwadde, kubanga okwambala akakookolo kiyinza okukugira ebbanga n’obungi bw’oluzzizzi omuntu lw’afulumya ng’ayogera, ng’anyiza n’okukolola.
WHO kiwadde ebiragiro ku kiseera n’engeri omuntu gy’alina okukozesa obukookolo.
Okusinziira ku Stephen Griffin, omunoonyereza ku buwuka mu University of Leeds, agamba nti "Okwambala akakookolo kusobola okukendeeza ku busobosi bw’abantu okwekwata mu maaso ate nga y’ensibuko y’okusaasaanya obulwadde esinga ng’omuntu tanaaba bulungi ngalo. “Obukookolo era busembebwa okukozesebwa omuntu ajjanjaba omutnu ayinza okuba ng’alina obulwadde.
WHO kisemba abantu abalamu okwambala obukookolo awo wokka nga bali mu kiseera kya bulabe bungi gamba ng’oyo ajjanjaba omuntu omulwadde wa COVID-19, weewaawo ng’era bakkiriza nti okwambala obukookolo kuyinza okuyamba abantu okwewala okwekwata mu bwenyi.
Amawanga mangi gatandise okukubiriza abantu bonna okwambala obukookolo.
Mu America, CDC kisemba abantu okwambala akakookolo akatali ka kisawo akakoleddwa mu lugoye. China yo esemba okukozesa obukookolo bw’ekisawo obukozesebwa omulundi ogumu, naddala ng’omuntu agenda kusemberera abantu (mmita 1 (fuuti 3) oba obutawera).
Hong Kong esemba okwambala akakookolo ng’omuntu alinnya ebidduka eby’olukale oba bw’aba ng’abeera mu bifo ebirimu abantu abangi.
Ab’ebyobulamu mu Thailand bakubiriza abantu okukola obukookolo mu ngoye ewaka era babwoze buli lunaku.
Czech Republic ne Slovakia baagaana abantu okuva ewaka nga tebambadde kakookolo oba nga tebabisse nnyindo na mumwa.
Nga 16 Ogwokusatu, Vietnam yasaba buli omu okwambala akakookolo ng’agenda mu lujjudde olw’okwekuuma ate n’okukuuma abalala.
Gavumenti ya Austria yalagira nti buli muntu ayingira mu dduuka alina okwambala akakookolo.
Israel esabye buli mutuuze okwambala akakookolo buli lw’abeera mu lujjudde.
Taiwan, ebadde ekola obukookolo obuwera obukadde kkumi buli lunaku okuva mu Gwokusatu wakati, nga 1 Ogwokuna yalagira abasaabaze ku ggaali y’omukka ne bbaasi ezitambula mu bibuga okwambala obukookolo.
Panama ekifudde kya tteeka okwambala akakookolo buli omuntu lw’ava ewaka, ate ng’era bakubiriza n’abantu okwekolera obukookolo ewaka eri abo abatasobola kwegulira.
Obukookolo era bukozeseddwa nnyo mu Japan, South Korea, Malaysia, ne Singapore.
Okwewa amabanga kulimu ebikolebwa okwewala okusaasaanya obulwadde ng’okusemberera abantu abalala kukendeezebwa.
Ebikolebwa mulimu kalantiini; okukugira mu ntambula; n’okuggala amasomero, ebifo ebikolerwamu, ebisaawe, ebifo ebisanyukirwamu n’amaduuka.
Abantu kinnoomu basobola okwewa amabanga nga basigala ewaka, okukendeeza ku kutambula, okwewala ebifo ebirimu abantu abangi, okulamusa nga tokutte ku muntu, n’okwesuula abantu abalala.
Gavumenti nnyingi kati zikaka abantu mu bifo ebikoseddwa obulwadde okweyawula ku balala.
Omuwendo gw’abantu ogusingayo obunene ogusembebwa ebitongole bya gavumenti mu America n’ebitongole by’ebyobulamu gukendeeredde ddala okuva ku bantu 250 (bwe waba nga tewali bulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu kitundu) okutuuka ku bantu 50, ate n’oluvannyuma ku bantu 10 bokka.
Nga 22 Ogwokusatu 2020, Germany yasazaamu enkuŋŋaana ez’abantu abasukka mu babiri. Abantu abakuluko n’abo abalina obulwadde obulala nga sukaali, obulwadde bw’omutima, obulwadde bw’omuyungiro gw’okussa, puleesa n’obusibage obutakola bulungi bali ku bulabe bwa maanyi era baweebwa amagezi ekitongole kya CDC okubeera ewaka nga bwe kisoboka naddala nga bali mu bitundu ebirimu obulwadde. Mu Gwokusatu nga guggwaako 2020, WHO n’ebitongole ebirala ebyebyobulamu byatandika okukozesa ekigambo “okweyawula ku balala” ne “okwewa amabanga” okutangaaza nti ekigendererwa kya kukendeeza bantu kukwatagana naye ng’abantu basigazza okuwuliziganya n’enkola endala oba nga buli omu yeesudde munne.
Enkozesa y’ekigambo "okweyawula" kyali kivuddemu okutegeeza nti abantu balina kweggyira ddala ku bannaabwe, mu kifo ky’okubakubiriza okusigala nga bawuliziganya ne bannaabwe nga bakozesa engeri endala. Aboobuyinza abamu bafulumizza ebigobererwa mu kwegatta mu mukwano okutaliimu bulabe mu kiseera kya nawookeera.
Muno mulimu okubakubiriza okwegatta n’omuntu oyo yekka gw’obeera naye, atalina kawuka oba atalina bubonero bw’akawuka.
Omuntu okweggya ku balala kusembebwa eri abo abakebeddwa nga balina COVID-19 n’abo abateebereza nti bafunye akawuka.
Ebitongole by’ebyobulamu bifulumizza ebiragiro by’omuntu kinnoomu okweyawula ku balala. Gavumenti nnyingi zikaka abantu oba zisemba omuntu okweteeka mu kalantiini okw’abantu bonna abali mu bitundu ebikoseddwa.
Ebiragiro by’okweteeka mu kalantiini ebisinga okuba eby’amaanyi biweereddwa mu bitundu ebisinga okubaamu obulabe.
Abo abayinza okuba nga bakwataganyeeko n’omuntu alina COVID-19 n’abo abatambudde mu nsi oba ekitundu obulwadde mwe busaasaanidde ennyo baweereddwa amagezi beeteeke mu kalantiini okumala ennaku 14 okuva mu kiseera we bayinza okuba nga baakwatagana n’obulwadde.
Obukodyo mu kutangira nawookeera mulimu okubulwanyisa oba okubuziyiza n’okubutangira.
Okutangira kukolebwa ku ntandikwa y’okubalukawo kw’obulwadde era kuluubirira kulondoola na kwawula abo abakoseddwa wamu n’okuleeta eby’okukola ebirala okulwanyisa n’okugema okukomya okusaasaana kw’obulwadde mu bantu abasigaddewo.
Bwe kiba nga tekikyasoboka kutangira kusaasaana kwa bulwadde, olwo amaanyi gadda ku kulwanyisa bulwadde: wabaawo ebikolebwa okukendeeza ku kusaasaana n’okutangira ebivaamu mu muyungiro gw’ebyobulamu ne mu bantu.
Omugatte gw’okutangira n’okulwanyisa byombi bisobola okukozesebwa mu kiseera kye kimu.
Okubukendeeza kwetaagisa ebikolebwa eby’amaanyiko okusobola okuzza nawookeera emabega nga wabaawo okukendeeza ku kuzaalukana okuli wansi wa 1. Emu ku ngeri y’okulwanyisa obulwadde obusiigibwa kwe kukendeeza nawookeera ekiyitibwa okubalukawo kwe kugezaako okukendeeza ku kutumbiira kw’okusaasaana kwa nawookeera okw’amaanyi ekiyitibwa okuseeteeza akooleko k’obulwadde (flattening the curve).
Kino kikendeeza ku bulabe bw’obuweereza bw’obulamu obubeeramu okukola ennyo n’okuwa obudde obumala okukola ku ddagala erigema.
Amagezi agatali ga ddagala agayambako mu kulwanyisa obulwadde obubaluseewo mulimu, ebikolebwa abantu kinnoomu okutangira obulwadde, gamba nga okunaaba mu ngalo, okwambala obukookolo, n’okweteeka mu kalantiini; ebikolebwa abantu ebiruubirirwa mu kwesuula amabanga gamba nga okuggalawo oamasomero n’okusazaamu enkuŋŋaana z’abantu abangi; okukubiriza abantu okukkiriza okwetaba mu bikolebwa ng’ebyo; wamu n’ebikolebwa okutaasa ekitundu nga okulongoosa ebifo n’ebintu. Ebikolebwa eby’amaanyiko okulwanyisa nawookeera byakolebwa mu China ng’obulwadde butaamye, gamba okuteeka kalantiini ku bibuga byonna n’okuteekawo amateeka amakakali ku kutambula.
Amawanga amalala nago gaateekawo obukodyo obulala obugenderera okukendeeza ku kusaasaana kw’akawuka.
South Korea yatandikawo okusunsula kw’abantu bonna n’okuteeka abantu mu kalantiini, n’okulabula ku bantu abalwadde abatambula.
Singapore yayamba abo abaali beetadde mu kalantiini nga balwadde ng’ebawa ssente ate abo abaagaana ne babatanza nnyo.
Taiwan yayongeza ku kukola obukookolo era n’etanza abantu abaakweka eddagala. Okwekkaanya okukoleddwa ku Bungereza ne America kulaga nti okutangira (okukendeeza so si kuyimiriza kusaasaana kwa bulwadde) wamu n’okukendeeza obulwadde (okulemesa obulwadde okusaasaana) birimu okusoomooza kwa maanyi.
Enkola ezisinga okukola mu kulwanyisa obulwadde ziyinza okukendeeza ku kweyongera kw’obwetaavu bw’obujjanjabi n’ebitundu 2/3 n’okufa ne kukendeerako amakkati naye ng’era ekyo kivaamu abantu nkumi na nkumi okufa n’amalwaliro okubeera nga tegalina na we gateeka balwadde.
Okukendeeza obulwadde kuyinza okusingako naye kulina okukolebwa kasita kiba nti akawuka kasaasaanira mu bantu (oba okutuusa eddagala erigema lwe lizuulwa, bwe kiba nga kye kisoose), naye nga obulwadde busobola okukomawo ebikolebwa bwe biragayizibwamu.
Ebikolebwa okulwanyisa obulwadde ebimala ebbanga eggwanvu bikosa abantu ate bitwala ne ssente nnyingi.
Tewali ddagala lirwanyisa kawuka ka COVID-19 eryakakasibwa, naye ng’okufuba okukola eddagala weekuli, omwo nga mwe muli n’okugezesa eddagala eririwo mu kiseera kino.
Okumira eddagala erya ssenyiga eritundibwa mu maduuka, okunywa ebyokunywa, n’okuwummula kiyinza okuyambako okukendeeza ku bubonero.
Okusinziira ku bunene bw’obulabe, okuteekebwako omukka ogussibwa, okuteekebwako amazzi n’okussibwako ebyuma okussizaamu biyinza okwetaagisa.
Okukozesa steroids kiyinza okuzibuwaza embeera.
Eddagala lingi (compounds) eryayisibwa edda okujjanjaba endwadde z’obuwuka endala linoonyerezebwako ku nkozesa yaalyo mu kujjanjaba COVID-19.
WHO era kyagamba nti "obumu ku bujjanjabi obw’ekinnansi" busobola okukkakkanya ku bubonero obumu obuleetebwa SARS-CoV-19.
Okwongeza ku busobozi n’okukyusakyusa mu bujjanjabi olw’obwetaavu bw’abalwadde ba COVID-19 nga bwe kinnyonnyolwa WHO kikolwa kya maanyi mu kukola ku kubalukawo kw’obulwadde.
ECDC ne wofiisi ya WHO ey’omu Bulaaya byafulumya ebiruŋŋamya amalwaliro n’obujjanjabi obusookerwako mu kuseetula obujjanjabi ku mitendera egy’enjawulo omwo nga mwe muli n’okufaayo ku buweereza bw’omu magezeserezo mu kukebera obulwadde bwa COVID-19, okusazaamu ebikolebwa ebirala ebitali bya mangu buli lwe kisoboka, okwawula n’okuggya abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu balala, n’okwongeza obujjanjabi obw’enjawulo nga batendeka abakozi n’okwongeza ku muwendo gw’ebyuma ebiyambako mu kussa n’ebitanda.
Waliwo endowooza ez’enjawulo ku nsibuko y’omulwadde eyasooka (ekiyitibwa patient zero).
Omulwadde eyasooka ow’akawuka ka coronavirus akaali temanyiddwa yaliwo eyo nga 1 Deesemba 2019 mu Wuhan, Hubei, China.
Mu bbanga lya mwezi gumu, omuwendo gw’abalwadde ba coronavirus mu Hubei gwagenda gulinnya mpola mpola.
Bano baali balina akakwate n’akatale k’ebyennyanja ak’e Huanan (Huanan Seafood Wholesale Market), akaatundanga n’ensolo ennamu, era endowooza emu egamba nti akawuka kaava mu emu ku nsolo zino; oba, mu bigambo ebirala, ensibuko yaako eri mu nsolo. Waliwo ekika kya lubyamira atamanyiddwa kimuleeta eyalabibwa nga 26 Deesemba nga yajjanjabibwa omusawo Zhang Jixian mu Hubei Provincial Hospital, ng’ono yategeeza Wuhan Jianghan CDC nga 27 Deesemba.
Nga 30 Deesemba, ekibiina ky’abasawo mu ddwaliro ly’e Wuhan Central Hospital baatemya ku bannaabwe nti wandibaawo akawuka akeefaanaanyirizaako "SARS coronavirus".
Munaana ku basawo abo, omwo nga mwe muli Li Wenliang, baanenyezebwa poliisi olw’okusaasaanya obulimba ate n’omulala Ai Fen, yanenyezebwa bakama be olw’okukuba omulanga.
Akakiiko k’eddwaliro lya Wuhan Municipal Health Commission oluvannyuma kaafulumya ekimanyiso nga 31 Deesemba ne kategeeza WHO.
Abalwadde abawerako abaalina yegu atamanyiddwa baali bamaze okutegeezebwa aboobuyinza mu Wuhan okutandika okunoonyereza ku ntandikwa ya Janwali. Okubalukawo kw’obulwadde nga kwakatandika, omuwendo gw’abalwadde gwekubisaamu emirundi ebiri kumpi buli luvannyuma lwa nnaku musanvu n’ekitundu.
Ku ntandikwa ne mu makkati ga Janwali 2020, akawuka kaasaasaana mu bitundu bya China ebirala, ng’okusaasaana okwo kuyambibwako ebikujjuko by’omwaka gwa China Omupya ate n’engeri Wuhan gye kiri ekibuga ky’ebidduka ebingi n’ekifo ewawaanyisiriganyizibwa eggaali z’omukka.
Nga 20 Janwali, China yategeeza nti erina abalwadde nga 140 abapya mu lunaku lumu, omwo nga mwe muli abantu babiri mu Beijing n’omulala omu mu Shenzhen.
Oluvannyuma, obubaka obutongole bulaga nti abantu 6,174 baali bamaze okufuna obubonero olwa 20 Janwali 2020 we lwatuukira. Nga 26 Ogwokusatu, America yayisa China mu muwendo gw’abalwadde abakakasiddwa mu nsi yonna. Nga 9 Ogwokuna 2020 we lwatuukira, abalwadde abasukka mu 1.61 baali bamaze okulabibwa mu nsi yonna; abantu abasukka mu 97,000 baali bafudde ate ng’abantu 364,000 bawonye.
Amawanga n’ebitundu nga 200 gafunye waakiri omulwadde omu.
Olwa nawookeera mu Bulaaya, ensi nnyingi mu kitundu kya Schengen zikugira abantu okutambula nga bwe baagala era zitaddewo obukwakkulizo ku nsalo zaazo.
Ebimu ku mawanga bye gakoze mulimu enkola ez’okutangira okusaasaana okugeza nga kalantiini (ekimanyiddwa nga ebiragiro by’okusigala ewaka, ebiragiro by’obutafuluma nnyumba, oba omuggalo) ne kaafiyu. Bwe zaawerera 2 Ogwokuna, abantu abakunukkiriza mu bukadde 300, oba ebitundu nga 90% ku bantu bonna nga bali ku muggalo egw’engeri emu mu America, abantu abasukka mu bukadde 50 baali ku muggalo mu Phillipines, abantu abali mu bukadde nga 59 baali ku muggalo mu South Afrika, n’abantu akawumbi 1.3 baali ku muggalo mu India.
Nga 26 Ogwokusatu, abantu akawumbi 1.7 mu nsi yonna baali ku muggalo ogw’engeri ez’enjawulo era nga omuwendo gweyongera okutuuka ku bantu obuwumbi 2.6 nga wayiseewo ennaku bbiri—kumpi ekitundu kimu kyakusatu ku bantu abali mu nsi yonna.
Omulwadde eyasooka owa COVID-19 asuubirwa okuba nga yazuulwa nga 1 Deesemba 2019 mu Wuhan; waliwo alipoota emu eteekakasika eraga nti omulwadde eyasooka yaliwo nga 17 Noovemba.
Doctor Zhang Jixian yekkaanya akabinja k’abalwadde ba yegu atamanyiddwa kyamuleeta nga 26 Deesemba, oluvannyuma eddwaliro mw’akolera ne litegeeza aboobuyinza mu Wuhan Jianghan CDC nga 27 Deesemba.
Okukebera kw’endagabutonde okwasooka ku sampolo z’abalwadde nga 27 Deesemba 2019 zaalaga nti zirimu akawuka ka coronavirus akalinga SARS.
Ekimanyiso eri abantu kyafulumizibwa eddwaliro lya Wuhan Municipal Health Commission nga 31 Deesemba.
Ekitongole kya WHO kyategeezebwa ku lunaku lwe lumu.
Okumanyisa okwo bwe kwabaawo, abasawo mu Wuhan baalabulwa poliisi olw’okusaasaanya “olugambo lw’okubalukawo” kw’obulwadde.
Akakiiko ka Chinese National Health Commission mu kusooka kaagamba nti tewali "bubaka bulambulukufu" bulaga nsaasaanya eva ku-muntu-ku-muntu.
Janwali ng’aggwaako, gavumenti ya China yatandikawo kaweefube ow’amaanyi eyayogerwako Ssaabawandiisi w’Ekibiina kya Chinese Communist Party Xi Jinping nga "olutalo lw’abantu" okulwanyisa okusaasaana kw’akawuka.
Mu kwogerwako nga “kalantiini ekyasinze mu bulamu bw’omuntu”, omuggalo kkuulaamalungi gwalangirirwa nga 23 Janwali okuyimiriza okutambula okugenda oba okuva mu Wuhan, era ne gwongezebwayo mu bibuga nga 15 mu Hubei, ne kikosa abantu nga obukadde 57.
Okukozesa emmotoka ez’obwannannyini kwagaanibwa mu kibuga.
Ebikujjuko by’Omwaka gwa China Omupya (25 Janwali) byasazibwamu mu bifo ebiwerako.
Aboobuyinza era baalangirira okuzimba kw’eddwaliro ery’ekiseera, Huoshenshan Hospital, eryamalirizibwa mu nnaku 10.
Eddwaliro eddala nalyo lyazimbibwa oluvannyuma nga liyitibwa, Leishenshan Hospital, likole ku balwadde abalala.
Ng’oggyeeko eddwaliro eddala eryazimbibwa, China era yakyusa ebifo ebirala 14 mu Wuhan, gamba nga ebifo ebituuza enkiiko n’ebisaawe by’omupiira n’ebifuulamu amalwaliro ag’ekiseera. Nga 26 Janwali, gavumenti yateekawo ebiragiro ebirala okulwanyisa okubalukawo kwa COVID-19, omwo nga mwe muli ebiwandiiko by’abatambuze ebyogera ku mbeera y’obulamu bwabwe n’okwongezaayo ebijaguzo by’oluwummula lwa Spring.
Yunivaasite n’amasomero okwetooloola eggwanga nabyo byaggalwa.
Ebitundu bya Hong Kong ne Macau byateekawo ebiragiro bingi, naddala ku masomero ne yunivaasite.
Entegeka z’okukola emirimu omuntu nga tali ku mulimu zaakolebwa mu bitundu bya China bingi.
Okukugira ku kutambula kwakolebwa munda n’ebweru wa Hubei.
Entambula y’olukale yakyusibwamu, n’ebifo by’obulambuzi eby’amakaddiyizo byaggalwawo okumala ekiseera.
Okukugira entambula y’abantu kwatandika okukolebwa mu bibuga bingi, era kiteeberezebwa nti abantu nga obukadde 760 (omuwendo ogusukka mu kitundu ky’abantu bonna) baafuna okukugirwa okw’engeri ez’enjawulo. Obulwadde bwe bwasaasaanira ensi yonna mu Gwokusatu, aboobuyinza mu China baateekawo ebyokugoberera ebikakali okuziyiza akawuka ate “okukaggya mu nsi” endala nga kagenda mu China.
Okugeza, Beijing yateekawo kalantiini ow’obuwaze wa nnaku 14 ku bantu bonna abava mu nsi endala abaali bayingira mu China. Nga 23 Ogwokusatu, mu China munda baalinamu omuntu omu yekka eyali akwatiddwa obulwadde mu bbanga ery’ennaku ettaanu ezaakulembera era ng’ono yali mutambuze eyali akomyewo ng’agenda mu Guangzhou ng’ava mu Istanbul.
Nga 24 Ogwokusatu 2020, Ssaabaminista wa China Li Keqiang yategeeza nti okusaasaana kw’akawuka mu China munda kuzibikiddwa era okubalukawo kw’obulwadde kulwanyisiddwa mu China.
Ku lunaku olwo lwennyini ebiragiro ebikugira okutambula ne babiddiriza mu Hubei, ng’oggyeeko Wuhan, oluvannyuma lw’emyezi ebiri nga bataddewo omuggalo. Minisitule ya China ekola ku nsonga z’ebweru yalangirira nga 26 Ogwokusatu 2020 nti visa z’okuyingira mu China oba olukusa lw’okukolerayo bijja kuyimirizibwa okuva nga 28 Ogwokusatu n’okweyongerayo nga teboogedde kiseera kiragiro kino lwe kirikoma.
Abo abaagala okuyingira mu China kijja kubeetaagisa okusaba visas okuva ku bitebe bya China.
Gavumenti ya China yakubiriza aba bizinensi n’amakolera okuggulawo nga 30 Owokusatu, era n’eteekawo ebisikiriza eri amakampuni. Akakiiko k’eggwanga kaatandika na kuteekawo lunaku lwa kukungubaga mu ggwanga nga batandika n’okusirikamu kwa ddakiika 3 ku ssaawa 4 nga 4 Ogwokuna, nga kino kikwatagana n’Ebikujjuko bya Qingming, wabula gavumenti eya wakati yasaba amaka okuwaayo obubaka obukungubaga ku yintaneeti nga bagenderera obuteeriraana olw’okwewala okuddamu okusaasaanya obupya COVID-19.
COVID-19 yakakasibwa nti atuuse mu South Korea nga 20 Janwali 2020 ng’ava mu China.
Ekitongole ky’eggwanga eky’ebyobulamu kyategeeza nti waaliwo okweyongera kw’abalwadde okw’amaanyi nga 20 Ogwokubiri, nga kigambibwa nti ekyo kyava ku lukuŋŋaana olwali mu Daegu olw’eddiini empya eyitibwa Ekkanisa ya Yesu ey’e Shincheonji (Shincheonji Church of Jesus).
Abagoberezi ba Shincheonji abaagenda e Daegu okuva mu Wuhan be bateeberezebwa okusibukako okubulakawo kw’obulwadde.
Nga 22 Ogwokubiri, mu bagoberezi b’ekkanisa 9,336, 1,261 oba ebitundu nga 13% baategeeza nti baalina obubonero bw’obulwadde. South Korea yalangiriria okulabula okusingayo okuba okw’amaanyi nga 23 Ogwokubiri 2020.
Nga 28 Ogwokubiri, abalwadde abaakakasibwa abasukka mu 2,000 be baategeezebwa mu Korea ne balinnya okutuuka ku 3,150 nga 29 Ogwokubiri.
Enkambi z’amagye zonna mu South Korea zaateekebwa mu kalantiini oluvannyuma lw’okukebera okwalaga nti abasirikale basatu baakakasibwa nga balina akawuka.
Enteekateeka z’entambula z’ennyonyi nazo zaakosebwa era bwe zityo ne zikyusibwa. South Korea yateekawo eteekateeka ezaatunuulirwa ng’ezisinga obugazi n’obulungi mu nsi yonna okusunsula abantu abalina akawuka, n’okwawula buli muntu alina akawuka nga bwe balondoola n’okuteeka mu kalantiini buli eyali akwataganyeeko n’omuntu oyo asangibwa n’akawuka.
Obukodyo bw’okusunsula bwalimu okweroopa okw’obuwaze oli ng’alina obubonero eri abo abaava mu mawanga amalala nga bakozesa app z’oku ssimu, okuvuga emmotoka n’ogenda mu kifo n’okeberwa akawuka ng’oweebwa ebivaamu enkeera, n’okwongeza ku busobozi bw’okukebera okusobozesa okukebera abantu 20,000 buli lunaku.
Enteekateeka ya South Korea programme etwalibwa okuba nga yalimu obuwanguzi mu kulwanyisa okubalukawo kw’obulwadde wadde ng’ebibuga byonna tebaabiteeka mu kalantiini. Abantu b’omu South Korean mu kusooka beeyawulamu olw’engeri Pulezidenti Moon Jae-in gye yali akuttemu ensonga z’obulwadde.
Abakorea bangi baateeka emikono ku kiwandiiko nga basaba Moon ave mu buyinza nga bagamba nti gavumenti tekutte bulungi kubalukawo kwa bulwadde ate ng’abalala bawaana by’akoze.
Nga 23 Ogwokusatu, kyategeezebwa nti South Korea ye yalina omuwendo gw’abalwadde abasinga obutono mu nsi okumala wiiki nnya.
Nga 29 Ogwokusatu kyategeezebwa nti okutandika nga 1 Ogwokuna abantu bonna abatambula okuva mu mawanga amalala bajja kuteekebwa mu kalantiini okumala wiiki bbiri.
Nga 1 Ogwokuna, ebitongole by’amawulire byategeeza nti South Korea yali asabye obuyambi bw’ebikozesebwa mu kukebera akawuka okuva mu mawanga 121.
Iran yalangirira omulwadde waayo owa SARS-CoV-2 eyasooka okukakasibwa nga 19 Ogwokubiri mu Qom, era ekitongole ky’Ebyobulamu (Ministry of Health and Medical Education) kyategeeza nti abantu babiri baafa ku lunaku olwo.
Eby’okukola ebyasooka okulangirirwa gavumenti mwalimu okusazaamu ebivvulu n’emikolo gy’ebyobuwangwa, emikolo gy’ebyemizannyo, n’okusaba kw’Olwokutaano, n’okuggalawo kwa yunivaasite, amatendekero aga waggulu, n’amasomero.
Iran yassaawo obutabalika (trillion) bwa rials butaano okulwanyisa akawuka.
Nga 26 Ogwokubiri 2020, Pulezidenti Hassan Rouhani yagamba nti tewaaliwo nteekateeka za kuteeka kalantiini ku bitundu ebyali bikoseddwa nti era abantu kinnoomu be balina okuteekebwa mu kalantiini.
Enteekateeka z’okukendeeza ku ntambula wakati w’ebibuga eby’enjawulo zaalangirirwa mu Gwokusatu wadde ng’ebidduka bingi ebyentambula z’ebikujjuko by’Omwaka omupya ogwa Persia (Persian New Year Nowruz) byo byagenda mu maaso.
Ebifo by’okusabiramu ebya Shia mu Qom byasigala nga biggule eri abalamazi okutuusa nga 16 Ogwokusatu 2020. Iran yafuuka entabiro y’okusaasaanya akawuka ng’eddirira China mu Gwokubiri.
Wakati mu kulumiriza nti waaliwo okubikkirira ekizibu ky’obulwadde mu Iran, amawanga agasukka mu kkumi gaali galondodde abalwadde baabwe nga baaliko mu Iran olwa 28 Ogwokubiri we lwatuukira, kino nga kiraga nti obunene bw’ekirwadde bwali bwa maanyi okusukka ku balwadde 388 gavumenti ya Iran be yali egamba nti be bali mu ggwanga eryo olunaku olwo we lwatuukira.
Paliyamenti ya Iran yayimirizibwa, nga bammemba 23 ku 290 baali bagambibwa okuba nga bakebeddwa ne basangibwa nga balina akawuka nga 3 Ogwokusatu.
Nga 12 Ogwokubiri, ekitongole kya Human Rights Watch kyakubiriza aboobuyinza mu makomera ga Iran okuta abamenyi b’amateeka ku ddembe ly’obuntu awatali kakwakkulizo wamu n’okuta abasibe bonna abasaanira okuteebwa okumala ekiseera ekigere.
Kigambibwa nti waliwo obulabe bw’akawuka bwa maanyi okusaasaanira mu bifo ebirimu abantu abangi gamba ng’amakomera, ate nga tebiriimu bujjanjabi bumatiza.
Nga 15 Ogwokusatu, gavumenti ya Iran yategeeza nti abantu 100 baafa mu lunaku lumu, nga guno gwe muwendo ogwasinga obunene mu ggwanga lino okuva obulwadde lwe bwabalukawo.
Olwa 17 Ogwokusatu we lwatuukira abakulembeze waakiri 12 ku abo abaali bakulembeddeko Iran n’abo abali mu bukulembeze baali bafudde olw’ekirwadde ekyo.
Olwa 23 Ogwokusatu we lwatuukira, Iran yali efuna abalwadde 50 abapya buli ssaawa n’omuntu omu ng’afa buli luvannyuma lwa ddakiika kkumi olwa coronavirus.
Okusinziira ku mukungu wa WHO, omuwendo gw’abalwadde mu Iran guyinza okuba nga gukubisa emirundi etaano mu ogwo ogwogerwa.
Kigambibwa era nti obukwakkulizo America bwe yateeka ku Iran buyinza okuba nga bukosa obusobozi bw’eggwanga eryo okulwanyisa obulwadde.
Ekitongole ky’Amawanga Amagatte Ekirwanirira Eddembe ly’obuntu (UN High Commissioner for Human Rights) kisabye nnati z’ebyenfuna ezaateekebwa ku mawanga okuddirizibwa naddala ago agasinze okukosebwa ekirwadde kino, omwo nga mwe muli ne Iran.
Okubalukawo kw’obulwadde kwakakasibwa okusaasaanira mu Italy nga 31 Janwali, abalambuzi Abachina babiri bwe baakeberebwa ne bazuulibwa nga balina SARS-CoV-2 mu Roma.
Omuwendo gw’abalwadde gwatandika okulinnyira ku mbiro ekyaleetera gavumenti ya Italy okuyimiriza ennyonyi zonna ezigenda n’eziva e China era ne balangirira n’akaseera aka kazigizigi.
Ekika ky’akawuka akatakwatagana na COVID-19 kaakengebwa oluvannyuma, nga katandikira ku balwadde 16 abaakakasibwa mu Lombardy nga 21 Ogwokubiri. Nga 22 Ogwokubiri, Akakiiko ka Baminista kaalangirira etteeka eppya okulwanyisa obulwadde, omwo nga mwe muli okuteeka abantu abasukka mu 50,000 abava mu Munisipaali ezisukka mu kalantiini mu bukiikakkono bwa Italy.
Ssaabaminista Giuseppe Conte yagamba nti, "Mu bifo ebibaluseemu obulwadde, okuyingira n’okubifuluma tekujja kukkirizibwa.
Okuyimiriza emirimu egikolebwa n’emikolo gy’ebyemizannyo kumaze okukolebwa mu bifo ebyo. "Nga 4 Ogwokusatu, gavumenti ya Italy yalangirira okuggalirawo ddala amasomero ne yunivaasite mu ggwanga lyonna nga mu kiseera ekyo Italy yali ewezezza abafu 100.
Emikolo gy’ebyemizannyo gyonna emikulu, omuli n’emizannyo gy’omupiira egy’eddaala A (Serie A football matches), gyalina kuzannyirwa munda mu bizimbe okutuusa nga 1 Ogwokuna, naye nga 9 Ogwokusatu, emizannyo gyonna gyayimirizibwa okumala waakiri omwezi gumu.
Nga 11 Ogwokusatu, Ssaabaminista Conte yalangirira okuyimiriza kumpi buli mulimu gwa busuubuzi okuggyako ssemaduuka n’amatundiro g’eddagala. Nga 6 Ogwokusatu, Ettendekero lya College of Anaesthesia, Analgesia, Resuscitation and Intensive Care (SIAARTI) lyafulumya ebiragiro ebikwata ku bigobererwa mu kunoonyereza okulimu enseetuka ekulembeza okufa ku balwadde (triage protocols) ebiyinza okukozesebwa mu kunoonyereza.
Nga 19 Ogwokusatu, Italy yayisa China mu muwendo gw’abafa ekirwadde kya coronavirus mu nsi yonna bwe baategeeza nti baalina abatu 3,405 abaafa nawookeera w’ekirwadde.
Nga 22 Ogwokusatu, kyategeezebwa nti Russia yali eweerezza ennyonyi z’amagye mwenda mu Italy.
Nga 5 Ogwokuna we lwatuukira, waaliwo abalwadde abakakasiddwa 128,948, abafu 15,887, n’abawonye 21,815 mu Italy, era ng’abasinga obungi ku abo baali mu kitundu ky’e Lombardy.
Amawulire ga CNN gaalaga nti olw’okuba Italy erina abakadde bangi okwo nga kw’ogasse n’obutasobola kukebera bantu bonna balina kawuka, kyandiba nga kyongereza ku muwendo gw’abafa omungi.
Engeri Bungereza gye yasooka okukwatamu obulwadde buno yafaanana okuba nga y’esinga okuba ey’emirembe mu nsi zonna ezaali zikoseddwa, era okutuusa nga 18 Ogwokusatu 2020, gavumenti ya Bungereza yali tennateekawo kiragiro kyonna ku bantu kwewa mabanga oba kalantiini ow’abantu bonna mu ggwanga eryo.
N’ekyava mu ekyo, gavumenti yanenyezebwa olw’okwesuulirayo ogwa nnaggamba mu buzibu obwali bwolekedde abantu. Nga 16 Ogwokusatu, Ssaabaminista Boris Johnson yalangirira ng’awa abantu amagezi okwewala okutambula okutali kwa nsonga n’okukwatagana n’abantu abalala, n’agamba nti we kisobokera bakolere ewaka era beewale n’ebifo ng’amabaala, ebifo ebiriirwamu n’ebifo ebisanyukirwamu.
Nga 20 Ogwokusatu, gavumenti yalangirira nti ebifo ebisanyukirwamu byonna ng’amabaala ne ggimu byali bya kuggalwa amangu ddala nga bwe kisoboka, era n’asuubiza okusasula okutuuka ku bitundu 80% eby’ensako y’abakozi okukoma ku £2,500 buli mwezi okwewala ebbula ly’emirimu mu kizibu kino. Nga 23 Ogwokusatu, Ssaabaminisita yalangirira enkola z’okwewa amabanga enkakali, n’awera enkuŋŋaana ez’abantu abasukka mu babiri n’okuwera okutambula n’ebikolerwa ebweru w’ennyumba nga birina kukolebwa nga ddala byetaagisa.
Ng’oggyeeko ebyokukola ebyasooka okuteekebwawo, obukwakkulizo buno poliisi ye yali erondoola okulaba nga bussibwa mu nkola nga baweesa abantu engassi n’okusattulula enkuŋŋaana zonna.
Bizinensi ezisinga zaalagirwa okuggalawo okuggyako ezo ezitwalibwa “ng’ez’enkizo” omwo nga mwe muli ssemaduuka, amatundiro g’eddagala, bbanka, amaduuka g’ebizimbisibwa, amasundiro g’amafuta ne galagi.
Nga 20 Janwali, omulwadde wa COVID-19 eyasooka okukakasibwa mu Pacific Northwest state of Washington yali musajja eyadda mu ggwanga ng’ava mu Wuhan nga 15 Janwali.
Akakiiko ka America akalwanyisa Coronavirus akayitibwa White House Coronavirus Task Force kaateekebwawo nga 29 Janwali.
Nga 31 Janwali, obukulembeze bwa Trump bwalangirira kazigizigi w’ebyobulamu mu ggwanga era ne bateekawo obukwakkulizo ku batambuze abava mu China.
Nga 28 Janwali 2020, Center for Disease Control—ekitongole ekikulu mu byobulamu mu America—kyalangirira nti kyali kikoze ebikozesebwa ebyakyo okukebera obulwadde.
Wadde nga kino baakikola, America yatandika kasoobo ng’ekebera, era nga kino kyalemesa okumanya obunene bw’ekizibu ky’obulwadde.
Okukebera kwajjamu omugozobano gw’okukozesa ebikebera obulwadde ebikyamu mu Gwokubiri, gavumenti obutakkiriza bikebera bulwadde bitali byayo kukozesebwa (ebikozesebwa abanoonyereza, amakampuni n’amalwaliro) okutuusa ku nkomerero y’Ogwokubiri, n’okukugira abantu nga balina kutuukiriza bisaanyizo bya kukeberebwa okutuusa mu Gwokusatu (oluvannyuma ekiragiro ky’omusawo kye kibaddenga kyetaagisa).
Nga 27 Ogwokubiri, Olupapula lw’Amawulire The Washington Post lwategeezeza nti abantu abatawera 4,000 be baali bakebeddwa mu America.
Nga 13 Ogwokusatu, The Atlantic lwategeeza nti abantu abatawera 14,000 be baali bakebeddwa.
Nga 22 Ogwokusatu, Associated Press kyawandiika nti: "Abantu bangi abeeyolekerako obubonero nga balina n’olukusa lw’omusawo balindira essaawa nnyingi oba ennaku eziwera okukeberwa.” Oluvannyuma lw’omuntu eyasooka okufa mu Washington state nga 29 Ogwokubiri, Governor Jay Inslee yalangirira ekiseera ekya kazigizigi, era nga kino ebitundu ebirala nabyo kye byakola.
Amasomero mu kitundu ky’e Seattle gaasazaamu ebibiina nga 3 Ogwokusatu era amakkati g’Ogwokusatu we gaatukira, amasomero okwetooloola mu ggwanga gaatandika okuggalawo. Nga 6 Ogwokusatu 2020, ekibiina ky’abanoonyereza ku ndwadde mu Imperial College London kyawa America amagezi ku kizibu kye yali eyolekedde bulwadde obwo.
Ku lunaku lwe lumu Pulezidenti Trump yassa omukono ku Tteeka ly’Okuwa Obuyambi obw’amangu (Coronavirus Preparedness and Response Supplemental Appropriations Act) mwe baaweerayo obuwumbi bwa doola 8.3 mu gavumenti z’ebitundu okulwanyisa nawookeera.
Ebitongole byateekawo obukwakkulizo ku bakozi, byasazaamu enkuŋŋaana, era baakubiriza abakozi okukolera ewaka.
Emikolo gy’emizannyo n’enzannya ezaali zitegekebwa byasazibwamu. Nga 11 Ogwokusatu, Trump yalangirira ebiragiro ku ntambula mu bitundu bya Bulaaya ebisinga, ng’oggyeeko Bungereza, okumala ennaku 30, okutandika ne 13 Ogwokusatu.
Ku lunaku olwaddirira yagaziya ebiragiro n’ayongerako Bungereza ne Ireland.
Nga 13 Ogwokusatu, yalangirira akaseera aka kazigizigi mu ggwanga lyonna ekyaleetera okukozesa ssente za gavumenti ez’ebitundu okukozesebwa ku bulwadde obuliwo.
Okutandika ne 15 Ogwokusatu, bizinensi nnyingi zaggalawo oba zaakendeeza ku budde bw’okukoleramu wonna mu America nga bagezaako okukekkereza okusaasaanya akawuka.
Nga 17 Ogwokusatu, obulwadde bwali bumaze okukakasibwa wonna mu masaza 50 ne mu District of Columbia. Nga 23 Ogwokusatu, kyategeezebwa nti Ekibuga New York kyalina abalwadde 10,700 aba coronavirus, era ng’omuwendo guno gusinga ogwo ogw’abalwadde abaali mu South Korea.
Nga 25 Ogwokusatu, gavana yagamba nti okwewa amabanga kwafaanana okuba nga kuvaamu ebirungi kubanga okwekubisaamu kw’abalwadde kulabika nga kwali kukendedde okuva ku nnaku 2.0 okudda ku nnaku 4.7.
28 Ogwokusatu we lwatuukira, waaliwo abalwadde abakakasiddwa 32,308 mu Kibuga New York, n’abantu 672 baali bafudde olw’akawuka. Nga 26 Ogwokusatu, America yali egambibwa okubeera n’abalwadde abakakasiddwa bangi okusinga ewalala wonna mu nsi, omwo nga mwe muli ne China ne Italy. Nga 8 Ogwokuna we lwatuukira, abalwadde 400,335 baali bakakasiddwa mu America n’abantu 12,841 nga bafudde.
Amawulire ga Per media nga 30 Ogwokusatu gaategeeza nti Pulezidenti wa U.S. Trump yasalawo okwongezaayo ebbanga ly’ebiragiro by’okwewa amabanga okutuusa nga 30 Ogwokuna.
Ku lunaku lwe lumu, eddwaliro lya USNS Comfort, erikolera ku lyato eririko ebitanda nga 1000 lyatuuka mu New York.
Nga 3 Ogwokuna, America yalina abantu abafudde 884 olwa coronavirus mu ssaawa 24 zokka.
Mu New York abalwadde baali basusse 100,000 olwa 3 Ogwokuna we lwatuukira. White House yakolokotebwa olw’okunyoomereza ekizibu n’okufuga obubaka obufuluma mu bantu nga balagira abeebyobulamu ne bannassaayansi okuweereza obubaka bwonna n’ebiwandiiko ebifulumizibwa mu wofiisi y’Omumyuka wa Pulezidenti Mike Pence.
Okutwaliza awamu engeri Trump gy’akuttemu ekizubu kino etunuuliddwa nnyo ng’etambulidde ku kyekubiira.
Abakulembeze abamu mu U.S. n’aboogera ku byamawulire baakolokota America olw’okwesigama ennyo mu kuggya ebweru ebintu eby’amanaanyi ebyetaagisa, omwo nga mwe muli n’eddagala ebiva mu China.
Okwekenneenya entambula z’omu bbanga kwakozesebwa okwoleka engeri obulwadde gye busaasaanamu era ne kufulumizibwa mu The Journal of Travel Medicine wakati wa Janwali 2020.
Okusinziira ku bubaka obwafuluma mu 2018 nga buva mu Kibiina ky’Ensi yonna ku ntambula z’omu bbanga (International Air Transport Association), Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, ne Taipei byalina abasaabaze abasinga obungi nga bava mu Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney, ne Melbourne nabyo byayogerwako ng’ebifo ebyettanirwa nnyo abantu abava mu Wuhan.
Bali kyayogerwako ng’ekisinga obutaba na busobozi mu bibuga ebituukirwamu ku ebyo 20 ebisinga okwettanirwa ng’otunuulidde okwetegeka, so ng’ate ebibuga mu Australia byayogerwako ng’ebirina obusobozi. Australia yafulumya enteekateeka yaayo ey’okulwanyisa Novel Coronavirus (COVID-19) nga 7 Ogwokubiri.
Kigambibwa nti bingi byali birina okuzuulibwa ku COVID-19, era nti Australia yali erina okutunuulira ennyo ensalo zaayo n’empuliziganya mu kulwanyisa nawookeera.
Nga 21 Ogwokusatu, akaseera ak’obwerende kaalangirirwa mu Australia.
Olw’okuba nti enkola ya kalantiini ku ntambula y’olukale yakoze bulungi mu Wuhan ne Hubei, amawanga mangi gateeseteese okuggya abantu baago n’abakungu mu kitundu ekyo, era nga kino bakikola nga bakozesa ennyonyi empangise okuva mu ggwanga eryo erinona abantu baalyo nga bakkirizibwa aboobuyinza mu China.
Canada, America, Japan, India, Sri Lanka, Australia, France, Argentina, Germany, ne Thailand ge mawanga agaasooka okutegeka okuddukira abantu baago.
Pakistan yagamba nti tejja kuggya mutuuze waayo yenna mu China.
Nga 7 Ogwokubiri, Brazil yaddukira abantu baayo 34 oba ab’omu maka agamu okwo nga kw’otadde n’aba Poland bana n’omutuuze wa India.
Abatuuze b’omu Poland, China, ne India baaviirmu mu Poland, ennyonyi ya Brazil we yamiriramukko nga tennaba kweyongerayo kugenda Brazil.
Bannansi ba Brazil abaagenda mu Wuhan baateekebwa mu kalantiini mu nkambi y’amagye okumpi ne Brasília.
Ku lunaku lwe lumu, Bannakanada 215 (176 okuva mu nnyonyi eyasooka, ne 39 okuva mu nnyonyi eyookubiri eyapangisibwa gavumenti ya America) baddukirwa okuva mu Wuhan ne babatwala e CFB Trenton bateekebwe mu kalantiini okumala wiiki bbiri.
Nga 11 Ogwokubiri, ennyonyi endala ng’erimu Abakanada 185 okuva mu Wuhan yatuuka e CFB Trenton.
Aboobuyinza mu Australia baddukira bannansi baabwe 277 nga 3 ne 4 Ogwokubiri ne babatwala ku Christmas Island Detention Centre, kye baali bataddewo ng’ekifo kya kalantiini era nga baali balina okubeera eyo okumala ennaku 14.
Ennyonyi ya New Zealand eyaddukira abantu baayo yatuuka mu in Auckland nga 5 Ogwokubiri; abasaabaze baayo (nga mulimu n’abamu okuva mu Australia ne Pacific) baateekebwa mu kalantiini mu Whangaparoa, mu bukiikakkono bwa Auckland.
Nga 15 Ogwokubiri, America yalangirira nti ejja kuddukira Abamerica nga batambulira ku lyato, Diamond Princess.
Nga 21 Ogwokubiri, ennyonyi eyaliko abasaabaze ba Canada 129 abaali baddukiddwa okuva mu Diamond Princess baatuuka mu Trenton, Ontario.
Ku ntandika y’Ogwokusatu, gavumenti ya Indian yatandika okuddukira abantu baayo mu Iran. Nga 14 Ogwokusatu gavumenti ya South Africa, yapangisa ennyonyi ya South African Airways okuddukira abatuuze baayo 112.
Okusunsula kw’ekisawo kwakolebwa ng’ennyonyi tennanasimbula era bannansi ba South Africa abaalabikirako obubonero bwa coronavirus baalekebwa emabega olw’okukendeeza ku bulabe.
Bannansi ba South Africa abataalina bulwadde be bazzibwayo ku butaka.
Ebyava mu kukebera byalaga nti bannansi ba South Africa bonna baali bulungi, omwo nga mwe muli abakozi bw’oku nnyonyi, abavuzi b’ennyonyi, abakozi b’omu wooteeri, abapoliisi n’abajaasi abeetaba mu kaweefube w’obuyambi, era nga bonna mu ngeri y’okwerinda, baasigala beetegerezebwa era nga bali mu kalantiini okumala ennaku 14 ku The Ranch Resort.
Nga 20 Ogwokusatu, America yatandika okuggya abajaasi baayo mu Iraq mu biwagu olw’obulwadde buno.
Nga 5 Ogwokubiri, Minisitule ya China ey’ensonga z’ebweru yagamba nti amawanga 21 (omuli Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad and Tobago, Egypt, ne Iran) gaali gabaweerezza obuyambi.
Abayizi abasibuka mu China nga basomera mu yunivaasite z’omu America beegatta wamu ne baweereza obuyambi mu bitundu by’omu China ebyakosebwa ennyo obulwadde, era nga waliwo ekibiina ekiri mu Chicago ekyaweereza obukookolo obw’ekika kya N95 obuwera 50,000 mu malwaliro g’omu Hubei nga on 30 Janwali. Ekitongole ekigabi ky’obuyambi (The humanitarian aid organization Direct Relief) wamu ne FedEx, baaweereza obukookolo 200,000 wamu n’ebintu ebirala eby’okwesabika omuli giraavu ne gawuni ne bigendera ku nnyonyi ey’obuyambi obw’amangu mu Wuhan Union Hospital nga 30 Janwali.
Nga 5 Ogwokubiri, Bill ne Melinda Gates baalangirira obuyambi bwa bukadde bwa doola 100 eri ekitongole kya WHO okukola ku kunoonyereza kw’eddagala erigema n’okukola ku bujjanjabi wamu n’okukuuma "abantu abali mu buzibu mu Afrika ne South Asia".
Interaksyon kyategeeza nti gavumenti ya China yagabira eggwanga lya Philippines obukookolo 200,000 nga 6 Ogwokubiri nga Omubaka Richard Gordon amaze okuweereza obukookolo obukadde 3.16 mu Wuhan.
Nga 19 Ogwokubiri, Ekitongole kya Red Cross mu Singapore kyalangirira nti kigenda kusindika obuyambi obubalirirwamu obukadde $2.26 mu China.
Japan yawaayo obukookolo akakadde kamu eri Wuhan, Turkey yawaayo ebikozesebwa mu kujjanjaba, Russia yaweereza ttani z’ebikozesebwa mu kujjanjaba ezisukka mu 13 mu Wuhan, Malaysia yalangirira nti ewadde China obukadde bwa giraavu 18, Germany yatwala ebikozesebwa mu kujjanjaba ebyenjawulo omuli Hazmat suits 10,000, ate America yawa China ttani 17.8 ez’ebikozesebwa mu kujjanjaba era n’esuubiza okwongerayo obukadde bwa ssente $100 okuyamba amawanga agaali gakoseddwa. Obulwadde bwe bugenze nga bukendeera mu China, China yo ebadde eweereza obuyambi mu mawanga ag’enjawulo agakoseddwa nawookeera ono.
Mu Gwokusatu, China, Chuba ne Russia baaweereza ebikozesebwa mu kujjanjaba n’abakugu okuyamba ku Italy ku coronavirus eyali abaluseewo.
Munnabizinesi Jack Ma yaweereza ebikozesebwa mu kukebera akakadde 1.1, obukookolo obukadde 6, n’obuganduula 60,000 mu Addis Ababa, Ethiopia African Union ebigabe.
Oluvannyuma yaweereza ebikozesebwa mu kukebera 5,000, obukookolo 100,000 n’ebyuma ebiyambako mu kussa 5 mu Panama.
Ma era yawaayo ebikozesebwa mu kujjanjaba eri Canada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia, ne Czech Republic beemulugunya ku bukookolo n’ebikozesebwa mu kukebera ebikolerwa mu China.
Okugeza, Spain yasazaamu ebikozesebwa mu kukebera coronavirus 58,000 ebikolebwa mu China nga bino obutuukirivu bwabyo bwali bwa bitundu 30% byokka, so nga Netherlands yasazaamu obukookolo bw’e China 600,000 obwali obufu.
Belgium yasazaamu obukookolo 100,000 obwali tebusobola kukozesebwa, nga bulowoozebwa nga bwava China, naye nga mu butuufu bwali buva Colombia.
Ku ludda olulala, Obuyambi bwa China bwayanirizibwa bulungi mu bitundu by’e Latin America ne mu Africa. Nga 2 Ogwokuna, Banka y’Ensi Yonna yatongoza obuyambi obw’amangu eri amawanga agakyakula.
WHO etenderezza kaweefube wa China mu ngeri gy’ekuttemu n’okulwanyisa obulwadde.
WHO yazuula enjawulo wakati w’obulwadde bwa SARS obwabalukawo mu 2002–2004, nga ku olwo abakulembeze ba China balumirizibwa okusirikira ebyama ekyalemesa kaweefube w’okubwewala n’okubulwanyisa, n’ekizibu ekiriwo kati nga gavumenti ya wakati "etegeeza abantu buli kiseera okwewala okubuguutana mu kwetegekera eggandaalo ly’okuyingira omwaka omupya (Lunar New Year holidays)".
Nga 23 Janwali, ng’ayanukula eky’abakungu ba gavumenti okusalawo okuyimiriza entambula mu Wuhan, omukiise wa WHO Gauden Galea yagamba nti “newankubadde WHO si ye yakisalawo”, kyali “kikolwa kirungi nnyo era nga kiraga okwewaayo okulwanyisa obulwadde mu kitundu mwe businze okwegiriisiza” era n’akyogerako nga “ekyali kitabangawo mu byafaayo byobujjanjabi”. Nga 30 Janwali, ng’okusiigibwa okuva ku muntu okudda ku mulala kumaze okukakasibwa ebweru wa China era nga n’omuwendo gw’abalwadde gweyongera mu mawanga amalala, WHO yalangirira nti obulwadde buno kyali Kizibu kya Byabulamu eky’Ensi Yonna ekyetaaga Okufiibwako mu Bwangu (Public Health Emergency of International Concern (PHEIC)), nga kino kyamukaaga okuva ekitegeero kino bwe kyassibwawo bwe waabalukawo ekirwadde ky’omusujja gw’embizzi mu 2009.
Omukulu wa WHO Tedros Adhanom yagamba nti PHEIC kino kyava ku "buzibu bw’okusaasaana mu nsi yonna, naddala mu mawanga amankuseere (low- and middle-income countries) agatalina byabujjanjabi birungi.
Ng’ayanukula ku ky’okuyimiriza ebyentambula, Tedros yagamba nti "tewali nsonga lwaki ebyentambula n’ebyobusuubuzi mu nsi yonna bimala gataataaganyizibwa" era nti "WHO tewagira kya kukendeeza busuubuzi na ntambula."
Nga 5 Ogwokubiri, WHO yawanjagira abantu mu nsi yonna okuwaayo obukadde bwa doola 675 okuvujjirira okweteekateeka mu mawanga amankuseere, n’alaga nti kyali kyetaagisa mu bwangu okuwagira amawanga ago "agatalina nkola za kuzuula bantu bakwatiddwa kawuka, singa kaba kabaluseewo ".
Tedros era yalangirira nti "amaanyi gaffe genkanankana n’awo we tusinga okubeerera abanafu" era n’asaba abantu mu nsi yonna "okusiga leero oba okusasula ekinene gye bujja". Nga 11 Ogwokubiri, WHO mu lukuŋŋaana lw’amawulire yalangirira COVID-19 ng’erinnya ly’obulwadde buno.
Ku lunaku lwe lumu olwo, Tedros yagamba nti Ssaabawandiisi w’Ekibiina ky’Amawanga Amagatte António Guterres yali akkirizza okuwaayo "amaanyi ga UN yonna mu kulwanyisa obulwadde ".
Tiimu ya UN ekola ku kulwanyisa ebibamba (UN Crisis Management Team) yassibwawo, esobole okukwanaganya kaweefube w’Amawanga Amagatte gonna, nga kino WHO egamba nti kijja kubayamba "okussa essira ku byobujjanjabi ng’ebitongole ebirala bwe bireeta obukugu bwabyo okuyamba ku nsonga z’embeera z’abantu, ebyenfuna n’enkulaakulana mu kiseera ky’obulwadde buno ".
Nga 14 Ogwokubiri, Tiimu ey’awamu eyakulirwa WHO mu China yassibwawo okuwaayo abakugu okuva mu nsi yonna ne mu WHO eri China okuyambako mu nkwata y’ebintu awaka n’okwekenneenya "obukambwe n’okusaasaana kw’obulwadde" nga bategeka emisomo n’enkuŋŋaana n’ebitongole ebikulu mu ggwanga n’okugenda mu bitundu okwekaliriza "ebiva mu bikoleddwa ku mutendera gw’ebitundu n’amasaza, omuli ebitundu eby’ebibuga n’eby’ebyalo". Nga 25 Ogwokubiri, WHO yalangirira nti "ensi erina okukola ekisingawo okwetegekera coronavirus ayinza okufuuka ekizibu ky’ensi yonna," n’egamba nti newankubadde obudde bwali bukyali okukiyita ekizibu ky’ensi yonna (pandemic), amawanga gaali gasaanye okubeera "nga geetegese ".
Ku bulwadde obwali butandise okubalukawo mu Iran, WHO yaweerezaayo Tiimu ey’Awamu (Joint Mission Team) okwekenneenya embeera. Nga 28 Ogwokubiri, abakungu ba WHO baagamba nti okwekenneenya ekizibu kya coronavirus ku mutendera gw’ensi yonna kwali kwa kulinnyisibwa okuva ku kubeera "okw’amaanyi" okutuuka ku "okw’amaanyi ennyo", nga gwe mutendera gwabwe ogw’okwekenneenya ekizibu ogusinga okuba waggulu.
Mike Ryan, nga y’akulira enteekateeka ya WHO ey’ebigwawo mu byobulamu (WHO's health emergencies program), yalabula bwe yagamba nti "Kino kya kwekebera eri buli gavument mu nsi yonna: Muzuukuke.
Akawuka kano kayinza okuba nga kali mu kkubo kajja era mwetaaga okubeera abeetegefu," n’alabula nti okubeera n’enkola entuufu ez’okukalwanyisa kiyinza okuyamba ensi okwewala "ekisinga okuba ekyobulabe ".
Ryan era yagamba nti obubaka obuliwo mu kiseera kino bwali tebuleetera bakungu ba byabulamu kulangirira kizibu kino ng’eky’awamu mu nsi yonna, n’agamba nti ekirangiriro eky’engeri eno kyandibadde kitegeeza nti "tuba tukkirizza nti buli muntu mu nsi yonna ajja kukosebwa akawuka ako."
Nga 11 Ogwokusatu, WHO yalangirira akawuka ka coronavirus ng’ekizibu eky’awamu mu nsi yonna.
Director-General yagamba nti WHO yali "efaayo nnyo ku misinde emingi akawuka gye kaali katambulirako n’obukambwe bwako, n’engeri gye wataaliwo kya maanyi kikolebwa". WHO ekolokoteddwa nnyo olw’ekirabika ng’obutakola kya maanyi mu ngeri y’okukwatamu obulwadde, omuli n’okulwawo okulangirira ekizibu ky’ebyobulamu ekyetaaga okufiibwako amangu n’okubulangirira ng’ekizibu eky’ensi yonna.
Okukolokota kuno kwalimu okukaka Director-General wa WHO Tedros Adhanom okulekulira, nga kaweefube ono yassibwako emikono abantu 733,000 we lwatuukira nga 6 Ogwokuna.
Nga 26 Ogwokusatu 2020, abakugu ba UN ku byeddembe ly’obuntu bakkaatiriza eky’okussa ekitiibwa mu ddembe lya buli muntu mu kiseera ky’obulwadde bwa COVID-19.
Ekibinja ky’abakugu kyagamba nti buli muntu alina eddembe okufuna ebitaasa obulamu era nti buno buvunaanyizibwa bwa gavumenti.
Ekibinja kino kyakkaatiriza nti ebbula ly’ebikozesebwa oba yinsuwa y’ebyobulamu tebirina kutwalibwa ng’ekyekwaso ky’okusosola abantu abamu.
Abakugu baakiraga nti buli muntu alina eddembe ku byobulamu, omuli n’abantu abalina obulemu, ebibinja by’abantu abatono, abakadde, abali mu nkambi z’ababudami, abatalina waabwe, ababeera mu mbeera embi ennyo, abasibe, awamu n’abanoonyi b’obubudamu n’abalala bonna abeetaaga obuyambi bwa gavumenti.
Ebitongole bya gavumenti mu nsi yonna bikola ku buzibu bwa COVID-19 eri ebyenfuna n’embeera z’abantu.
Ekitongole ki Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development kitaddewo enkola mwe kinaayita okuwa obubaka mu budde era mu bujjuvu ku nkola eziteereddwawo mu mawanga okwetooloola ensi, awamu n’ebirowoozo n’amagezi.
Okuva ku nkola z’okunyweza ebyobujjanjabi n’ebyenfuna by’ensi yonna okutuuka ku kukola ku bireetebwawo omuggalo n’okuggala ebyentambula, enkola enko erimu Akalondoola Enkola mu Mawanga (Country Policy Tracker), era egenderera okuyamba amawanga okuyigira ku gannaago era n’okukwaganya kaweefube w’omu nsi yonna mu kusoomoozebwa kwa coronavirus.
Gavumenti ya China ekolokoteddwa United States, Minisita wa UK owa Kabineeti Michael Gove, ne mutabani wa Pulezidenti wa Brazil Jair Bolsonaro nga ye Eduardo Bolsonaro olw’engeri gye baakuttemu ekizibu kino, ekyatandikira mu Province y’e China ey’e Hubei.
Abakulembeze bangi ku mutendera gwa Province mu kibiina kya Communist Party of China (CPC) baagobwa olw’engeri gye bakwatamu kaweefube wa kalantiini mu Masekkati ga China, akabonero akalaga obutali bumativu ku ngeri abakulembeze gye bakwatamu obulwadde mu bitundu ebyo.
Abatunuulizi abamu balowooza nti ekikolwa kino kyagendererwamu okutaasa Ssaabawandiisi w’ekibiina kya Chinese Communist Party Xi Jinping ku busungu bw’abantu olw’ekirwadde kya coronavirus ekyali kibaluseewo.
Abakungu ba China abamu, okugeza Zhao Lijian baawakanya ekyali kisoose okukkirizibwa nti akawuka ka coronavirus kaatandikira mu Wuhan, nga bawagira endowooza z’okwekobaana ezaali ziraga nti COVID-19 yatandikira mu U.S. oba Italy.
Obukulembeze bwa Donald Trump mu Amerika bwogera ku coronavirus nga "Akawuka k’e China " oba "Akawuka k’e Wuhan " nga bagamba nti "okuwangulwa kwa China kwabaleetera okukola akawuka kati akafuuse ekizibu ky’ensi yonna ", nga kino nakyo kikolokoteddwa abantu abamu ng’okusosola mu langi "nga kivudde ku kulemererwa kw’obukulembeze bwe okulwanyisa obulwadde " buno.
Daily Beast yafuna obubaka okuva mu gavumenti ya Amerika nga bulaga akakodyo k’empuliziganya okuva mu National Security Council, ng’akakodyo kalaga nti "Buli kimu kikwata ku China.
Tutegeezebwa okugezaako okufulumya amawulire gano mu ngeri yonna esoboka, omuli enkuŋŋaana z’amawulire n’okulabikira ku ttivvi." Emikutu nga Politico, Foreign Policy, ne Bloomberg gyagamba nti kaweefube wa China ku kuweeeza obuyambi eri amawanga agakoseddwa akawuka kye kimu ku ppokoppoko waabwe ow’okufuna obuganzi mu nsi yonna.
Akulira ensonga z’amawanga amalala mu EU (foreign policy chief) Josep Borrell yalabula nti mulimu "ebyobufuzi by’amawanga omuli n’okulwanira obwannampala ne 'ebyobufuzi bya mwoyo gwa ggwanga'".
Borrell era yagamba nti "China erwana okuyisaawo obulaga nti, obutafaanana na Amerika, bo balina obuvunaanyizibwa era beesigika."
China era yasaba Amerika okuggya envumbo ku Syria, Venezuela ne Iran, ng’eno bw’egenda mu maaso n’okuweereza amawanga ago obuyambi.
Obuyambi bwa Jack Ma obw’obukookolo 100,000 eri Cuba bwakwatibwa olw’envumbo za Amerika nga 3 Ogwokuna.
Aboobuyinza mu Amerika nabo baanenyezebwa olw’okuwamba obuyambi obwali buweerezebwa mu mawanga amalala ne babwekomya.
Era wabaddewo obutakkaanya obukwata ku bukookolo wakati w’amawanga amalala, nga Germany, Austria ne Switzerland; ne Czech Republic ne Italy.
Ekirala, Turkey yabowa ebikumi n’ebikumi by’ebyuma ebiyamba mu kussa (ventilators) ebyali bigenda e Spain.
Ku ntandikwa y’Ogwokusatu, gavumenti ya Italy yakolokota Omukago gwa Bulaaya olw’obutayimirira wamu ne Italy ng’ekoseddwa coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, omukiise wa Italy mu EU, yagamba nti "China yokka ye yabafaako.
Mu buli ngeri, kano si kabonero kalungi ak’omukago gwa Bulaaya."
Nga 22 Ogwokusatu, oluvannyuma lw’okwogera ku ssimu ne Ssaabaminisita wa Italy Giuseppe Conte, Pulezidenti wa Russia Vladimir Putin yateekateeka amagye ga Russia okuweereza abasawo b’amagye, ebimotoka ebifuuyira eddagala, n’ebikozesebwa ebirala mu kujjanjaba mu Italy.
Olupapula (lw’amawulire) lwa Italy olwa La Stampa nga lwesigama ku "munnabyabufuzi owa waggulu ennyo" ataayatuukirizibwa lwagamba nti ebitundu 80 ku kikumi eby’obuyambi bwa Russia "tebwalina mugaso oba bwalina omugaso mutono nnyo eri Italy ".
Munnabyabufuzi ono yalangira Russia okuzannya "ebyobufuzi" bya kabampaane.
Pulezidenti wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, ne Minisita wa Italy ow’Ensonga z’Ebweru Luigi Di Maio baasambajja ebyafulumira mu mawulire ago era ne balaga okusiima kwabwe.
Russia era yaweereza ennyonyi y’emigugu ng’erimu obuyambi bw’eddagala eri Amerika.
Omwogezi wa Kremlin Dmitry Peskov yagamba nti "mu kuwaayo obuyambi eri Amerika, [Putin] asuubira nti abakozi b’eddagala mu Amerika bwe banaatereera ebintu ne bidda mu nteeko, nabo bajja kuba basobola okumusasula bwe kinaaba kyetaagisizza."
Enteekateeka ya NATO eya "Defender 2020" mu Germany, Poland, n’amawanga ga Baltic, ng’eno y’enteekateeka y’amagye eya NATO esinga obunene okuva Cold War bwe yakomekkerezebwa, ejja kubaawo ng’ekendeezeddwa ku mudigido.
Omuwandiisi wa Kakuyege w’Okuggyako Ebyokulwanyisa Namuzisa (Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament) Kate Hudson yakolokota enteekateeka ya Defender 2020: "Mu kizibu ky’ebyobulamu ekiriwo kati, kissa mu katyabaga obulamu bwa bannamagye ga Amerika n’amawanga ga Bulaaya mangi awamu ne bannansi b’omu mawanga gye bakolera." Gavument ya Iran ekoseddwa nnyo akawuka, nga bammemba ba paalamenti abasoba mu makumi abiri bakwatiddwa akawuka awamu ne bannabyabufuzi abalala kkumi na bataano.
Pulezidenti wa Iran Hassan Rouhani yawandiika ebbaluwa ey’awamu eri abakulembeze mu nsi yonna ng’asaba obuyambi nga 14 Ogwokusatu 2020, ng’agamba nti eggwanga lye likaluubirizibwa okulwanyisa obulwadde olw’okusalwa ku butale bw’ensi yonna olw’envumbo Amerika ze yassa ku Iran. Okubalukawo kw’obulwadde buno kwongedde ku kulaajanira Amerika okugoberera enkola za nnaakalyakaani (social policies) ezisangibwa ennyo mu mawanga amalala amagagga, omuli obujjanjabi obwa bonna, okulabirira abaana bonna, empummula ensasulire, n’okussa ennyo ssente mu byobujjabi bw’abantu bonna.
Abatunuulizi b’ebyobufuzi baateebereza nti kiyinza okukosa emikisa gya Donald Trump okuddamu okulondebwa mu kulonda kwa pulezidenti okwa 2020. Enkolagana wakati wa Japan ne South Korea yasajjuka olw’ekirwadde kino.
South Korea yakolokota enkola za Japani eza "kalantiini ezibuzaabuza n’obutabaamu mulamwa" oluvannyuma lwa Japan okulangirira nti buli muntu ava e South Korea ajja kussibwa mu kalantiini mu bifo ebiteereddwawo gavumenti okumala wiiki bbiri.
Abantu b’e South Korea mu kusooka baali beeyawuddemu olw’engeri Pulezidenti Moon Jae-in gye yakwatamu ensonga z’ekirwadde.
Abakoleya bangi bassa emikono ku kiwandiiko ekisaba okugobwa kwa Moon olwa kye baayita gavumenti okukwata obubi ensonga y’ekirwadde ekibaluseewo, ate abamu nga bawagira enkola ye. Ekizibu kino kireetedde amawanga okuyisa amateeka ag’amangu okusobola okukirwanyisa.
Abatunuulizi abamu balaze okutya nti kiino kiyinza okusobozesa gavumenti okunywereza mu buyinza.
Mu Hungary, paalamenti yaayo yalonda ng’ekkiriza ssaabaminisita, Viktor Orbán, okufugira mu kirangiriro awatali bbanga ggere, ne bayimiriza paalamenti awamu n’okulonda n’okubonereza abo abatwalibwa okuba nga basaasaanya amawulire ag’obulimba ku kawuka n’engeri gavumenti gy’ekuttemu ekizibu kino.
Okubalukawo kwa coronavirus kuweereddwa ng’eky’okwekwasa olw’ebintu bingi ebikendedde, nga kiva ku bintu ebyongedde okukozesebwa ennyo okwetooloola ensi mu kulwanyisa obulwadde gye bugenze bubalukawo, okugula ebintu ebingi omulundi ogumu, n’okutaataaganyizibwa mu nkola y’amakolero n’emirimu emirala.
Ekitongole kya America ekikola ku by’emmere n’eddagala (United States Food and Drug Administration) kyayisa okulabula ku bbula ly’eddagala n’ebikozesebwa mu kujjanjaba olw’obwetaavu bwabyo okweyongera n’okutaataaganyizibwa mu nfulumya yaabyo.
Ebitundu bingi era byalimu okugula ebintu ebingi omulundi ogumu ekyaviirako amaduuka okuggwaamu ebintu eby’omugaso ng’emmere, ebikookooma, n’amazzi g’okunywa, so nga ne gye bisuubulwa bikendedde.
Okusingira ddala abakola ebyuma bikalimagezi baalabula nti wajja kubaawo okukeerewa mu kutambuza ebyuma bino.
Okusinziira ku mukulu wa WHO Tedros Adhanom, obwetaavu bw’ebintu eby’okwekuuma bulinnye emirundi 100.
Obwetaavu buno buleeseewo okweyongera mu miwendo egyekubisizzaamu emirundi egiwera amakumi abiri n’okuleetera ebintu ebikozesebwa mu byobulamu okukeerewa okutuuka emyezi egiwera ena okutuuka ku mukaaga.
Era kireeseewo ebbula ly’ebintu ebikuuma abantu mu nsi yonna, nga WHO erabula nti kino kijja kussa obulamu bw’abasawo mu katyabaga.
Mu Australia, ekizibu ky’ekirwadde kino kyawa omukisa abasuubuzi ba daigou okutunda ebyamaguzi by’e Australian mu China.
Ekikolwa kino kyaleetawo ebbula ly’emmere y’abaana abawere mu ssemaduuka ezimu era oluvannyuma ne kiwerebwa mu gavumenti ya Australia. Newankubadde waliwo abalwadde ba COVID-19 bangi mu Bukiikakkono bwa Italy ne mu kitundu ky’e Wuhan, nga noolwekyo waliyo obwetaavu bw’emmere bungi, ebitundu bino byombi tebibaddeemu bbula lya mmere liyitiridde.
Amakubo China ne Italy ge baayitamu okulwanyisa okugula ebintu ebingi n’obusuubuzi obutali mu mateeka gakoze, ne basobola okwewala ebbula ly’emmere eriyitiridde eryasuubirwa mu Bulaaya ne mu Bukiikakkono bwa America.
Mu bukiikakkono bwa Italy ewali obulimi obungi tewabaddeeyo bbula lya mmere lya maanyi, wabula emiwendo biyinza okulinnya okusinziira ku bakiikirira amakolero.
Amasa g’emmere ameereere gaalabwako ekiseera kitono, wadde ne mu kibuga Wuhan, ng’eno abakungu ba gavumenti ya China baggula amaterekero g’ennyama y’embizzi okukakasa ng’abantu balya ekimala.
Amateeka geegamu gali ne mu Italy ng’abakozi b’emmere kibeetaagisa okukuuma emmere olw’ebibamba nga bino.
Okukosebwa okutuuse ku byenfuna by’ensi yonna China ekuwuliddemu: okusinziira ku alipoota eyafulumira mu mawulire nga 16 Ogwokusatu, ebyenfuna mu China byakosebwa nnyo mu myezi ebiri egyasooka mu 2020 olw’enkola ezassibwawo gavumenti okulemesa akawuka okusaasaana, era ebitundibwa eri abantu byakendeera ebitundu 20.5%.
Olw’okuba nga China erina ebyenfuna bya maanyi era efulumya ebintu bingi, okubalukawo kw’akawuka kutaataaganyizza nnyo ebyenfuna by’ensi yonna.
Agathe Demarais owa Economist Intelligence Unit yateebereza nti obutale bujja kusigala nga tebutegeerekeka bulungi okutuusa ng’ekifaananyi ekitegeerekeka ku kiyinza okuddirira kirabise.
Mu Janwali 2020, abeekenneenya abamu baateebereza nti obulwadde kye bunaatuusa ku byenfuna ku nkulaakulana y’ensi yonna kiyinza okusinga ku ekyo ekyaliwo olw’obulwadde bwa SARS mu 2002–2004 SARS.
Okuteebereza kw’omukugu omu mu Washington University mu St. Louis kwalaga ekkonde lya buwumbi bwa doola 300 n’okusingawo ku bintu ebikolebwa mu nsi yonna nga kino kiyinza okubeerawo okumala emyaka egiwera ebiri.
Ekibiina ky’Amawanga Agatunda Amafuta (Organization of the Petroleum Exporting Countries (OPEC)) kigambibwa nti “kyagwa” oluvannyuma lw’ebbeeyi y’amafuta okukendeera ennyo olw’okukendeera kw’obwetaavu bwago mu China.
Obutale bw’emigabo mu nsi yonna bwagwa nga 24 Ogwokubiri olw’okweyongera ennyo mu muwendo gw’abalwadde ba COVID-19 wabweru wa China.
Nga 27 Ogwokubiri, olw’okweyongera okweraliikiriza ekirwadde kya coronavirus, ebibalo by’enkola y’emigabo (stock indexes) bingi mu U.S. omuli NASDAQ-100, S&amp;P 500 Index, ne Dow Jones Industrial Average byalaga okukka kw’emiwendo okukyasinze okuva mu 2008, nga Dow yakka obutundutundu 1,191, nga kuno kwe kukka okwali kukyasinze okuba okunene okuva ku katyabaga k’ebyenfuna aka 2007–08.
Ebibalo byonsatule byamalako wiiki nga biri wansi ebitundu 10%.
Nga 28 Ogwokubiri, Scope Ratings GmbH baakakasa nti China yali ekyetengeredde mu byenfuna (sovereign credit rating), wabula baalaga nti kino kyali kisobola okukyuka (Negative Outlook).
Emigabo gyaddamu ne gikka olw’okutya coronavirus, ng’okukka okungi kwaliwo nga 16 Ogwokusatu.
Bangi balowooza nti wajja kubaawo okugwa mu byenfuna (economic recession).
Munnabyanfuna Mohamed El-Erian yatendereza enkola za banka eza wakati n’amasaza.
Banka za wakati zaasitukiddemu mangu okusinga bwe zaakola mu kudobonkana kw’ebyenfuna okwa 2008.
Ebyobulambuzi kye kimu ku bitongole ebisinze okukosebwa olw’okuyimiriza entambula, okuggala ebifo by’olukale omuli n’ebyo ebyettanirwa abatambuze, n’okuwabula kwa gavumenti okwewala okutambula okw’engeri yonna okwetooloola ensi yonna.
Ekyava mu kino, ennyonyi ezisinga zaasazaamu entambula zaazo olw’obutettanirwa bulungi, omuli British Airways, China Eastern Airlines, ne Qantas, so nga kampuni y’ennyonyi y’e Bungereza eya Flybe yo yagwa.
Ekyatuusibwa ku kampuni z’amaato agalambuza abantu kyo kyali tekirabwangako emabega.
Sitashoni z’eggaali z’omukka nnyingi n’emyalo gy’ebidyeri nagyo gyaggalwa.
Obulwadde buno bwajjira mu kiseera kyekimu ne Chunyun, ekiseera ky’okutambula ennyo mu kwetegekera oluwummula lw’Omwaka gwa China Omupya.
Emikolo mingi egibaamu abantu abangi gyasazibwamu gavumenti ya wakati n’ez’ebitundu, nga mwemuli n’ebikujjuko by’Omwaka Omupya, nga n’amakampuni ag’obwannannyini gaggalawo awamu n’ebifo by’abalambuzi nga Hong Kong Disneyland ne Shanghai Disneyland.
Emikolo gy’Omwaka Omupya mingi n’ebifo by’abalambuzi byaggalwa okwewala okukuŋŋaanya abantu abangi, omuli Forbidden City mu Beijing n’emyoleso gy’omu masinzizo amakadde.
Mu province za China 24 ku ezo 31, zi munisipaali, n’ebitundu, abakulembeze baayongezaayo oluwummula lw’Omwaka Omupya okutuuka nga 10 Ogwokubiri, ne balagira emirimu egisinga obutaggulawo okutuusa olunaku olwo.
Ebitundu bino bikola ebitundu 80% eby’enfuna y’eggwanga (GDP) n’ebitundu 90% eby’ebintu ebitundibwa ebweru w’eggwanga.
Hong Kong yalinnyisa ku mutendera gwayo ogw’okulwanyisa endwadde ezisiigibwa n’egutuusa ku ogwo ogusinga okubeera waggulu (highest level) era n’erangirira akaseera aka kazigizigi, n’eggala amasomero okutuusa mu Gwokusatu era n’esazaamu ebikujjuko by’Omwaka Omupya. Obusuubuzi bw’ebintu ebiguzibwa abantu ba bulijjo (retail sector) bukoseddwa mu nsi yonna, ng’amaduuka gaakendeeza ku ssaawa ze gaggulirawo oba okugira nga gaggaddewo.
Okugula ebintu ku basuubuzi bano mu Bulaaya ne Latin America kwakendeera ebitundu 40%.
Abatunzi ab’ekika kino mu North America ne Middle East baafuna okukendeera kw’emirimu gyabwe kwa bitundu 50–60%.
Kino era kyavaamu okukendeera kwa bitundu 33–43% okw’abantu abatambuza ebigere okugenda mu maduuka mu Gwokusatu bw’ogeraageranya n’Ogwokubiri.
Abaddukanya ebizimbe by’amaduuka ebinene (shopping malls) okwetooloola ensi bassaawo ebigobererwa ebirala, ng’okwongera ku buyonjo, okussaawo obupima ebbugumu ly’abaguzi, n’okubaako emikolo gye basazaamu. Okusinziira ku kuteebereza kwa United Nations Economic Commission for Latin America, okugwa kw’ebyenfuna okunaaleetebwa ekizibu ky’obulwadde buno kuyinza okuleka abantu abalala abali wakati w’obukadde 14 ne 22 mu bwavu obuyitiridde mu Latin America okusinga nga bwe kyandibadde singa ekizibu kino tekyagwawo.
Mu Janwali n’Ogwokubiri 2020, obulwadde we bwasingira okuba obungi mu Wuhan, abantu obukadde nga 5 mu China baafiirwa emirimu gyabwe.
Bangi ku bantu mu China abali eyo mu bukadde nga 300 abaddukira mu byalo okukola baakonkomalira awaka mu province z’omunda oba mu Hubei province. Mu Gwokusatu 2020, Abamerika abasoba mu bukadde 10 baafiirwa emirimu gyabwe ne basaba obuyambi bwa gavumenti.
Okubalukawo kwa coronavirus kuyinza okuviirako okufiirwa emirimu obukadde 47 mu Amerika era n’abantu abatalina mirimu ne batuuka ku bitundu 32%, okusinziira ku kuteebereza kwa Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis. Omuggalo mu India gulesse obukadde n’obukadde bw’Abayindi abakozi ba lejjalejja nga tebalina mirimu. Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa Angus Reid Institute kwakizuula ng’ebitundu 44% eby’amaka mu Canada gafunye ku kizibu ky’obutaba na mirimu. Abakozi kyenkana 900,000 baafiirwa emirimu gyabwe mu Spain okuva lwe baagenda mu muggalo mu makkati g’Ogwokusatu 2020.
Mu kitundu ekyokubiri eky’Ogwokusatu, Abakozi mu France obukadde 4 baasaba obuyambi olw’okuba nga tebalina mirimu mu kiseera kino (temporary unemployment benefits) ate abakozi akakadde 1 mu Bungereza baasaba ebbanja ery’awamu (universal credit scheme). Amakampuni emitwalo nga ataano mu Germany baasindika abakozi baabwe ku nkola ya gavumenti ey’okukolera n’okusasulirwa ekiseera ekitonoko emanyiddwa nga Kurzarbeit.
Enkola ya Germany ey’okukolera n’okusasulirwa ekiseera ekitono etandikiddwa ne mu France ne Britain.
Ebisaawe bya katemba n’okukuuma obuwangwa nabyo bikoseddwa nnyo ekizibu kino, nga kiziŋŋamizza emirmu gy’ebitongole n’abantu ssekinnoomu—abakozesebwa n’abeekozesa—mu nsi yonna.
Ebitongole by’okuyiiya n’obuwangwa byagezaako okusigala nga bikola emirimu gyabyo (nga gino gitera okubeera nga gusasulirwa bantu) egy’okukkiriza abantu okugenda mu bifo by’obuwangwa, okukuuma abakozi baabyo n’abantu abalala nga balamu, n’okuyamba abayiiya we kiba kyetaagisizza.
Mu Gwokusatu 2020, mu nsi yonna, amakaddiyiro, amaterekero g’ebitabo, ebifo ewategekerwa ebiyiiye, n’ebitongole by’ebyobuwangwa ebirala byali biggaddwa nga n’emyoleso, n’emikolo emirala gisaziddwamu oba gyongezeddwayo.
Oluvannyuma lwa kino waaliwo kaweefube ow’amaanyi okutuusa ku bantu obuweereza nga bayita ku mikutu gya kompyuta. Ekintu ekirala ekivudde mu bulwadde kwe kuyimiriza obuweereza bw’eddiini, ebyemizannyo, ebintu ebirala ebikwata ku byokwesanyusa, ng’ebivvulu by’ennyimba ne konsati, emisomo gya tekinologiya, n’emikolo gy’emisono.
Ekisaawe kya cinema nakyo kifunye okutaataaganyizibwa. Vatican yalangirira nti okukuza Wiiki Entukuvu mu Rooma, okubaawo mu wiiki y’Ekisiibo esembayo, kusaziddwamu.
Amasaza mangi gaasaba Abakristu abakadde okusigala eka mu kifo ky’okusoma Emmisa ku Sande; kkereziya ezimu zaateeka okusaba ku leediyo, ku yintaneeti oba ku ttivvi so ng’abalala basaba nga tebavudde mu bidduka byabwe (drive-in worship).
Essaza ly’Abakatoliki e Rooma bwe lyaggala Kkereziya zaalyo ne kkereziya z’omu St. Peter's Square ne ziggwaamu abalamazi, eddiini endala nazo zaasazaamu okusaba kwazo era ne zikendeeza ku nkuŋŋaana z’abantu mu makanisa, emizikiti, sinaagooga, ebiggwa ne gwadala.
Minisitule ya Iran ey’Ebyobulamu yalangirira okusazaamu okusaala kw’Olwokutaano mu bitundu ebikoseddwa obulwadde era amasinzizo oluvannyuma ne gaggalwa, so nga Saudi Arabia yayimiriza abalamazi okuva ebweru w’eggwanga awamu ne bannansi baayo okuyingira mu bifo ebitukuvu ekya Mecca ne Medina.
Ekirwadde kyaleetawo okutaataaganyizibwa mu kalenda y’ebyemizannyo okukyasinze okuba okw’amaanyi okuva mu Ssematalo Owookubiri.
Ebyemizannyo ebisinga ettutumu bingi byasazibwamu oba byayongezebwayo, omuli UEFA Champions League ya 2019–20, Premier League wa 2019–20, UEFA Euro 2020, NBA wa 2019–20, ne NHL wa 2019–20.
Ekirwadde kyataataaganya enteekateeka za Summer Olympics wa 2020, ezaali zitegekeddwa okutandika ku nkomerero y’Ogwomusanvu; International Olympic Committee ayalangirira nga 24 Ogwokusatu nti emizannyo gijja “kuddamu gitegekebwe oluvannyuma lwa 2020 naye obutasukka summer wa 2021". Casino n’ebifo by’ebyemizannyo ebirala mu nsi yonna byaggalwawo n’empaka z’emizannyo gy’oku mmeeza (poker tournaments) nazo zaayongezebwayo oba okusazibwamu.
Kino kiviiriddeko abazannyi ba zzaala bangi okugenda ku yintaneeti, nga kati emikutu gya zzaala w’oku yintaneeti giraga nti omuwendo gw’abagyetabako gulinnye nnyo. Ekisaawe ky’ebyokusanyusa abantu nakyo kikoseddwa nnyo, ng’ebibiina by’abayimbi bingi bisazizzaamu oba biyimirizza eŋŋendo za konsati zaabyo.
Thieta ennene nnyingi okugeza ezo eziri ku Broadway nazo zaasazaamu ebivvulu byazo byonna.
Abayimbi abamu bagezezzaako ku ngeri endala ez’okufulumya n’okugabana emirimu gyabwe nga bayita ku yintaneeti mu kifo ky’enkola eya bulijjo ey’okuyimbira abantu obutereevu, okugeza konsati z’oku yintaneeti (live streaming concerts) oba okussaawo “ebivvulu” by’oku yintaneeti (web-based "festivals") abayimbi mwe basobolera okuyimba, okusaasaanya, n’okulanga emirimu gyabwe.
Ku yintaneeti, obubaka obugingirire obukwata ku coronavirus busaasaanye olw’abantu abangi okutandika okukifuula eky’okuseka n’okuzannya wakati mu butamanya kituufu.
Okuva COVID-19 lwe yabalukawo, waliwo okusalira abalala omusango, obukyayi bw’amawanga, n’obusosoze mu mawanga ebirabiddwako eri abantu abasibuka mu China ne East Asia, n’eri abantu abava mu bitundu ebikoseddwa ennyo mu Bulaaya, United States n’amawanga amalala.
Waliwo okutya, okusongwamu ennwe, n’obukambwe ebirabiddwako mu mawanga mangi, okusingira ddala mu Bulaaya, East Asia, North America, n’ekitundu kya Asia-Pacific.
Alipoota okuva mu Gwokubiri (ng’abalwadde abasinga bakyali mu China) ziraze ebikolwa by’obusosoze mu mawanga eri ebibinja by’Abachina mu nsi yonna nti basaanidde okubeera n’akawuka oba nga batuusibwako ekyo ekitwalibwa okuba okusasulwa okutuufu.
Amawanga agamu mu Africa nago gabaddemu ebikolwa ebyeyongedde ebiraga obukyayi eri China.
Abatuuze b’omu Wuhan ne Hubei bangi bagambye nti basosolebwa olw’ekitundu gye bava.
Wabaddewo obuwagizi eri Abachina, ku yintaneeti n’awalala, n’eri abo ababeera mu bitundu ebikoseddwa akawuka.
Akawuka nga kamaze okusaasaanira amawanga amalala, abantu b’omu Italy, eggwanga eryasooka mu Bulaaya okukosebwa ennyo COVID-19, nabo baatandika okwekengerwa n’okusosolwa. Bannansi mu mawanga omuli Malaysia, New Zealand, Singapore, ne South Korea mu kusooka bassa emikono ku biwandiiko ebisaba okuwera Abachina okuyingira mu mawanga gaabwe mu kugezaako okukomya obulwadde.
Mu Japan, eŋŋombo #OmuchinaTojjaMuJapan (#ChineseDontComeToJapan) yakyaka nnyo ku Twitter.
Abachina ne bannansi ba Asia abalala mu United Kingdom ne United States baloopye okweyongera mu bikolwa by’okusosolwa, n’okulumizibwa.
Pulezidenti wa gurdwaras Donald Trump akolokoteddwa nnyo olw’okuyita coronavirus "Akawuka k’e China", ekigambo abakolokosi kye bayise eky’obusosoze era ekiraga obukyayi eri China.
Abeekalakaasi mu Ukraine baalumba baasi eyali eggya bannansi ba Ukraine n’amawanga amalala mu Wuhan okubatwala mu Sanzhary.
Abayizi abava mu Northeast India, ng’eno esalagana ne China, nga basomera mu bibuga bya India ebikulu kigambibwa nti baayita mu kutulugunyizibwa okwekuusa ku bulwadde bwa coronavirus.
Pulezidenti w’ekiwayi ky’e West Bengal eky’Ekibiina kya Bharatiya Janata Dilip Ghosh yagamba nti Abachina baayonoona obutonde era nti "ye nsonga eyaleetera Katonda okubabonereza."
Ebigambo bino oluvannyuma byavumirirwa omubaka wa China mu Kolkata, eyabiyita "ensobi". Mu China, obukyayi bw’abagwira n’okusosola mu mawanga eri abatuuze abatali Bachina bisajjuddwa ekirwadde kino, ng’abagwira bayitibwa "kasasiro omugwira" era bamulondoola "okumusuula".
Empapula z’amawulire nnyingi ezirimu ebifo ebisasulirwa zaabiggyamu ne zissaamu obubaka obukwata ku coronavirus mu bimu ku byo oba byonna.
Abafulumya empapula z’ekinnassaayansi bangi empapula ezikwata ku kirwadde kino baazifuula za bwereere.
Bannassaayansi abamu baasalawo okugabana mangu bye bazudde ku mikutu emyangu nga bioRxiv.
